\v 17 Tamba la nyan Iliaja n…®ma kwondumba Godna nj…®vwa kwutnda vla wan nyan kwukiyand…®. Nd…®nai waigaa nyaang…®t wutaa God kat kai wal…®ga n…®mba God waa nyaang…®t mbukiya nyan kat kawiga t…®giyandi waa wand…® ensel.   
