\p
\v 26 Ilisabetna yaapmba nyan mbak s…®la k…®ta t…®nd…® maa God nd…®na ensel Gebriel kat wand…® maa Galili wal…®nja n…®ma k…®pmana ngepma Nasaret wal…®nja ngepmat yind…®.  
