\p
\v 38 Wand…® maa Maria wal…®. Wovuna. Wama nyaang…®t t…®giyand…®. Wun ana kai waigowun. Godna nj…®vwa kwukiyowun waa wal…® maa ensel l…® kat kwagalalaa yind…®.   
\s1 MARIA ILISABET KAT V∆óVAT YIL∆ó  
\p
\v 39 T…®ga l…®ga Maria laataa nduwi la kavat yil…®. Juda wal…®nja n…®ma k…®pmana nat ngepmat laataa yil…®.  
