\v 78 God n…®n kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka l…®gand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga n…®n kat kavle vat awagapma s…®l…®mbwigiyand…®.  
\v 79 Mbambala n…®n kulun wal…®ga kavamba t…®ga n…®mba vla l…®gan…®n. mbambala wundumbu yil…®ga n…®mba vla l…®gan…®n. n…®n kat kwunatnd…® maa n…®na maawut apma vat m…®na yelav…®ka l…®giyan…®n waa wand…® Sekaraia.   
\p
\v 80 Mat nyan Jon tamba n…®ma yind…®. Apma maawut s…®ka l…®nd…®. T…®ga l…®ga ngepma kwagalalaa ndinyangu lapman kwo kava yiga yet…®nd…®. Isrel wal…®nja n…®mba kat nyaang…®t mbutndeya nandinya kat kwo kavamba l…®ga kawiga l…®nd…®.   
\c 2  
\s1 MARIA JISAS KAT KWUT∆ó  
\p
\v 1 Ndina k…®pmana njambwi nyan Sisa Ogastas ngepma ngepmana n…®mbana s…® klavat wand…®.  
