\v 19 Maria wutaa ana mand…®p mand…®p yelav…®ka l…®l…®. L…®la maawupmba t…®nd…®, yelav…®ka l…®l…®.  
\v 20 Sip sip kat v…®ga la n…®mba ndi kat kwagalalaa lungwamataa yindi. Ensel n…®n kat wanda nyaang…®t t…®gand…®, v…®n…®n. God apma nyana. Njambwi nyana waa wandi.   
\s1 JISAS WAA S∆ó WANDI  
