\v 21 Nandinya s…®la kuvuk yind…® maa mat nyana mbang…® p…®taa nd…® kat s…® wandi. Nd…®na s…® jisasa waa wandi. Ndina maawupmba ana wandi. Ensel kan s…® wand…® maa mat nyan ny…®mena yapmba t…®nd…®.   
\p
\v 22 Taagwa nyan kwuta nglambi l…®mbwinjeya nj…®mbla ngwaymba l…®gand…®. Tamba la nyan Moses p…®l…®wuta nyaang…®pmba nglambi s…®l…®mbwindi. Ngi kat t…®ga nglambi l…®mbwivat Jerusalemat yindi. Mat nyan kwutaa God kat s…®mogwivat kalimb…®t.  
\v 23 Tamba Moses kwiya nyaang…®t p…®l…®wutnd…®. Ng…®ma nyan nondanyan aywaa God kat s…®mogwigiyangwuk. Ndi Godna nj…®vwa kwukiyandi waa tamba p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\v 24 Nglambi s…®l…®mbwivat waavi vatnyalaa kwimb…®t. Tamba Moses kwiya nyaang…®pmba kwimb…®t. nugul…®v…®k v…®l…®l…®k kwingweyan wovuna. Namio v…®l…®l…®k kwingweyan wovuna waa tamba p…®l…®wutnd…® Moses.   
\p
\v 25 K…®ta nyan Jwerusalemba la nyan nd…®na s…® Simion. Nd…® apma vat yiga yet…®l…®ga nyana. God waa nyaang…®t wut…®ga nyana. God Isrel wal…®nja n…®mba kat kwunatndeya nj…®mbla kat kawiga l…®l…®nd…® wan nyan. Godna waagan nd…®na mbang…® tavilaa l…®nd…®.  
\v 26 Tak Godna waagan nd…® kat mbutnd…®. Tak ana kiyaigam…®n. Tak God wand…®, yaa nyan Kraist nd…® kat v…®giyam…®n. V…®laa ng…®ni kiyaigam…®n waa mbutnd…®.  
\v 27 Godna waagan ndi kat wand…® maa Godna ngay wuleind…®. Wuleind…® maa Jisasna nyaek ny…®me nd…® kat kwutaa wuleimb…®t. Tamba Moses mbuta nyaang…®pmba nglambi s…®l…®mbwivat wuleimb…®t.  
\v 28 Simion mat nyan kat v…®laa yiga nd…®na taambamba kwutaa Godna s…® kwutaa katsolaa God kat wand…®.  
\v 29 Njambwi nyan tak wun kat wama nyaang…®t mbambala tamba v…®gowun. Mbambala kiyaweyan wovuna. Ana kai waigowun.  
\v 30 Ndinyangu kat kwunapmak kwima nyan mbambala tamba v…®gowun.  
\v 31 Wam…®n maa wan nyan ndinyangu kat aywaa kwunapmak yand…®.  
\v 32 Juda ana ndi nat n…®mba ndi kat apma nyaang…®t v…®s…®mogwind…®, v…®ga wukiyandi. N…®n Isrel waa Juda wal…®nja n…®mba n…®na n…®nd…®mba laatnd…®. N…®na n…®nd…®mba laatndangat nat n…®mba n…®na s…® kwutaa katsogiyandi waa wand…® Simion.   
\p
\v 33 Simion wand…® mala Jisasna nyaek ny…®me wutaa mand…®t mand…®t yelav…®pmb…®k.  
\v 34 Simion mb…®k kat wand…®. God mb…®k kat apma vat yigiyand…® waa walaa Jisasna ny…®me Maria l…® kat v…®ga wand…®. Awut ny…®la. Wan mat nyan kwutndeya nj…®vwa kwutnd…® mala Judana n…®ma sakwat njambwi n…®mba kavle yigiyandi. N…®ma sakwat n…®mba kwo n…®mba apma vat t…®giyandi. Nat n…®ma sakwat n…®mba nd…® kat kai waigandi.  
\v 35 Nd…® kat kai waiga n…®mba maawupmba yelav…®tnjeya vak ana pagwugiyandi. Kapmba kai waigandi. Kai wanja nj…®mbla ny…®n kat n…®ma vat t…®giyand…® waa wand…® Simion.   
\p
\v 36 Profetna nj…®vwa kwut…®ga taagwa k…®ta l…®l…®. L…®la s…® Ana. L…®la nyaekna s…® Panuel. L…®la yelang…® Asa wal…®nja yelang…®. L…® av…®t taagwak. Tak ndu klalaa naambi s…®la v…®li t…®l…®.  
\v 37 L…®la lan kiyand…® maa to lagwa kwal…®. L…®la naambi ndumi aynat kiyeli aynat. Godna ngaymba m…®na jnj…®vwa kwuka yet…®l…®. Nat walaa nandinya ngan God kat m…®na wagalaga yet…®l…®l…®.  
\v 38 Jisasna nyaek ny…®me t…®l…®mb…®k mala Godna ngay wuleil…®l…®. Mat nyan kat v…®laa God kat s…®vu l…®l…®l…®. Kumba la nat n…®mba God ng…®ni Juda kat kwunatndeya nj…®mbla kat kawiga l…®ndi. Wundi n…®mba kat v…®laa wal…®. Nd…®nay…®. N…®n kat kwunakiya nyana waa wal…®. N…®n kat kwunakiya nyan tamba yalaa l…®gand…® waa Jerusalemba la n…®mba kat mbutseli mbutsela mbut…®l…®.   
\s1 NASARETNAT LUNGWAMATAA YINDI  
\p
\v 39 God waa nyaang…®pmba nglambi aywaa l…®mbwiyagilaa ngepmat y…®mb…®t. Galili wal…®ngja k…®pmat yiga mb…®tna angwa ngepma Nasaretnat Jisas kat kwutaa yimb…®t.  
\v 40 T…®ga l…®ga mat nyan n…®man yind…®. Nd…®na maawut apma vat s…®ka l…®nd…®. Apma vat nd…®na nambu l…®gand…®. God nd…® kat n…®ma kwondu kwind…®.   
\s1 JISAS KWAND∆ó NYAN T∆óGA GODNA NGAYAT YIND∆ó  
\p
\v 41 Jisasna nyaek ny…®me naambi naambi pasova wal…®nja pesto v…®vat Jerusalemat yil…®mb…®t.  
\v 42 Jisasna naambi taamba v…®li kiyeli v…®l…®l…®k t…®nd…®, yil…®nja vak vla pesto kat yil…®ndi.  
\v 43 Pesto ng…®l…®nd…® mala Jerusalem kwagalalaa ngepma lungwamataa yindi. Jisas nd…® ana yind…®. Nd…® wumba l…®nd…®. Mb…®k Jisas tamba yigand…® waa yelav…®taa Jerusalem kwagalalaa yimbit.  
\v 44 N…®ma sakwat n…®mba k…®tamba yil…®ndi. Jisas k…®ta vat yil…®gan…®n waa yelav…®taa k…®ta nandinya yiga t…®mb…®k. Ava yamb…® yiga l…®ga ngan mb…®la ngepma n…®mba al…® n…®mba kat Jisas kat kwaka wagalamb…®t.  
\v 45 Wagalamb…®t, kai ana l…®gand…® wandi. Kai wandi mala nd…® kat kwapmak Jerusalem lungwamataa yimb…®t nd…® kat v…®vat.  
\v 46 Nd…® kat kwaka v…®levimb…®t. Kwaka v…®levilaa kuvut wan nandinya Godna ngay wuleilaa nd…® kat v…®mb…®t. Nat n…®mba kat s…®mogwi l…®ga njambwi n…®mbana n…®nd…®mba ndal…®nd…®, v…®mb…®t. Nd…® kat wagalalaa mbut…®nja nyaang…®t wuka l…®nd…®.  
\v 47 Jisas mbuta nyaang…®t wuta n…®mba ng…®paliga ndandi.  
\v 48 Nd…®na nyaek ny…®me nd…® kat v…®laa mb…®tno ng…®paliga ndamb…®t. Nd…®na ny…®me nd…® kat wal…®. Nyan, an kat manda kat wupma yim…®n. Wuno m…®na nyaekno m…®n kat kwaka yeta. N…®ma vak yelav…®ka kwaka yeta waa wal…® maa wand…®.  
\v 49 Mand kat wun kat kava kava kwat…®mb…®t. Wuna nyaekna ngaymba tuwan apma vatna. Nglaatnd…®. Tuwa vak wupma mb…®k ana v…®ga l…®gamb…®t? Waa wand…®.  
\v 50 Wanda nyaang…®t wutaa ana yigumba yelav…®pmb…®k.   
\p
\v 51 B…®lagwio k…®ta k…®ta yigand…® Nasaretnat. Nasaretmba yiga t…®ga mb…®lai waa vak Jisas wuka l…®nd…®. Nd…®nai ya vak v…®laa nd…®na ny…®me maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®l…®.  
\v 52 Jisas n…®ma yilaa nd…®na nambu apma vat t…®nd…®. Godno nat n…®mbo nd…® kat v…®laa apma vat t…®gand…® waa Jisas kat wandi.   
\c 3  
\s1 JON NYAANG∆óT MBUTND∆ó  
\p
\v 1 Njambwi nyan Tabirias Sisa naambi taamba v…®li kiyeli tambanat v…®ga l…®nd…®. Judia wal…®nja n…®ma k…®pma kat v…®ga la njambwi nyan Pontias Pailat. Galili wal…®nja n…®ma k…®pma kat v…®ga la njambwi nyan Herot. Herotna yakwa nyan Filip kava v…®l…®l…®k kat v…®ga l…®nd…®. Nd…® Ituriagwi Trekonaitis kat v…®ga l…®nd…®. Abilini wal…®nja kava kat v…®ga la nyan Laisenias.  
\v 2 Judana njambwi n…®mba God kat kwunat…®ga n…®mba v…®l…®l…®k pal…®. Mb…®la s…® Anaso Kaiafas. Wan nj…®mbla God Sekaraiana nyan Jon kat wand…®. Wand…®, Jon ndinyangu lapman kwo kavamba yiga l…®nd…®.  
\v 3 God wand…® maa kwo kava kwagalalaa Jodan wal…®nja ndandang…® wayat yind…®. Yiga mbutnd…®. Kavle maawut kwagalalaa mand…®t kupi maawupmba l…®ga ngu yagungweyan God ngwutna kavle vat s…®l…®mbwigiyand…® waa mbutnd…®.  
\v 4 Jon mbuta nyaang…®t tamba la profet Aisaia nd…® tamba k…®ta vat p…®l…®wutnd…®. Kupma p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\li1 K…®ta nyan kwo kavamba l…®ga laataa nyaang…®t mbukiyand…®.  
\li1 Njambwi nyan yaiga yamb…® kwunak ngwula waa bukiyand…®.  
\li1 Ngu l…®ga kava kava ng…®ni tagula k…®pmat t…®giyand…®.   
\li1
\v 5-6 Nduwi t…®ga kava nduwi ndand…®, apma savagu k…®pma t…®giyand…®. S…®vi vita l…®ga yamb…® ng…®ni apma vat t…®giyand…®. N…®ma kambat t…®ga yamb…® ng…®ni savagu l…®giyand…®.  
\li1 Ng…®ni God ndinyangu kat kwunatndeya vak ndinyangu aywaa v…®giyandi  
\p waa tamba p…®l…®wutnd…® Aisaia.   
\p
\v 7 N…®ma sakwat n…®mba ngu yaguvat Jon kat yandi. Yandi maa ndi kat mbutnd…®. Ngwuk apma n…®mba ana ngwuk. Ngwuk kamboyna nyangu vla l…®gangwuk. Ng…®ni yaiga kavle vak kat vaaka l…®ga wun kat yangwuk.  
\v 8 Kavle maawut kwagalalaa apma kupi maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®ngweyan apma vapmba yiga al…® ngwuk. Ngwuk kupma yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk. N…®n Ebrahamna nyangu n…®n. Ngi kat t…®ga kavle savle yiga yet…®neyan God n…®n kat ana kai waigand…® waa yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk. Wupma ke yelav…®ka. Ana nglaatnd…®. Kavle savle yiga yet…®ngweyan God ngwuk kat kai walaa kan t…®ga kambak kwutnd…® mala Ebrahamna nyanguat t…®giyandi.  
\v 9 Kavle mi v…®t…®ga nyan v…®p m…®na l…®gand…®. Av…®mba ngwuk. Apma m…® s…®k kwalapma mi aywaa v…®taa yamba yaagind…®, v…®kiyand…® waa mbutnd…® Jon.   
\p
\v 10 Mbutnd…® mala n…®ma sakwat n…®mba nd…® kat wagalandi. Anda apma nj…®vwa kwutaa apma vat kwo l…®giyan…®n waa nd…® kat wagalandi.  
\v 11 Wagalandi mala ndi kat wand…®. Waavwi v…®l…®l…®k t…®ga nyan nat nyan waavi lapman t…®ga nyan kat agwi. K…®g…®nda l…®ga nyan k…®g…®nda lapman t…®ga nyan kat v…®laa agwi waa wand…® Jon.  
\v 12 Takis sanya klal…®ga n…®mba ngu yaguvat Jon kat yalaa wagalandi. S…®mogwi l…®ga nyan n…®n angambak yigiyan…®n waa wagalandi maa Jon ndi kat wand…®.  
\v 13 Ngwuk kiap waa sakwapmba m…®na klaigangwuk takis sanya. Mand…®p wata kwuleiga s…®kwupmak klal…®ngweya waa Jon ndi kat wand…®.  
\v 14 Soldia nd…® kat wagalandi. N…®n angamak yigiyan…®n waa wagalandi maa Jon ndi kat wand…®. Ngwuk wata woseka waga ndi kat viyaga nat n…®mbana nda s…®kwupmak wal…®ngweya. Ngwuk kat pe kwindi, ngiyambak waa awa waa wand…® Jon.   
\p
\v 15 N…®ma sakwat n…®mba Jon kat v…®laa mand…®p mand…®p yelav…®ka l…®ndi. Nd…® n…®n kat kwunakiya nyan anagand…® waa maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®ndi.  
\v 16 Yelav…®ka l…®nja vak wutaa Jon ndi kat wand…®. Wun n…®ma nj…®vwa ana kwut…®gowun. Ngwuk kat ngu yagua nj…®vwa mat nj…®vwat. Ng…®ni yaiga nyan wuna njambwi nyanat. Wun apma nyan ana wun. Nd…®na man suna yaaw ana al…®ps…®ga njalakiyowun. Apma nyan m…®na njalakiyand…®. Wuna kwupmba ng…®ni yaiga nyan wand…® mala Godna waagan ngwuk kat tavigiyand…®. Tayind…® mala k…®s…®k yamba v…®ka ng…®l…®ndaya vak ngwutna kavle vat ng…®l…®giyand…®.  
\v 17 Ng…®ni yaiga nyan yuwi s…®k kwut…®ga nyan vla l…®gand…®. S…®la s…®lak klalaa yiga yuwi s…®k s…®ka yiga ngaymba yisol…®gand…®. Nd…®na ava nd…®na s…®mb…® s…®ka n…®ma vat v…®t…®ga yamba yisol…®gand…®.   
\p
\v 18 Ndina kavle maawut kwunapmak Jon n…®ma sakwat nyaang…®t mbut…®nd…®. Ndi kat apma nyaang…®t mbut…®nd…®.   
\s1 HEROT JON KAT KALABUS KWUTND∆ó  
\p
\v 19 Wan k…®pmana njambwi nyan Herot nd…®na yakwa nyana taagwa Herodias vanyang…®ka kland…® maa Jon nd…® kat kavle vat yim…®n, m…®n kavle vat yil…®ga nyan m…®n waa wand…®.  
\v 20 Herot ya kavle vat n…®ma sakwatna. Nat kavle vat yiga Jon kat kalabus kwutnd…®.   
\s1 TAT JON KALABUS YILAPMAN T∆óGA JISAS KAT NGU YAGUND∆ó  
\p
\v 21 Jon n…®ma sakwat n…®mba kat ngu yagulaa Jisas kat yagund…®. Yagund…® maa Jisas God kat wagalal…®nd…® maa nyinangwut yamb…® kwand…®.  
\v 22 Wungi yamb…®mba Godna waagan ngaga yand…®. Namiyo saava klalaa yand…®, v…®ndi. V…®laa nyinangwupmba l…®ga kwundi wutndi. M…®n wuna apma nyan m…®. M…®n kat wun solat s…®l…®gowun waa wand…® kwundi.   
\s1 JISASNA YELANG∆ó N∆óMBANA S∆ó  
\p
\v 23 Jisasna naambi ndumi v…®li kiyeli tamba v…®li t…®nd…®, nj…®vwa kwupmat laatnd…®. Nd…® Josepna nyana waa n…®ma sakwat n…®mba yelav…®ka l…®ndi. Wan nyan Josep nd…®na nyaek Hilai.   
