\c 4  
\s1 SETEN JISAS KAT KAVLE VAT AY WAA WAND∆ó  
\p
\v 1 Godna waagan Jisasna mbang…® tavind…® mala Jisas Jodan wal…®nja ndandang…® kwagalalaa kwo kavat yind…®. Godna waagan wanda ava yamb…®mba yind…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 2 Kwo kavamba nandinya ndumi v…®l…®l…®k yet…®nd…®. Yet…®ga l…®ga Seten nd…® kat yalaa kavle vat ay waa wand…®. Nandinya ndumi v…®l…®l…®k k…®g…®nda ana k…®nd…® Jisas. Kwo yet…®nd…®. Wan nandinya ng…®l…®nd…®, wund…® kat t…®nd…®.  
\v 3 Seten nd…® kat yalaa wand…®. Godna nyanat t…®meyan kan t…®ga kambak klalaa bretnao kwupmeyan Godna nyanat t…®ma vak v…®giyowun waa wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®.  
\v 4 Tamba la nyan God waa nyaang…®t p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\li1 K…®g…®nda k…®vak kat m…®na yelav…®t…®giya n…®mba ndi apma vat ana t…®giyandi  
\p waa tamba la nyan p…®l…®wutnd…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 5 Seten Jisas kat kwutaa nat kavat kalind…®. Nd…® kat kalilaa kan k…®pmana njambwi n…®mba v…®ga la kava aywaa nd…® kat kwiyatapman v…®s…®mogwind…®.  
\v 6 V…®s…®mogwilaa wand…®. V…®l…®ma njambwi n…®mbana ava kwondu wuna kwondua. Wunamba klandi. Wuna maawupmba nat n…®mba kat kwil…®gowun.  
\v 7 Wun kat v…®laa nambu s…®landalaa m…®n njambwi nyan m…®n waa wameyan m…®n kat wuna kwondu kwigiyowun waa wand…® Seten.  
\v 8 Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Tamba la nyan God waa nyaang…®t p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\li1 Ngwutna njambwi nyan k…®ta l…®gand…®. Godna. Nat nyan kat m…®n njambwi nyan m…®n waa ke waa. God k…®ta l…®gand…® njambwi nyan  
\p waa tamba p…®l…®wutnd…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 9 Setan nd…® kat nat njamb…® kwutaa Jerusalemat kalind…®. Kalind…® maa God kat kwunat…®nja s…®vla mbund…® ngayna samb…® ngeat wokemb…®t. Wokemb…®t maa Seten nd…® kat wand…®. Godna nyanat t…®meyan valaseliga k…®pmamba ndam…®n, v…®lu.  
\v 10 Tamba la nyan God waa nyaang…®t p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\li1 Godna ensel m…®n kat v…®ga l…®giyandi. Ana kavle yigiyam…®n  
\p waa p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\v 11 Nat nyan p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\li1 M…®n kat ensel kwutaa taambamba kwutaa katsogiyandi. N…®mbumba ana n…®mamba ndai viyaigam…®n. Ndi kwutaa katsogiyandi  
\p waa tamba p…®l…®wutnd…® waa wand…® Seten.  
\v 12 Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Nat tamba la nyan God waa nyaang…®t p…®lwutnd…®. Awup m…®la.  
\li1 Ngwula njambwi nyan God kat kavle vat ay waa ke waa  
\p waa tamba p…®l…®wutnd…® waa Jisas wand…®.   
\p
\v 13 Seten Jisas kat kavle vat ay waa wanda nyaang…®t ng…®l…®nd…® maa Jisas kat kwagalalaa yind…®. Yilaa yelav…®tnd…®. Ng…®ni nd…® kat yiga nat njambi waigowun waa yelav…®tnd…®.   
\s1 JISAS GALILI YILAA NJ∆óVWA LAATAA KWUTND∆ó  
\p
\v 14 Godna waagan Jisas kat kwondu kwind…® maa Jisas Galili wal…®nja k…®pmat yind…®. Nj…®vwa kwut…®nda vak kava kava la n…®mba mbutseli mbutsela mbut…®ndi, wutndi.  
\v 15 Juda yisolaa t…®nja ngay wuleilaa ndi kat nyaang…®t mbut…®nd…®. Wutaa apma nyana waa yelav…®taa wandi.   
\s1 NASARETMBA LA N∆óMBA JISAS KAT KAI WAA KWUK NGINDI  
\p
\v 16 Jisas Nasaret wal…®nja ngepma yind…®. Tamba mat nyan t…®ga kan ngepma yet…®ga n…®man yind…®. Nd…®na angwa ngepma. Nj…®vwa lapman nandinya aywaa yisolaa l…®nja ngay wuleil…®ndi. Wuleilaa nyinga l…®ga nyaang…®t v…®vat laatnd…® Jisas.  
\v 17 Laatnd…® maa tamba la profet Aisaia p…®l…®wuta nyaang…®t t…®ga nyinga nd…® kat kwindi. Kwindi maa lavwilaa v…®ga kwundimba wand…®.   
\li1
\v 18-19 Godna waagan wun kat tavilaa mbutnd…®. Kavle vat t…®ga n…®mba ndi kat apma nyaang…®t ambuk m…®la waa mbutnd…®. Ngindi, kalabusmba l…® vla l…®ga n…®mba ndi kat yiga njalap m…®la waa mbutnd…®. Vat ta n…®mba kat ndi kat kwunap m…®la waa mbutnd…®. Mbambala God n…®n kat kwunakiyand…® waa ambup m…®la waa Godna waagan wun kat mbutnd…®  
\p waa tamba la profet p…®l…®wutnd…® waa Jisas viga kwudimba walaa  
\v 20 nyinga wan ngavna nyinga kat v…®ga la nyan kat kwilaa ndaal…®nd…®. Ndaa l…®nd…® mala wan ngaymba la n…®mba apma nyaang…®tna ngambul…®nda waa yelav…®ka aywaa nd…® kat v…®l…®ndi.  
\v 21 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Tamba la nyan p…®l…®wutnda nyaang…®t viga wawa nyaang…®t mbambala kak kiyagand…® waa wand…® maa  
\v 22 wuta n…®mba yelav…®tndi. Wan nyan apma nyaang…®t ngambul…®gand…®. Apma nyaang…®t ngambul…®nda vak andamba kland…®. Nd…® kwo nyana. Nd…® Josepna nyana waa yelav…®ka wandi.   
\p
\v 23 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. K…®ngi ngepmana nyan wun viga l…®gangwuk. Ng…®ni wun kat anagangwuk waiga. Nat ngepma kapaneam yilaa ndina yelogwen kat ta n…®mba kat kwunapm…®n. Angwa ngepma yalaa manda kat kwunatapman yil…®gam…®n waa wun kat anagangwuk waiga.  
\v 24 Wun kat wagalangweya nyaang…®t kat awat waigowun. Awuk ngwula. God waa nyaang…®t but…®ga nyan profet wal…®na nyan nd…®na angwa ngepmamba ta n…®mba nd…® kat kai wal…®gandi.  
\v 25 Tamba wupma l…®nd…®. Tamba Ilaija ta nj…®mbla talagwa n…®ma sakwat t…®ndi n…®n isrelna k…®pmamba. Wan tamba la nj…®mbla naambi kuvuk mbak s…®la k…®ta meik ana ndand…®, k…®g…®nda ng…®l…®nd…®.  
\v 26 Godna nj…®vwa kwutaa tamba la nyan Ilaija k…®g…®nda lapman talagwa kat kwunapmak yind…®. God wand…®, yind…®. N…®n Isrelna talagwa kat kwunapmak nd…® ana yind…®. Kapman ngepmamba ta talagwa kat kwunapmak yind…®. L…®la ngepma Sarefat. Wan ngepma Saidon wal…®nja n…®ma k…®pmamba la ngepma.  
\v 27 Godna nj…®vwa kwuta tamba la nat nyan Ilaisa nd…®no n…®mbun. Nd…®nai la nj…®mbla kawia k…®la Juda n…®ma sakwat t…®ndi. Ndina k…®ta nyan kat ana kwunatnd…®. Kawia k…®la kapma ngepma nyan kat kwunatnd…® Ilaisa. Wan nyana ngepma Siria wal…®na ngepma. Nd…®na s…® Neaman waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 28 Yisolaa l…®nja ngaymba la n…®mba wutaa Jisas kat walia l…®ndi.  
\v 29 Walial…®ga laataa Jisas kat kwutaa ngepma alaguat kalindi. Wungi ngepma nambu nduwimba ngindi, l…®nd…®. Nambu nduwi valagalaa t…®ga kavamba nd…® kat sandavat kalindi.  
\v 30 Ndi n…®ma sakwat n…®mbana mbupmba wuleilaa yind…® Jisas.   
\s1 KAVLE WAAGAN TAVILA NYAN KAT JISAS KWUNATND∆ó  
\p
\v 31 Jisas Galilina nat ngepma kapaneam wal…®nja ngepmat ndaind…®. Nj…®vwa lapman nandinya ndi kat nyaang…®t mbut…®nd…®.  
\v 32 Nd…®nai waa nyaang…®t wuta n…®mba ng…®paliga ndalaa maawupmba yelav…®tndi. Nat n…®mba mbut…®nja vla ana mbut…®gand…®. Kwondumba mbut…®gand…®.  
\v 33 Yisola l…®nja ngaymba Jisas mbut…®nd…® mala kavle waagan tavila la nyan laataa Jisas kat n…®ma kwundimba walega wand…®.  
\v 34 M…®n Jisas Nasaret nyan manda kat n…®n kat yam…®n. N…®n kat vatnyavak yam…®n? M…®n kat v…®ga l…®gowun. M…®n God wand…®, yaa apma nyan m…®n waa walega wand…®.   
\p
\v 35 Wand…® mala Jisas kavle waagan kat kai waga wand…®. makayak. Nd…® kat kwagala waa wand…® maa waagan wan nyan kat kwutaa viyand…® mala ndina n…®nd…®mba k…®pmamba ndand…®. Waagan nd…® kat ana kavle vat yind…®. Nd…® kat viyalaa kwagalalaa yind…®.  
\v 36 Va n…®mba ng…®paliga ndalaa awat sowat wandi. Nd…®nai mbuta nyaang…®t kwonduo tagula nyaang…®tna. Kavle waagan kat wand…® maa wutaa kwagalalaa yil…®gandi. n…®ma tagula vatna waa awat sowat wandi.  
\v 37 Yinda vak kat kava kavamba la n…®mba mbutseli mbutsela mbut…®ndi. Aywaa wutndi.   
\s1 JISAS PITANA NASAKWAT KAT KWUNATND∆ó  
\p
\v 38 Jisas yisolaa t…®nja ngay kwagalalaa Saimon waa Pita wal…®nja nyana ngay wuleind…®. Pitana nasakwatna mbang…®mba n…®mamba kangan wal…®nd…®, kavle vat t…®l…®. L…® kat kwunapmak Jisas kat wagalandi.  
\v 39 L…®la ngwaymba laataa l…®ga yelogwen kat kai wand…®, kwo l…®l…®. L…® laataa ndi kat k…®g…®nda kwutaa kwil…®.   
\s1 JISAS N∆óMA SAKWAT N∆óMBA KAT KWUNATND∆ó  
\p
\v 40 Nya tamba ndai m…®na l…®nd…®. Nat n…®ma sakwat n…®mba yelogwen kat ta n…®mba kat kwutaa Jisas kat kalindi. Ndi kat aywaa taamba taagalaa kwunatn…®.  
\v 41 Kavle waagan tavila la n…®mba kat ndino ndi kat kwunatnd…®. Kan waagan ndinyangu kat kwagalalaa walega wandi Jisas kat. M…®n kat v…®ga l…®gan…®n. M…®n Godna nyan m…®n waa walega walaa kwagalalaa yindi. Jisas ndi kat wupma ke waa waa wand…®. God wand…®, yaa nyan Kraist t…®nda vak nat n…®mba kat mbutnjangat kai walaa wupma ke waa waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 JISAS NGEPMA NGEPMAMBA YIGA NJ∆óVWA KWUTND∆ó  
\p
\v 42 Ngambi wan ngepma kwagalalaa ndinyangu lapman kwo kavat yind…®. Wan ngepma n…®mba nd…® kat kwaka l…®ga nd…®na kwupmba yindi. Ndina ngepma kwagalaa yivak kat kai waa wandi Jisas kat.  
\v 43 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Wuna nj…®vwa k…®ngiyan. God ndinyangu kat v…®ga l…®ga vat ngepma ngepmamba mbukiyowun. Wuna nj…®vwa. K…®ta ngepma m…®na ana mbukiyowun. Ngepma ngepmamba mbukwangat wuna nyaek wand…® mala yawun waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 44 Ndi kat kwagalalaa Judia wal…®nja n…®ma k…®pman ngepma ngepmat yind…®. Ngepma yilaa yisolaa l…®nja ngay wuleilaa nyaang…®t mbut…®nd…®.   
\c 5  
\s1 JISAS WAND∆ó MALA PITA KAMI N∆óMA SAKWAT KWUTND∆ó  
\p
\v 1 Jisas Genesaret wal…®nja sak waymba l…®nd…®. Waymba l…®ga God waa nyaang…®t ndinyangu kat mbut…®nd…®. Wungi nyaang…®t wupmat ngwaymba yaa nd…® kat kematndi.  
\v 2 Jisas v…®nd…® bot v…®l…®l…®k yaawmba tundi, l…®mb…®k. Kami kwuta n…®mba bot kwagalalaa ndina njula k…®s…®k t…®ndangat njangil…®ndi.  
\v 3 Jisas yiga bot k…®ta kund…®. Saimon waa Pita wal…®nja nyana botna kunda Jisas. Saimon kat wagaland…® mala s…®vasagund…®, Jisas bopmba ndaal…®ga ndinyangu kat nyaang…®t mbut…®nd…®.   
\p
\v 4 Jisas mbuta nyaang…®t ng…®l…®nd…® mala Saimon kat wand…®. Jula kulaa samat wogwelaa yiga kami kat yaagi waa wand…®.  
\v 5 Wand…® maa Saimon nd…® kat wand…®. Njambwi nyan kami kai. Nak ngan njula yaagiga v…®levin…®n. Kami kai. M…®n wameyan m…®na kwundimba yiga yaagigiyan…®n njula waa wand…® maa njula kulaa yindi.  
\v 6 Njula yaagilaa n…®ma sakwat kami njula taata l…®nd…®. Njula ng…®l…®p m…®na l…®nd…®.  
\v 7 T…®ga l…®ga nat botna n…®mba kat yagwa waa wandi maa yandi. Yandi maa bot v…®l…®l…®k kami kundi. Bot v…®l…®l…®k taata lumaka ndaivat yimb…®t.  
\v 8 Saimon waa Pita wal…®nja nyan v…®laa Jisasna man ngand…®mba ndalaa wand…®. Njambwi nyan wun kat kwagala. Wun apma nyan ana wun waa wand…®.  
\v 9 Pitagwi nat n…®mbo kami kwutnja sakwat kat v…®laa ng…®paliga ndandi.  
\v 10 Sebedina nyan v…®l…®l…®k Jonogwi Jemso v…®laa ng…®paliga ndamb…®t. Mb…®t Saimono k…®ta nj…®vwa nyan mb…®t. Jisas Jaimon kat wand…®. Ke vaaka. Mbambala kami kwut…®gangwuk. Ng…®ni ndinyangu kat kwutaa wuna mbaapmamba taagagiyangwuk waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 11 Yiga kawilaa bot njula kwagalalaa Jisasna kwupmba yindi.   
\s1 JISAS KAWIA K∆óLA NYAN KAT KWUNATND∆ó  
\p
\v 12 Jisas ngepmamba l…®nd…®, kawiya k…®la nyan nd…® kat yaa v…®laa Jisasna man ngand…®mba ndalaa wand…®. Wun kat kwunapmat wameyan kwunakiyam…®n waa wand…®.  
\v 13 Wand…® maa Jisas nd…®na mbang…® taamba taagalaa wand…®. M…®n kat kwunapmak wowun. Apma vak t…®giyam…®n waa wand…® maa kawiya k…®la vat ng…®l…®nd…®, kwo l…®nd…®.  
\v 14 Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. M…®n kat kwunakwa vat nat n…®mba kat ke mbuka. Tamba Moses mbutnda nyaang…®pmba agwup m…®la. God kat kwunat…®ga nyan kat yiga m…®na mbang…® nd…® kat s…®mogwi. S…®mogwilaa God kat s…®vu k…®vat nd…® kat kwanda kwanda vatnyalaa agwi. Kwimeyan ndinyangu kwo l…®meya vat v…®giyandi waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 15 N…®ma sakwat n…®mba Jisas kwunatnda vak kat mbuseli mbutsela mbut…®ndi. Ngi kat t…®ga n…®ma sakwat n…®mba nd…®na nyaang…®t wupmat yisolaa l…®ndi. N…®ma sakwat n…®mba ndina yelogwen kwunatndangat yisolaa l…®ndi.  
\v 16 Jisas ndi kat kwagalalaa ndinyangu lapman kwo kavat yilaa God kat ngambul…®nd…®.   
\s1 MAN K∆óV∆ó WATNA NYAN KAT JISAS KWUNATND∆ó  
\p
\v 17 Nat nandinya Jisas ngaymba l…®ga nyaang…®t mbut…®nd…®. Ferisiagwi tamba Moses kwiya nyaang…®t s…®mogwi l…®ga n…®mba n…®ma sakwat ndaa l…®ga wut…®ndi. Ndi Galiliagwi Judiana ngepma ngepmamba l…®ga yandi. Ndina nat n…®mba Jerusalemba l…®ga yandi. God Jisas kat kwondu kwind…® mala n…®ma sakwat yelogwen kat ta n…®mba kat kwunat…®nd…®.  
\v 18 K…®v…® watna nyan kat njambamba taagalaa aynat n…®mba walalaa Jisas ta ngayat kalindi.  
\v 19 Nd…® kat kalinjeya yamb…® v…®lavindi. N…®ma sakwat n…®mba taata l…®ndi. T…®ga l…®ga sambange wokelaa nj…®k vla plalaa yaaw tulaa nd…® kat sandandi njambonala. Jisasna m…®ndama kava sandandi.  
\v 20 Jisas nd…® kat v…®laa nd…® kat kwunakwangat sanda n…®mba n…®ma nj…®vwa kwuka sandandi waa yelav…®taa njamb…®mba la nyan kat wand…®. M…®n, kavle vat yiga yet…®ma vak tamba s…®l…®mbwigowun waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 21 Jisas wand…® mala Ferisiagwi Moses kwiya nyaang…®t s…®mogwi la n…®mbo awat sowat ngambul…®ndi. Wan nyan God kat kavle nyaang…®t wand…®. Kavle vat yiga yet…®ma vak tamba s…®l…®mbwigowun waa manda kat wand…®. Nd…® ana al…®ps…®ga s…®l…®mbwigiyand…®. God m…®na al…®ps…®ga s…®l…®mbwigiyandi waa awa saowat ngambul…®ndi.  
\v 22 Maawut wumba yelav…®ka awat sowat ngambul…®nja vat v…®laa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Manda kat wupma yelav…®t…®gangwuk. Ana nglaatnd…®.  
\v 23 Nd…® kat kavle vat yiga yet…®ma vak tamba s…®l…®mbwigowun waa wowun Laataa kwal…®ma njamba kwutaa kali waa wagewan k…®ta nyaang…®tna. Kapmanyaang…®t ana nd…®.  
\v 24 Manda kat kavle vat yiga yet…®ma vak tamba s…®l…®mbwigowun waa wowun. Kan k…®pmamba l…®ga n…®mba kavle vat yiga yet…®njeya vak kat s…®l…®mbwiweya kwondu ngil…®ga. God wun kat kwind…®. Kan kwondu v…®ngwangat nd…® kat kwunakiyowun. Godna vak s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan wun waa wand…® Jisas. Ndi kat walaa njambamba kwa nyan kat wand…®. Laataa kwal…®ma njamba kwutaa kali waa wand…® maa  
\v 25 wan nyan laataa kwal…®nda njamba kwutaa klaiga ngayat yind…®. God nd…® apma nyana n…®ma nyana waga yind…®.  
\v 26 Va n…®mba ng…®paliga ndalaa Godna s…® kwutaa katsondi. Ng…®paliga ndalaa wandi. Mbambala tamba n…®ma vak v…®gan…®n waa wandi.   
\s1 JISAS LIVAI KAT YAGWA WAND∆ó  
\p
\v 27 T…®ga l…®ga wan ngay wogwelaa takis sanya klal…®ga nyan kat v…®nd…®. Wan nyan takis sanya taagal…®nja ngaymba ndaa l…®nd…®. Nd…®na s…® Livai. Jisas nd…® kat v…®laa wand…®. Wuna kwupmba yagwa wand…®.  
\v 28 Wand…® maa Livai nd…®na nda kwagalalaa Jisasana kwupmba yind…®.   
\p
\v 29 Ng…®ni Jisas kat Livai nd…®na ngaymba n…®ma k…®g…®nda kwutnd…®. Takis sanya klal…®ga n…®ma sakwat n…®mbagwi nat n…®mba kat Livai wand…® maa k…®vat yandi. Ndino Jisas nd…®na mbaapma n…®mbo k…®ta vat k…®l…®ndi.  
\v 30 Ng…®ni Ferisio tamba Moses kwiya nyaang…®t s…®mogwi la n…®mbo Jisasna mbaapma n…®mba kat wagalandi. Kavle vat t…®ga takis sanya klal…®ga n…®mbo nat kavle n…®mbo manda kat k…®ta vat k…®l…®gangwuk. Wan apma vat ana nd…®. Wan kavle vatna waa wandi.  
\v 31 Wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Kwo l…®ga n…®mba ndi dokta kat ana yil…®gandi. Yelogwen kat ta n…®mba m…®na dokta kat yil…®gandi.  
\v 32 Mabmbala wungi vat s…®g…®t. Apma vat yiga yet…®l…®ga n…®mba kat kwunapmat ana yawun. Kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®ga n…®mba kat kwunapmak yawun. Kavle maawut kwagalalaa mand…®p kupi maawupmba yet…®njangat yawun waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 K∆óG∆óNDA K∆óVAK KAT KAI WAL∆óNJA VAK  
\p
\v 33 Jisas wand…® mala wandi. Ngu yagu l…®ga Jona mbaapma l…®ga n…®mba ndi n…®ma sakwat njamb…® k…®g…®nda k…®vak kat kai walaa God kat m…®na ngambul…®gandi. Ferisi wal…®nja mbaapma n…®mba ndino wupma yil…®gandi. M…®na mbaapma l…®ga n…®mba kai. Ndi k…®g…®nda ngu nj…®mbla nj…®mbla k…®l…®gandi waa wandi mala Jisas ndi kat wand…®.  
\v 34 Ndu taagwa kat kla nj…®mbla n…®ma k…®g…®nda k…®vak kat kai waigandi? E? K…®giyandi luwa. N…®ma k…®g…®nda.  
\v 35 Ng…®ni yaiga nj…®mbla taagwa kla nyan kat kwutaa kalindi mala ndi n…®ma vak yelav…®ka k…®g…®nda k…®vak kat kai waigandi waa Jisas walaa   
\s1 JISAS TAMBA YET∆óNJA VAK KWAGALALAA MAND∆óT KUPI VAPMBA YET∆óNDA VAK KAT MBUTND∆ó  
\p
\v 36 ndi kat pagwula la nyaang…®tmba wand…®. Tamba ng…®l…®kna waavwi la nyan mand…®t kupi waavwi klalaa tamba waavwi kat kwunapmak ana ng…®l…®kiyand…® kupi waavwi. Ng…®l…®taa tavandeyan mand…®p mand…®p vaand…® kwaigand…®.  
\v 37 Tamba s…®mb…®mba kwutnja awmba k…®ta nyan kupi n…®ma ngu ana kal…®kiyand…®. kal…®tndeyan nguna mbiyak wokend…® mala tamba s…®mb…® ng…®l…®kiyand…®. Ng…®l…®t…®, ngu k…®pma yind…®, s…®mb…® kavle yigiyand…®.  
\v 38 Kupi n…®ma ngu kupi s…®mb…®mba m…®na kal…®t…®gandi. N…®na ngepmana vatna.  
\v 39 K…®ta nyan tamba n…®ma ngu k…®laa kupi n…®ma ngu k…®vak kat ana waigand…®. Kupi n…®ma ngu k…®vak kat kai waigand…®. Tamba n…®ma ngu apma ngua waa waigand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\c 6  
\s1 NJ∆óVWA LAPMAN NANDINYANA NJAMBIA  
\p
\v 1 Nj…®vwa lapman nandinya Jisasagwi nd…®na mbaapma n…®mbo yuwi s…®k kwal…®ga kava yindi. Yiga nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba s…®k klalaa taambamba l…®gagagiga kwut…®ndi, s…®mb…® ndand…®, k…®ndi.  
\v 2 Nat Ferisi k…®l…®nja vak v…®laa wandi. Nj…®vwa lapman nandinyana njambia kat kai walaa manda kat wupma k…®l…®gangwuk waa wandi.  
\v 3-4 Wandi mala Jisas ndi kat wand…®. N…®na tamba njambwi la nyan Devit yinda vak ana wuka l…®gangwuk? Tamba p…®l…®wutndi. Ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk? Nd…® wund…® kat t…®ga Godna ngay wuleilaa God kat kwunapmak kat kwil…®nja bret-nao k…®nd…®. K…®laa nd…®nogwi l…®ga n…®mba kat kwind…®, k…®ndi. God kat kwunat…®ga n…®mba m…®na k…®l…®ndi. Kwo n…®mba ana k…®l…®ndi. Njambia l…®gand…®. ndi njambia kat kai walaa k…®l…®ndi. Ndi God kat twunata n…®mba ana ndi.  
\v 5 Wun Godna vak s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan wun. Wun nj…®vwa lapman nandinya kat v…®ga l…®gowun. Wan nandinya wun kat ana v…®ga l…®gand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 NJ∆óVWA LAPMAN NANDINYAMBA JISAS K∆óTA NYAN KAT KWUNATND∆ó  
\p
\v 6 Nat nj…®vwa lapman nandinya yisolaa l…®nja ngay wuleilaa Jisas ndi kat nyaang…®t mbut…®nd…®. Wan ngaymba ta nyana taamba mak kaaland…®.  
\v 7 Ferisiagwi tamba Moses kwiya nyang…®t s…®mogwi la n…®mbo Jisas kat v…®ga l…®ndi. Nd…® kat kwunakiyand…®? E? Ana kwunakiyand…®? Waa yelav…®ka l…®ndi. Nd…® kat nj…®vwa kwuka kwunaka n…®na ngepmana njambia kat kai wandeyan nd…® kat kotmak kaligiyan…®n waa yelav…®ka l…®ndi.  
\v 8 Nd…®na maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®nja vak Jisas nd…® tamba v…®ga l…®nd…®. V…®ga l…®ga taamba mak kaala nyan kat yagwa kumba yaa al…® waa wand…®. Wand…® mala laataa yand…®.  
\v 9-10 Jisas Ferisi kat wand…®. Mbambala nj…®vwa lapman nandinya apma vat yiweyan wovuna? Kavle vat m…®na yilu? K…®ta nyan kat kwunapmat yiweyan wovuna? Nd…® kat kavle vat m…®na yilu? Waa ndi kat wagalalaa wan nyan kat wand…®. M…®na taamba sate m…®la waa wand…® mala satend…®. satend…® mala nd…®na taamba kwo l…®nd…®.  
\v 11 Ferisi nd…® kat v…®laa walaa l…®ndi. Jisas kat anda vapmba kavle yigiyan…®n waa awat sowat ngmambuga l…®ndi.   
\s1 JISAS TAAMBA V∆óLI KIYELI V∆óL∆óL∆óK N∆óMBA KAT YAGWA WAND∆ó  
\p
\v 12 Jisas God kat ngambuvat nduwiat wokend…®. Ngan k…®ta God kat ngambuga t…®nd…®.  
\v 13 Nya wokend…® mala nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat yagwa wand…®, yandi. Ndina nat n…®mba kat mand…®t s…® kwind…®. Ngwuk aposel ngwuk waa wand…®. Wanda n…®mbana sakwat tamba v…®li liyeli v…®l…®l…®k n…®mba.  
\v 14 Wan n…®mbana s…® k…®ngiyan. Nat nyan Saimon. Jisas nd…® kat mand…®t s…® wand…®. M…®n Pita m…®n waa wand…®. Nat nyan Pitana yakwa nyan Endru. Nat v…®l…®l…®k pal…® Jemsogwi Jono. Nat nyan Filip. Nat nyan Batolomyu.  
\v 15 Nat nyan Matyu. Nat nyan Tomas. Nat nyan nat k…®ta Jems. Nd…® Alfiasna nyan. Nat nyan nat kita Saimon. Nd…® ngepma ngepma yiga nat n…®mba n…®na k…®pma kat yalaa v…®ga l…®njangat kai waa ngambund…®.  
\v 16 Nat nyan Judas. Nd…®na nyaek Jems. Nat nyan Judas Iskeriot. Wan nyan ng…®ni Jisas kat vatnyavat kamwin kwind…®.   
\p
\v 17 Jisasagwi nd…®na mbaapma n…®mbo nduwimba l…®ga ndaindi. ndailaa savagu k…®pma la kavamba l…®ndi. Jisasna mbaapma n…®mba n…®ma sakwat t…®ndi. Kava kavamba l…®ga n…®mba nd…® kat v…®vat yandi. Nat n…®mba Judiamba l…®ga yandi. Nat n…®mba yelogwen kat ta n…®mba ndi kat kwunatndangat yandi.  
\v 18 Kavle waagan tavila la n…®mba kat Jisas kwunatnd…®, kwo l…®ndi.  
\v 19 Nd…® kat n…®ma sakwat n…®mba nd…®na mbang…® taamba taagavat wandi. Taamba taagandi mala nd…®na kwondu ndi kat yalaa kwunat…®nd…®.   
\s1 JISAS LAATAA NDI KAT NYAANG∆óT MBUT∆óND∆ó  
\p
\v 20 Jisas laataa nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat wand…®. ngwuk kwanda kwanda lapman t…®ngweyan apma vatna. God kwindeya apma nda aywaa klaigangwuk.   
\p
\v 21 Mbambala wund…® kat t…®ngweyan apma vatna. ng…®ni ngwula yaak taakiyand…®. Mbambala n…®ma vak yelav…®ka nglangweyan apma vatna. ng…®ni kasegiyangwuk.   
\p
\v 22 Wun God wand…®, yaa nyan wun. Wuna nyaang…®t mbukngwuk mala wukna n…®mba ngwuk kat kai waalaa nj…®ka ngwutna s…® viyesendalaa k…®klinjeyan apma vatna.  
\v 23 Ngwuk kat kavle vat yinjeya nandinya ngwuk solat as…® ngwula. Solat s…®ga ng…®ni nyinangwutwokelaa apma klaigangwuk waa yelav…®k ngwula. Ngwuk kat kavle vat yigiya n…®mbana tamba la walanga ngwak tamba la profet kat wupma kavle vat yindi.   
\p
\v 24 Ngwuk n…®ma sakwat nda l…®ga n…®mba apma vat ana nd…®. Mbambala ngwutna wenga tamba klangwuk. Ng…®ni kai.   
\p
\v 25 Yaat taat t…®ga n…®mba ngwuk apma vat ana nd…®. Ng…®ni wund…® kat t…®giyangwuk. Mbambala kasel…®ga n…®mba ngwuk apma vat ana nd…®. Ng…®ni n…®ma vat yelav…®ka nglagiyangwuk.   
\p
\v 26 Nat n…®mba ngwutna s…® kwutaa katsonjeyan apma vat ana nd…®. Ngwutna s…® katso l…®ga n…®mbana tamba la walanga ngwak tamba la kavle profetna s…® kwutaa katsondi. God waa nyaang…®t mbut…®ga profetna s…® ana katsondi.   
\p
\v 27 Ngwuk wuna mbaapma n…®mba awuk ngwula. Ngwutna maama n…®mba kat ndi kat kwunapmak n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka al…® ngwula. Ngwuk kat kai wal…®ga n…®mba ndi kat apma vat ay ngwula.  
\v 28 Ngwutna s…® kwutaa viyesenda l…®ga n…®mba kat ndina s…® kwutaa katso ngwula. Ngwuk kat kavle vat yil…®ga n…®mba ndi kat t…®ga God kat wagala ngwula.  
\v 29 K…®ta nyan ngwuk kat k…®ta naang…® k…®pmwimba viyandeyan nat naang…® agwi. K…®ta nyan ngwutna kol siot klavat wandeyan agwi ngwula. Kol siot kwilaa siot n…®mbun agwi.  
\v 30 Ngwuk kat wagala l…®ga n…®mba ndi kat agwi ngwula. K…®ta nyan ngwutnaqmba klandeyan ng…®ni wun kat awat agwi waa ke waa.  
\v 31 Nat n…®mba wun kat kan vat yinjeyan apma vatna waa yelav…®kngweyan kan yelav…®t…®ngwa vak nat n…®mba kat ay ngwula.   
\p
\v 32 Ngwuk kat woviyaguga t…®ga n…®mba ndi kat m…®na n…®ma vak yelav…®ka t…®ngweyan n…®ma vak ana nd…®. Kavle n…®mba ndino wupma yil…®gandi.  
\v 33 Ngwuk kat apma vat yil…®ga n…®mba ndi kat m…®na apma vat yingweyan n…®ma vat ana nd…®. Kavle n…®mba ndino wupma yil…®ngandi.  
\v 34 Ngwuk kat ng…®ni awat kwigiya n…®mba ndi kat m…®na kwingweyan n…®ma vat ana nd…®. Kavle n…®mba ndino wupma yil…®gandi. Kwilaa ng…®ni awat kwinja sakwat klal…®gandi.  
\v 35 Kavle n…®mba ya vak vla ngwuk key yiga. Ngwuk mand…®t apma vak yiga yet…® ngwula. Ngwuk ngwula maama n…®mba kat kwunapmat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka al…® ngwula. Ndi kat apma vat ay ngwula. Ng…®ni awat ana klaigan…®n waa yelav…®taa agwi ngwula. Wupma yingweyan ng…®ni Godnanamba apma wenga kaligangwuk. God nd…® kat s…®vu k…®lapman n…®mba ndi kat apma vat yil…®gand…®. N…®n n…®na mbang…® m…®na kwunakiyan…®n waa wal…®ga n…®mba God ndi kat apma vat yil…®ngand…®. Ngwuk wupma kai. Ngwuk njambwi nyan Godna nyangu ngwuk. Ngi kat t…®ga God nd…® kat kai wal…®ga n…®mba kat kwunat…®nda vla ngwuk kwunak ngwula.  
\v 36 Ngwutna nyaek ya vak vla ngwuk apma vak ay ngwula nat n…®mba kat.  
\v 37 Nat n…®mba kat v…®laa ndi kavle vat yindi waa walapman yingweyan God ngwuk kat v…®laa kavle vat yindi waa ana waigand…®. Nat n…®mba kat v…®laa ndi kavle n…®mba ndi waa walapman yingweyan God ngwuk kat v…®laa ndi kavle n…®mba ndi waa ana waigand…®. nat n…®mba kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®nja vak kat yelav…®tapman yingweyan God kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®ngwa vak kat yelav…®tapman yigiyand…®.  
\v 38 Nat n…®mba kat kwingweyan God ngwuk kat apma wenga kwigiyand…®. K…®ta nyan yuwi s…®k kwivat yindeyan n…®ma sakwat tulaa yiyal…®nd…®, k…®nd…®k…® ndaind…®, nat kuvuk kwutaa naangand…® maa taataa nat yuwi s…®k ndal…®nd…®, salatnd…®. God wupma kwil…®gand…®. Ngwuk nat n…®mba kat n…®ma sakwat kwingweyan God ng…®ni ngwuk kat n…®ma sakwat kwigiyand…®.   
\s1 JISAS PAPWUGA LA NYAANG∆óT TAMBANAT MBUT∆óND∆ó  
\p
\v 39 Nat m…®ni v…®lapman yila nyan nat m…®ni v…®lapman yila nyan kat taamba kwutaa yamb…® ana al…®ps…®ga v…®s…®mogwigiyand…®. V…®s…®mogwivat kalindeyan v…®li apa waangumba ndaigiyamb…®t.  
\v 40 Skul boi nd…®na tisa kat ana kwulat…®gand…®. Wan skul boi skul kwulataa nd…®na nambu tisana nambu l…®ga vla wupma l…®giyand…®.   
\p
\v 41 Ngwutna k…®ta mbaapma l…®ga k…®ta nyana m…®nimba l…®ga mat k…®s…®k v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Ngwutna m…®nimba l…®ga n…®ma k…®s…®k ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk.  
\v 42 Ngwutna k…®ta mbaapma nyan kat wal…®gangwuk. Mbaapma nyan m…®na m…®nimba l…®ga k…®s…®k klalaa yaagigiyowun. Wupma waga ngwutna m…®nimba l…®ga n…®ma k…®s…®k ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Wan yingwa vak ana nglaatnd…®. Ngwutna m…®nimba l…®ga n…®ma k…®s…®k klalaa yaagingweyan apma vak v…®ga ngwula k…®ta mbaapma nyana m…®nimba l…®ga mat k…®s…®k klalaa yaagigiyangwuk.   
\p
\v 43 Apma mi kavle mi s…®k ana kwal…®gand…®. Kavle mi apma mi s…®k ana kwal…®gand…®.  
\v 44 Mina s…®k v…®laa kan apma mi? E? Kavle mi? Waa yelav…®ka l…®gandi. Kavle n…®mbio l…®ga yamboy apma mi s…®k ana kwal…®gand…®. Apma l…®s…®k yil…®ga s…®k kavle mimba ana kwal…®gand…®.  
\v 45 Ndinyangu ndino wupma l…®gand…®. K…®ta nyan apma maawupmba yet…®giyaa nyan apma nj…®vwa kwukiyand…®. Nat k…®ta nyan kavle maawupmba yet…®giyaa nyan nd…® kavle nj…®vwa kwukiyand…®. N…®na maawupmba yelav…®taa vak vla nyaang…®t mbut…®gan…®n.   
\p
\v 46 Manda kat wuna kwundi wutapman t…®ga wun kat njambwi nyan njambwi nyan waa wal…®gangwuk. Kan kavle vatna.  
\v 47 K…®ta nyan wun kat yalaa wuna nyaang…®t wutndeyan wan nyan apma nyana. Nd…® ngay kwuta nyan vla l…®gand…®.  
\v 48 Nat k…®ta nyan ngay kwupmat yind…®. N…®mamba waangu vaa klanda kalilaa kwaal…®k tawnd…®. Sambiyangu mbal…®nd…®, ana yuvut yind…® ngay. Tagula vat t…®nd…®. Wuna nyaang…®t wut…®ga nyan k…®ngi ngay tagula ngay kwuta nyan vla l…®gand…®.  
\v 49 Nat k…®ta nyan kwaal…®k tawlapman kwo k…®pmamba ngay kwutnd…®. Sambiyangu yand…®, ngumbi kalind…®, p…®tsond…®, wan ngay kavle yind…®. Wuna nyaang…®t wutapman nyan k…®ngi kavle ya ngay kwuta nyan vla l…®gand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\c 7  
\s1 AMINA NJAMBWI NYANA NJ∆óVWA KWUTA NYAN KAT JISAS KWUNATND∆ó  
\p
\v 1 Jisas nyaang…®t ndi kat mbutaa wan kava kwagalalaa Kapaneamat yind…®.  
\v 2 Wan kavamba soldiana njambwi nyan k…®ta l…®nd…®. Nd…® soldia ndumi tambanat v…®ga l…®nd…®. Nd…®na nj…®vwa kwuta nyan yelogwen kat t…®ga kiya m…®na l…®nd…®. Njambwi soldia woviyaguga t…®nda nyana.  
\v 3 Jisas yand…®, wutaa Judana njambwi n…®mba kat wand…® mala ndi Jisas kat wagalavat yindi. Njambwi soldiana nj…®vwa kwuta nyan kat kwunap m…®la waa wavat yindi.  
\v 4 Jisas ta kava yiga nd…® kat yiga wagalaga wandi. Wan njambwi soldia apma nyana.  
\v 5 N…®n Juda n…®na n…®mba kat kwunat…®gand…®. Kan ngepmamba yisolaa l…®na ngay nd…®nai kwukna waa wandi.   
\p
\v 6 Wandi maa Jisas ndina kwupmba yind…®. Ngay ngwaymba l…®ndi. L…®vlamba ana l…®ndi, njambwi soldia nd…®na ngaymba la n…®mba kat wand…® maa Jisas kat yindi. Yilaa wandi. Soldiana njambwi nyan m…®n kat kupma wand…®. Njambwi nyan n…®ma nj…®vwa ke kwuka. Apma nyan ana wun. Ke yaa wuna kavle ngay.  
\v 7 M…®n kat v…®vak kat vaaka l…®wun. Wun mat nyan wun. Nyaang…®t wam…®n mala nj…®vwa kwut…®ga nyan apma vat t…®giyand…®.  
\v 8 Wuna njambwi n…®mba waa nyaang…®t wut…®gowun. Wuna soldia wuna nyaang…®t wut…®gandi. Ndina k…®ta nyan kat ay wowun mala yigiyand…®. Ndina nat nyan kat yagwa wowunj mala yigiyand…®. Yelogwen kwagaland…® kwo l…®giyam…®n waa wameyan nd…® kwo l…®giyand…®. V…®l…®gowun waa wand…® njambwi soldia waa nd…®na ngaymba la n…®mba mbutndi.   
\p
\v 9 Jisas wutaa ng…®paliga ndalaa nd…®na kwupmba la n…®ma sakwat n…®mba kat lungwamataa wand…®. Wan njambwi soldia maawupmba yelav…®t…®nda vat apma nglage vatna. Judana ngepma ngepma k…®ngi vat tak ana v…®l…®wun waa wand…® maa  
\v 10 Jisas kat yaa n…®mba lungwamataa yindi. Yilaa ngay wuleilaa njambwi soldiana nj…®vwa kwuta nyan kat v…®ndi. Kwo l…®nd…®, v…®ndi.   
\s1 JISAS WAND∆ó MAA KIYA NYAN LAAT∆óGAND∆ó  
\p
\v 11 Ng…®ni Jisas Nen wal…®nja ngepmat yind…®. Kapma ana yind…®. Nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba, nat n…®ma sakwat n…®mbagwi yind…®.  
\v 12 Ngepma t…®vwina suwi ngwaymba t…®ga kiya nyan kat walalaa kalindi, v…®ndi. Kiya nyana ny…®me t…®l…®. L…® talagwa. L…®la nyan k…®ta nyana. Kiya nyan. Kan ngepmana n…®ma sakwat n…®mba ndino l…®ndi.  
\v 13 Njambwi nyan l…® kat v…®laa n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka wand…®. Ke ngla waa wand…®.  
\v 14 L…® kat walaa yiga njambamba taamba taagand…®, wal…®ga n…®mba tolal…®ndi. Taamba taagalaa kiya nyan kat wand…®. Kwand…® nyan laap m…®la waa wand…® maa  
\v 15 laatnd…®. Laataa nyaang…®t ngambund…®, nd…® kat kwutaa ny…®meat kwind…®.  
\v 16 Va n…®mba ng…®paliga ndalaa vaaka l…®ndi. Ndi Godna s…® kwutaa katsoga wandi. n…®na ngepmamba n…®ma profet laatnd…®. God n…®n kat kwunapmak kat wand…® maa yand…® waa wandi.  
\v 17 Jisas ya vak va n…®mba yiga Judiagwi nat kavamba la n…®mba kat mbutseli mbutsela mbut…®ndi.   
\s1 NGU YAGU LA JON V∆óL∆óL∆óK PAL∆ó KAT WAND∆ó MAA JISAS KAT YIMB∆óT  
\p
\v 18 Jona kwupmba la n…®mba ndino mbut…®ndi Jon kat.  
\v 19 Wutaa Jon nd…®na mbaapmamba la v…®l…®l…®k pal…® kat wand…®. Jisas kat yiga wagala mb…®la. M…®n God wand…®, yaa nyan m…®n? E? Kai? Nat nyan kat kawiga v…®ga l…®gat? E? Kai? Waa wagala mb…®la waa Jon wand…® maa yimb…®t.  
\v 20 Yilaa Jisas kat wagalamb…®t. Ngu yagu l…®ga Jon an kat ay wand…® maa m…®n kat yaa. M…®n God wand…®, yaa nyan m…®n? E? Kai? Nat nyan kat kawiga v…®ga l…®gat E Kai? Waa Jisas kat wagala waa Jon an kat wand…® maa yaa waa wamb…®t.   
\p
\v 21 Walaa t…®mb…®k. T…®l…®mb…®t mala Jisas n…®ma sakwat yelogwen kat ta n…®mba kat kwunat…®nd. M…®ni v…®lapman n…®mba kat n…®ma sakwat kwunat…®nd…®, v…®l…®mb…®k.  
\v 22 V…®mb…®t mala Jisas mb…®k kat wand…®. Ay mb…®la. Yiga v…®ga wupmba vak Jon kat ambup mb…®la. M…®ni v…®lapman n…®mba kat kwunatnd…® mala v…®l…®gandi. Man k…®v…® wakna n…®mba kat Jisas kwunatnd…® mala apma vat veil…®gandi. Kawia k…®la n…®mba kat Jisas kwunatnd…® mala kwo apma vat yet…®…®gandi. Waan wutapman n…®mba kat Jisas kwunatnd…® mala waan wut…®gandi. Kiya n…®mba kat Jisas kwunatnd…® mala laat…®gandi. Kwo n…®mba kat Jisas wan apma nyaang…®t mbut…®gand…® waa yiga Jon kat ambup m…®la.  
\v 23 K…®ta nyan kwutuwa nj…®vwa v…®laa nd…® God wand…®, yaa nyana waa yelav…®tndeyan nd…® apma maawut t…®ga nyana. Wan nyan ng…®ni ana kavle yigiyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 24 Jisas wand…® mala Jon wand…®, yamb…®t v…®l…®l…®k pal…® lungwamataa yimb…®t. Yimb…®t maa Jisas wumba l…®ga n…®ma sakwat n…®mba kat v…®laa Jona s…® katsoga wand…®. Tamba ndinyangu lapman kwo kavat Jon kat v…®vat yingwuk. Tamba wan kava yingwuk, Jon mwuk viyal…®nd…®, yuvut yil…®ga suwa vla l…®ga nyana waa yelav…®ka yingwuk? Nd…® wupma ana l…®nd…®.  
\v 25 Tamba yingwa nj…®mbla Jon nd…® n…®ma sakwat ndo l…®ga apma waavwi kwusol…®ga nyana waa yelav…®ka yingwuk? Nd…® wupma ana l…®nd…®. N…®ma sakwat ndo l…®ga apma waavwi kwusol…®ga n…®mba ndi njambwi kingna ngaymba yet…®l…®gandi. Ndinyangu lapman kwo kavamba ana yet…®l…®gandi.  
\v 26 Tamba yingwa nj…®mbla Jon nd…® God waa nyaang…®t mbut…®ga profetna waa yelav…®ka yingwuk? Wupma yelav…®kngweyan wovuna. Wupma l…®nd…® Jon. Nd…® nat profetna njambwia Jon.  
\v 27 God Jon kat yelavtaa wanda nyaang…®t tamba la profet p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\li1 Awuk ngwula. Wuna nyaang…®t mbut…®ga nyan tat yigiyand…®. M…®n ng…®ni yigiyam…®n. Y…®meya yamb…® nd…® kwunakiyand…® waa God wand…®  
\p waa tamba la profet p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\v 28 Kan k…®pmamba ngu yagu l…®ga Jon nd…® kat kwulaka l…®ga nyan ana l…®gand…®. God v…®ga l…®ga n…®mba ndi kapma vat t…®gandi. Ndina mat nyan Jon kat kwalakiyand…®. Ndi kapma vat t…®gandi waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 29 Jisas mbuta nyaang…®t wuta n…®mba tat Jon ndi kat ngu yagund…®. God waa nyaang…®t mbut…®gand…® waa wandi maa ndi kat ngu yagund…®. Ngi kat t…®ga Jisas mbuta nyaang…®t wutaa apma nyaang…®tna ngiyambak wama waa wandi. Ndina nat n…®mba takis sanya klal…®ga n…®mba ndi.  
\v 30 Nat n…®mba Ferisiagwi Moses kwiya nyaang…®t s…®mogwi la n…®mbo ndi wutaa kai wandi. Tat Jon mbukna God waa nyaang…®t wupmak kat kai wandi. Jon ndi kat ana ngu yagund…®.   
\p
\v 31 Jisas wundi kavle n…®mba kat v…®laa wand…®. Yiga yet…®l…®ngwa vak vla yet…®l…®ga n…®mba ndi kat angamak waigowun. Ndi anda nda vla l…®gandi. Ngwuk kat waigowun.  
\v 32 Ndi kwand…® nyangu vla l…®gandi. Wundi kwand…® nyangu n…®nd…® ngepmamba ndaa l…®ga awat sowat wal…®gandi. Waavi wal…®n…®n, ndi wan n…®mba mbangu ana veindi waa awat sowat wal…®ndi. Nat nj…®mbla wal…®ndi. nglal…®na vak vla ndi wan n…®mba ana nglaa l…®ndi. Yet…®l…®na vak vla yet…®lapman manda kat apma yet…®l…®gandi waa awat sowat wal…®gandi. Wundi kwand…® nyangu vla t…®gangwuk.  
\v 33 Tak ngu yagula Jon yalaa k…®g…®nda n…®ma ngu k…®vak kat kai wand…®, nd…® kavle waagan tavila la nyana waa nd…® kat wangwuk.  
\v 34 Wun God wand…®, yaa nyan wun. Wun k…®g…®nda k…®ga n…®ma ngu k…®l…®wun. Wun kat v…®laa wal…®gangwuk. Nd…® n…®ma sanya klal…®ga n…®mbagwi kavle n…®mbonala yet…®l…®gand…®. Kavle vatna waa wun kat wangwuk.  
\v 35 Nat kuvuk n…®mba m…®na Jon yeta vak v…®laa yet…®luwa vak v…®laa apma vatna waa wandi. Wundi n…®mba apma maawut yelav…®ka yeta n…®mba ndi.   
\s1 KAVLE VAPMBA YIGA YETA TAAGWA JISASNA MAMBA SANDA TAAGAL∆ó  
\p
\v 36 Ferisina k…®ta nyan Jisasogwio k…®ta vak k…®g…®nda k…®vat Jisas kat nd…®na ngay wuleilaa k…®g…®nda k…®vat ndaa l…®nd…®.  
\v 37 T…®ga l…®ga kavle vapmba yiga yeta taagwa Jisas Saimon ngaymba l…®nda vat wutaa yal…®. kambapmba kwutnja awmba l…®ga sanda kwutaa yal…®.  
\v 38 Jisasna man ngand…®mba kwali mamba s…®laa nglal…®l…®. Nglal…®l…®, l…®la m…®ni ngu nd…®na mamba ndand…®. L…®la s…®vla n…®mb…® yuwi kwutaa nd…®na mamba la ngu nyangat…®. Nyangataa nd…®na man kwutaa wus…®taa sanda mamba taagal…®.   
\p
\v 39 Jisas kat wuna ngaymba nao yaa ag…® waa wanda Ferisi v…®laa maawupmba yelav…®tnd…®. Jisas Godnanamba wutaa mbut…®ga profet ana nd…®. Profet t…®gendan nd…®na mamba taagala taagwana kavle vak v…®gend…®. Ana v…®ga l…®gand…® waa maawupmba yelav…®tnd…®.   
\p
\v 40 Jisas Saimona maawupmba t…®ga vak v…®laa wand…®. Saimon m…®n kat nyaang…®tno l…®gowun waa wand…® mala Saimon wand…®. Njambwi nyan ambuk waa wand…®.  
\v 41 Jisas nd…® kat wapuseput mbut…®nd…®. V…®l…®l…®k pal…® dinau k…®ta nyananamba klamb…®t. Nat nyanadinau l00 dol kland…®. Nat nyana dinau 10 dola kland…®.  
\v 42 T…®ga l…®ga awat kwimbeya sanya kat v…®levilaa l…®mb…®t. Dinau kwiya nyan wand…®. Wun kai wowun dinau kat. Ke kwimba waa wand…®. Saimon m…®n angamak yelav…®ka l…®gam…®n. Anda nyan ke kwiga waa nyan kat n…®mamba woviyagluga l…®giyand…® waa wand…® maa Jisas wand…®. Ngiyambak wama waa wand…®.   
\li1
\v 43 N…®ma dinau ta nyan nd…® n…®mamba woviyaguga l…®giyand…®. Mat dinau ta nyan nd…® samat woviyaguga l…®giyand…® waa wand…® maa Jisas wand…®. Ngiyambak awama waa wand…®.   
\p
\v 44 Jisas wat taagwa kat v…®ga Saimon kat wand…®. Wat taagwa av…® m…®la. M…®na ngay wuleiwun mala n…®na ngepmana vapmba wuna man njangiweya ngu wun kat ana kwim…®n. L…® wupma kai. L…® l…®la m…®ni ngumba njangilaa l…®la n…®mb…® yuwimba nyangat…®.  
\v 45 M…®na ngay wuleiwun mala wun kat apma nandinya waga wuna taamba ana kwupm…®n. L…® wupma kai. Wuleiwun mala l…® n…®ma sakwat njamb…® wuna man kwutaa wus…®t…®l…®.  
\v 46 M…®na ngay wuleiwun mala n…®na ngepmana vak kat kai walaa wuna n…®mb…® yuwimba sanda ana taagam…®n. L…® wupma kai. N…®ma sakwat sanyo l…®ga sanda wuna mamba taagal…®.  
\v 47 Kapma kapma yil…®mba vatna angwa m…®n kat mbukiyowun. L…®la n…®ma sakwat kavle vat s…®l…®mbwiwun mala wun kat n…®mamba woviyanguga l…®gal…®. K…®ta nyana kavle vat sakwat ana nd…® s…®l…®mbwiwun mala wun kat samat woviyaguga t…®giyand…® waa walaa.  
\v 48 Jisas wat taagwa kat wand…®. Kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®nya vak tamba s…®s…®mbwigowun waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 49 Wand…® mala nd…®nogwinala ka n…®mba ndina maawupmba yelav…®tndi. Nd…® anda nyana apma waa. Nd…® kavle vat s…®l…®mbwil…®gand…®? Waa maawupmba yelav…®tndi.  
\v 50 Jisas wat taagwa kat wand…®. Njambwi nyan tuwa vak yelav…®t…®nyangat nyina kavle vat tamba s…®l…®mbwiwun. Yiga apma vat yet…®giyany…®n waa wand…® Jisas.   
\c 8  
\s1 JISASNA MBAAPMAMBA L∆óGA TAAGWA  
\p
\v 1 Jisas ngepma ngepma yil…®nd…®. God ndinyangu kat kwunapmak wanda apma nyaang…®t yiga mbut…®nd…®. Nd…®na mbaapmamba la tamba v…®li kiyeli v…®l…®l…®k n…®mba nd…®nogwinala yil…®ndi.  
\v 2 Nat taagwa ndino yil…®ndi. Nat taagwa tamba yelogwen kat t…®ndi. Nat taagwa tamba kavle waagan tavila la ndi taagwa. Jisas ndi kat tamba kwunatnd…®. Nat taagwana s…® maria. L…®la angwa ngepma Magdala. Tamba kavle waagan s…®la v…®li m…®na l…® kat tavilaa l…®ndi, Jisas tamba ndi kat sav…®l…®nd…®.  
\v 3 Nat taagwana s…® Joana. L…®la lana s…® Susa. Nd…® njambwi nyan Herotna nj…®vwa kwuta nyana. Nat taagwana s…® Susana. Nat taagwa ndino l…®ndi. K…®ndi lagwa Jisas kat sanya kwiga k…®g…®nda kwiga kwil…®ndi.   
\s1 JISAS PAGWULA LA NYAANG∆óT MBUT∆óND∆ó  
\p
\v 4 Ngepma ngepmamba la n…®mba Jisas kat wupmak yisolaa l…®ndi maa ndi kat pagwula la nyaang…®pmba mbut…®nd…®.  
\v 5 Mbuka wand…®. Yuwi s…®k yaagi l…®ga nyan yuwi s…®k yaagivat yind…®. Yaagiga yiga nat s…®k ava yamb…®mba ndand…®. Ndand…® mala waavi yalaa nat s…®k k…®ndi.  
\v 6 Nat s…®k kambat t…®ga kava tagu k…®pma kuvut t…®ga kavamba ndand…®. ndalaa waatnd…®. Nd…®na njingwut samat ndailaa kambapmba s…®laa kiyand…®. Njingwut ngu l…®ga kava ana ndaind…®.  
\v 7 Nat s…®k kavle yuwi s…®k t…®ga kavamba ndand…®. Kavle yuwi s…®knonala waatnd…®. Apma yuwi s…®k kavle yuwinana njingwupmba tamata kiyand…®.  
\v 8 Nat yuwi s…®k apma k…®pmamba ndand…®. Ndalaa wataa n…®man yind…®. N…®ma ava yind…®. Yilaa ava k…®ta s…®k ndumi tambanat kwand…® waa pagwula la nyaang…®t mbutaa wundi n…®mba kat wand…®. Apma maawutno l…®ga nyan nd…® kan nyaang…®tna angwa yelav…®kiyand…® waa wand…® mala nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba nd…® kat wagalandi.   
\p
\v 9 Kan nyaang…®tna angwa n…®n kat s…®maga. N…®n ana yelav…®ka l…®gan…®n waa wandi maa Jisas ndi kat s…®magaga wand…®.  
\v 10 God ndinyangu kat kwunat…®ga vatna angwa ngwuk kat sw…®magagiywoun. Nat n…®mba kat ana s…®magagiyowun. Ndi kat pagwula la nyaang…®t m…®na waigowun. Ndi maawut yelav…®tapman kwo m…®ni m…®na v…®giyandi. Maawut yelav…®tapman kwo waan m…®na wukiyandi.   
\p
\v 11 Tak mbukwa nyaang…®tna angwa kingiyan. Yaagil…®nda yuwi s…®k God waa nyaang…®tna.  
\v 12 Ava yamb…®mba l…®ga k…®pma nd…® ndinyangu vla l…®gand…®. Wundi n…®mba ndi God waa nyaang…®t wutndi. Wutaa maawupmba yelav…®tndi. Yelav…®tndi maa Seten yalaa ndina maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®nja vak kwutaa yaagil…®gand…®. Apma kupi maawupmba yelav…®ka t…®landi walaa kwutaa yaagil…®nd…® Seten.  
\v 13 Tagu kambapmba kuvuk k…®pma t…®ga kava ndinyangu vla l…®gand…®. Ndi Godna nyaang…®t wutaa apma nyaang…®tna waa yelav…®ka l…®gandi. T…®ga l…®ga nat n…®mba yaa yelav…®t…®ngwa vak kavle vatna waa wandi maa kwagalal…®gandi. Ndi tamb…® njingwut t…®ga yuwi vla l…®gandi.  
\v 14 Kavle yuwi s…®k t…®l…®ga k…®pma ndinyangu vla l…®gand…®. Ndi Godna nyaang…®t wut…®gandi. T…®ga l…®ga k…®pmana nda k…®pmana vak m…®na yelav…®ka t…®ga God waa nyaang…®t kwagala l…®gandi. Ndi God waa vapmba ana yiga yet…®l…®gandi.  
\v 15 Apma k…®pma ndinyangu vla l…®gand…®. Ndi apma maawutno l…®ga n…®mba. Ndi wutaa maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®ga God waa vapmba nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vapmba yiga yet…®l…®gandi waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 JISAS NAT NYAANG∆óT WAND∆ó  
\p
\v 16 K…®ta nyan tuway klalaa ya sag…®lalaa awmba ana naangal…®gand…®. Njamba v…®lumba taagal…®gand…®. Kwutaa katsolaa yindeya yamb…® kemband…®, v…®giyand…®.  
\v 17 Mbambala pagwuga l…®ga nyaang…®t ng…®ni aywaa wukiyandi. Mbambala pagwuga l…®ga nda ng…®ni aywaa v…®giyandi.   
\p
\v 18 Ngwuk mbutuwa nyaang…®t yigumba wuka yelav…®k ngwula. Apma maawutno l…®ga nyan nd…® yigumba wuka nyaang…®tna angwa yelav…®ka l…®giyand…®. Apma maawut tapman t…®giya nyan nd…® kwo wuka kwagalagiyand…®. Nd…®na maawupmba mand…®t mand…®t yelav…®ka l…®giyand…®. Wun apma maawupmba yelav…®ka tigowun waa t…®giyand…®. Nd…® wupma kai waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 JISASNA NY∆óMEAGWI ND∆óNA YAKWA N∆óMBA ND∆ó KAT V∆óVAT YANDI  
\p
\v 19 N…®ma sakwat n…®mba yisolaa l…®ndi maa Jisasna ny…®meagwi nd…®na yakwa n…®mba nd…® kat v…®vat yandi. Nd…® kat v…®vat wuleinjeya yamb…® kai. N…®ma sakwat n…®mba.  
\v 20 Ngi kat t…®ga Jisasna ngwaymba l…®ga n…®mba nd…® kat mbutndi. M…®na ny…®meagwi yakwa n…®mbo alagumba l…®gandi. M…®n kat v…®vat wandi waa mbutndi.  
\v 21 Mbutndi mala Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Godna nyaang…®t wutaa God waa vapmba yiga yet…®l…®ga n…®mba wuna ny…®meagwi yakwa n…®mba ndi.   
\p
\v 22 Ng…®ni nat nandinya nd…®na mbaapma n…®mbonala bot kund…®. Val…®gegat waa wand…® mala bot s…®vasagulaa val…®gendi.  
\v 23 Val…®gelaa yiga Jisas bopmba s…®ndu kwand…®. N…®ma mwuk pali kwut…®, bot ngu ngwand…®l…®nd…®. Bot lumaka ndaivat yind…®.  
\v 24 T…®ga l…®ga Jisas kat s…®vul…®laa wandi. Njambwi nyan njambwi nyan n…®n kavle yiveigan…®n wandi mala Jisas laataa mwuknagwi pali kat kai wand…®, kiyak wand…®. Ngu savagu l…®nd…®. Mwuk kai.  
\v 25 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Ngwuk manda kat vaat…®gangwuk. Njambwi nyanat tuwa vak ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk waa wand…® Jisas. Ndi vaaka l…®ga mand…®p mand…®p yelav…®ka awat sowat wal…®ndi. Wan nyan angamat t…®ga nyana. Mwukno palio nd…®nai wal…®ga vak wuka l…®gand…® waa awat sowat wal…®ndi.   
\s1 KAVLE WAAGAN TAVILA LA NYAN KAT JISAS KWUNATND∆ó  
\p
\v 26 Sak val…®gelaa Gegesa wal…®nja ngepma kawindi. Gegesa Galili nat naangamba la ngepma.  
\v 27 Kawilaa valilaa l…®nd…®. Wan ngepmana k…®ta nyan ndi kat yaa v…®nd…®. Nd…® kavle waagan tavila la nyana. Nd…® s…®p m…®na l…®nd…®. Ngaymba ana t…®l…®nd…®. Kiya n…®mba waangumba taagal…®nja kavamba yet…®l…®nd…®.  
\v 28 Jisas kat v…®l…®…® nd…®na man ngand…®mba ndalaa walega n…®ma kwundimba wand…®. Wun kat angamak yivat yam…®n. M…®n njambwi nyan Godna nyan m…®n. Wun kat kavle vat ke yiga waa walega wand…®.   
\p
\v 29 Tak Jisas kavle waagan kat sav…®l…®vat wand…® mala wan nyan wupma wand…®. Tak kan ngepma n…®mba n…®ma sakwat njamb…® nd…® kat kwutaa nd…®na man taamba senmba ngindi. Kavle waagan nd…® kat tavind…® maa sen t…®taa ndinyangu lapman kwo kavat yil…®nd…®.   
\p
\v 30 M…®na s…® angamak waigowun waa Jisas wand…® maa wand…®. Wuna s…® N…®ma Sakwat N…®mba waa wand…®. Nd…® kat kavle waagan n…®ma sakwat nd…® kat tavila l…®ndi. Ngi kat t…®ga wand…® wuna s…® N…®ma Sakwat N…®mba.  
\v 31 N…®na angwa ngepma n…®n kat ke waga yinangat waa wagalaga wandi waagan Jisas kat.   
\p
\v 32 Angwi l…®ga nduwimba l…®ga mbak ndi kat yiga taavi waa awa waa wagalandi mala ay ngwula wand…® Jisas.  
\v 33 Wand…® mala wan nyan kat kwagalalaa mbapmba yiga tavindi. Tavindi maa mbak p…®l…®ga ndaiga nguapa yindi. Yilaa ngu k…®laa kiyalaa l…®ndi.   
\p
\v 34 Mbak kat b…®ga la n…®mba v…®laa vaaka p…®l…®ga ngepma apa wuleilaa ngepma la n…®mba kat mbutndi. Ngepma yilaa kava kava yiga mbutndi.  
\v 35 Ngepmamba la n…®mba wutaa Jisas kwuta vak v…®vat yandi. Yalaa tak kavle waagan tavila la nyan Jisasna man ngand…®mba ndaal…®nd…®, v…®ndi. Waavwi kwusolaa l…®nd…®, v…®ndi. Nd…®na maawut apma vat s…®ka l…®nd…®, v…®laa vaaka l…®ndi.  
\v 36 Jisas waagan kat sav…®l…®nda vat va n…®mba ngepmamba yaa n…®mba kat mbut…®ndi.  
\v 37 T…®ga l…®ga Gegesana ngepma ngepmamba la n…®mba Jisas ndi kat kwagalalaa nat ngepmat yindangat wandi. Ndi vaaka l…®ga nat ngepmat ay waa wandi. Wandi mala Jisas ndi kat kwagalalaa nd…®na mbaapma n…®mbonala bot kulaa val…®gend…®.  
\v 38 Tak kavle waagan tavila la nyan Jisasonala yivat wand…® mala Jisas nd…® kat kai wand…®.  
\v 39 M…®na ngepma yiga god m…®n kat apma vat yinda vat m…®na ngepma n…®mba kat yiga ambup m…®la waa wand…® Jisas. Jisas wand…® mala ngepma yilaa Jisas nd…® kat apma vat yila vak nd…®na ngepma n…®mba kat aywaa mbut…®nd…®.   
\s1 JISAS KIYA KWAND∆ó LAGWA KAT KWUSELATND∆ó  
\p
\v 40 Valigelaa kawilaa valindi. valindi maa wumba ngepmamba la n…®mba Jisas kat v…®laa solat …®sga wal…®ndi. Tat nd…® kat kwo kawiga l…®ndi.  
\v 41 Yisolaa l…®nja ngay v…®ga la nyan Jisas kat yand…®. nd…®na s…® jairas. nd…® yalaa Jisasna man ngand…®mba ndalaa wand…® Jisas kat. Wuna nga y yagwa waa wand…®.  
\v 42 Nd…®na k…®ta nyan taagwa nyan yelogwen kat t…®l…®. Kiya m…®na l…®l…®. L…®la naambi tamba v…®li kiyeli v…®l…®l…®k. Jisas l…® kat kwunatndangat Jairas wand…®. Yil…®nd…® maa n…®ma sakwat n…®mba yaa yisondi. Jisasna ngwaymba yaa yisolaa l…®ndi.   
\p
\v 43 Taagwa k…®ta yal…®. L…® yelogwen kat t…®l…®. Naambi taamba …®l…®i kiyeli v…®l…®l…®k yelogwen wogwuga yet…®l…®l…®. Ana ng…®l…®nd…®. Dokta n…®ma sakwat kwunaka v…®levindi. L…®la sanya aywaa ndi kat kwil…®.  
\v 44 L…® Jisasna kwupmba yalaa nd…®na nj…®mbwi waavwi …®ny…®t…®. S…®ny…®t…® mala yelogwen wogwul…®la vat ng…®l…®nd…®.  
\v 45 S…®ny…®t…® maa Jisas lungwamaka v…®laa wuna waavwi kanda s…®ny…®ka wand…®. Wand…® mala k…®ta nyan wunay…® waa ana wand…®. Pitagwi nat mbaapma n…®mbo Jisas kat wandi. Njambwi nyan m…®na ngwaymba n…®ma sakwat n…®mba yaa yisolaa l…®gandi. M…®na mbang…® waavwi s…®ny…®ka yil…®gandi. Manda kat kanda wun kat s…®ny…®ka waa wam…®n waa wandi.  
\v 46 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. K…®ta nyan wun kat s…®ny…®tnd…®. Wuna kwondu samat ng…®l…®nd…®. V…®ga l…®gowun waa wand…®.  
\v 47 Wat taagwa wun kat v…®giyand…® waa yelav…®taa ava plaga yaa Jisasna man ngand…®mba ndalaa wal…®. Wunay…® s…®ny…®kna. S…®ny…®kwun mala wuna yelogwen ng…®l…®nd…® waa wal…® mala aywaa wutndi.  
\v 48 Jisas l…® kat wand…®. Taagwa ke vaaka. S…®ny…®kweyan kwo l…®giyowun waa yelav…®taa kwo l…®gany…®n. Apma vat t…®ga yigiyany…®n waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 49 Ngambul…®mb…®t mala yisola l…®nja ngay kat v…®ga la nyana ngaymba la k…®ta nyan yand…®. Yalaa Jairas kat wand…®. M…®na taagwa nyan tamba wundumbu yil…®. Njambwi nyan kat wagala l…®ma vak kwagala m…®la waa wand…®.  
\v 50 Jisas wutaa wand…®. Ke vaaka. Jisas l…® kat al…®ps…®ga kwunakiyand…® waa yelav…®t…®ma vak ke kwagalaga. Apma vat t…®gval…® waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 51 Jairasna ngay yandi mala nat n…®ma sakwat n…®mba ngay wuleilandi walaa Jisas kai wand…®. L…®la nyaek, ny…®me, Pita, Jems, Jon, Jisas m…®na wuleindi.  
\v 52 N…®ma maawut yelav…®ka nglal…®ndi. Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Ke ngla. Ana kiyal…®. S…®ndu kwaal…® waa wand…® mala  
\v 53 ndi nd…® kat nj…®t…®ndi. Tamba kiyal…® waa yelav…®taa nj…®t…®ndi.  
\v 54 Jisas ndi kat wand…®, alaguat wogwendi. Wogwendi mala Jisas l…® kat taambamba kwutaa wand…®. Taagwa nyan laat ny…®la wand…®.  
\v 55 Wand…® maa l…®la kait yand…®, laat…®. laat…® mala l…® kat k…®g…®nda agwi wand…® Jisas.  
\v 56 L…®la nayaek ny…®me v…®laa ng…®paliga ndamb…®t. Kan yuwa vat nat n…®mba kat ke mbuka waa wand…® Jisas.   
\c 9  
\s1 JISAS ND∆óNA MBAAPMA N∆óMBA KAT NJ∆óVWA KWIND∆ó  
\p
\v 1 Jisas nd…®na taamba v…®li kiyeli v…®l…®l…®k n…®mba kat wand…® mala yisolaa l…®ndi. Kavle waagan sav…®l…®njeya kwondu yelogwen kat ta n…®mba kat kwunatnjeya kwondu ndi kat kwind…®.  
\v 2 God ndinyangu kat yil…®nda apma vat yiga ambuk waa wand…®. Yelogwen kat ta n…®mba kat yiga kwunak ngwula waa wand…®.  
\v 3 Ndi kat nat nyaang…®t wand…®. Yingweya nj…®mbla vas…® vas…® ke kwuka. Y…®mbwi nao sanya ke klaa. Waavwi v…®l…®l…®k ke kaliga. Kwo ay.  
\v 4 Ngepma yilaa ngay wuleilaa wan ngaymba t…®ga kwaigangwuk. Nj…®vwa ng…®l…®nd…® maa wan ngay kwagalalaa yigiyangwuk. Ngay ngay ke yiga kwangwa.  
\v 5 K…®ta ngepma n…®mba ngwuk kat kai wanjeyan ndi kat kwagalalaa God ngwuk kat s…®giyand…® waga mana mbaw v…®vl…® waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 6 Wand…® mala ngepma ngepmat yindi. Yiga wan apma nyaang…®t mbuka yelogwen kat ta n…®mba kat kwunat…®ndi.   
\s1 JISAS KAT MBUTNJA NYAANG∆óT HEROT WUTND∆ó  
\p
\v 7 Njambwi nyan herot Jisas kwuta vat mbut…®ndi, wutnd…®. Wutaa mand…®p mand…®p yelav…®tnd…®. nat n…®mba Jisas kat t…®ga wandi. Jon kiyalaa laatnd…®. Nd…®nay…® waa wandi.  
\v 8 Nat n…®mba Jisas kat t…®ga wandi. Nd…® tamba la nyan Ilaija. nd…® kiyalaa laatnd…®. Nat n…®mba wandi. Nd…® kiyalaa laakna tamba la profetna waa wandi.  
\v 9 Herot wand…®. Jon kat nambu tamb kal…®kwun, kiyand…®. Mbut…®nja nyan anda nyana waa mand…®p mand…®p yelav…®tnd…®. Ngi kat t…®ga Jisas kat v…®vat wand…®.   
\s1 JISAS 5,000 N∆óMBA KAT K∆óG∆óNDA KWIND∆ó  
\p
\v 10 Jisasna mbaapma n…®mba ngepma ngepmamba yiga yet…®ga yandi. Yalaa yinja vat Jisas kat yaa mbutndi. T…®ga l…®ga Betsaida wal…®nja ngepma ngwaymba l…®ga kwo kava ndi kat kwutaa kalind…®.  
\v 11 Wan ngepmamba la n…®mba yinja vak wutaa ndina kwupmba yindi. Yandi maa Jisas ndi kat yagwa ngwula wand…®. God ndinyangu kat yil…®nda apma vat ndi kat mbut…®nd…®. Yelogwen kat ta n…®mba kat kwunatnd…®.  
\v 12 Nya samat ndaind…® kan nglaambu Jisasna mbaapmamba la tamba v…®li kiyeli v…®l…®l…®k n…®mba nd…® kat yalaa wandi. Ndi kat mbupm…®n, yigandi. Ngepma ngepmat yiga kwanjeya ngay k…®g…®nda v…®gandi. T…®l…®na kava kwo kava. Ndinyangu kai waa wandi.  
\v 13 Wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Wundi n…®mba kat k…®g…®nda agwi ngwula waa wand…®. N…®n k…®g…®nda kai. Nao tambanat kami v…®l…®l…®k m…®na l…®gand…®. Sanya yiga kwiga ndi kat k…®g…®nda klagat? Waa Jisas kat wandi.  
\v 14-15 Jisas nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat wand…®. Ndi kat wangwuk, kava kavamba ndaa l…®giyandi. Nat kava ndumi v…®li kiyeli tamba v…®li n…®mba. Wupma ndaa l…®giyandi waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 16 Jisas nao tambanat kami v…®l…®l…®k kwutaa tanamb…®taa nyinangwutnat v…®ga God kat s…®vu k…®nd…®. S…®vu k…®laa l…®mbaga l…®mbaga nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat kwil…®nd…®. Kwind…® maa nat n…®mba kat kwil…®ndi.  
\v 17 K…®ga yaat taat…®, t…®ndi. K…®lamb…®njan nao kami mbanimba naangandi. Mbani tamb v…®li kiyeli v…®l…®l…®k taat…®.   
\s1 M∆óN KRAIST M∆óN WAA PITA WAND∆ó JISAS KAT  
\p
\v 18 Nat nandinya Jisas God kat ngambul…®nd…®. Nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba nd…®nogwinala l…®ndi. Nat n…®mba kai. God kat ngambulaa ndi kat wagaland…®. Wundi n…®mba wun kat angamak yelav…®tndi. Wun kanda wun waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 19 Wand…® maa wandi. Nat n…®mba Jisas nd…® ngu yagula Jona waa wandi. Nat n…®mba Jisas nd…® Ilaija waa wandi. Nat n…®mba Jisas nd…® tamba kiyala laakna profetna waa wandi waa Jisas kat wandi.  
\v 20 Wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wagaland…®. Ngwuk angamak yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk. Wun kanda wun waa wand…®. Wand…® maa Pita nd…® kat wand…®. M…®n Kraist m…®n. M…®n god wand…®, yaa nyan m…®n waa wand…® Pita.   
\p
\v 21 Pita wand…® maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. yelav…®tingwa vak nat n…®mba kat wana mbut…®ngweya.  
\v 22 Wun Godna vak s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan wun. Ng…®ni wun kat n…®ma sakwat kavle vat yigiyandi. Judana njambwi n…®mba, God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mba, tamba Moses kwiya nyaang…®t s…®mogwi l…®ga n…®mba ndi aywaa wun kat kai waigandi. Wun kat vatnyagiyandi. Kiyalaa nandinya kuvut t…®ga laakiyowun waa Jisas ndi kat wand…®.   
\s1 APMA VAK YIGA YET∆óNEYA VAK  
\p
\v 23 Jisas nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat wand…®. K…®ta nyan wuna kwupmba yavat wandeyan nd…®na maawupmba l…®ga vak kat kai walaa wuna nj…®vwa m…®na kwuka wuna kwupmba yaigand…®. Wuna kwupmba yandeyan wun kat yinja kavle vat vla nd…® kat yigiyandi.  
\v 24 K…®ta nyan nd…®na maawupmba l…®ga vat m…®na yelav…®ka l…®ndeyan nd…® kavle yigiyand…®. K…®ta nyan kan k…®pmana kwanda kwanda nda n…®ma sakwat klalaa kavle yindeyan wan apma vatna? Kai. Apma vat ana nd…®. Kavle vatna.  
\v 25-26 K…®ta nyan wuna s…® waga wuna nyaang…®t mbupmat t…®pmwigwula yindeyan ng…®ni ngaga yaweya nj…®mbla nd…® kat wuna apma nyana waa ana waigowun. Wun Godna vak s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan wun. Ng…®ni wuna nyaek wand…® maa enselogwinala ngaga yaigowun. K…®opmamba l…®ga n…®mba njambwi nyanat tuwa vat v…®giyandi.  
\v 27 Ngwuk kat nyaang…®t k…®ta mbukiyowun. Woseka ana waigowun. Ngwutna nat n…®mba tak ana kiyaigangwuk. Tak God ndinyangu kat v…®ga l…®ndeya vak v…®laa kiyaigangwuk.   
\s1 JISASNA MBANG∆ó MAND∆óT T∆óND∆ó  
\p
\v 28 Nandinya s…®la kuvut yind…®, Jisas nduwiat wokevat wand…®. Pita, Jon, Jems ndi kat kwutaa nduwiat kalind…®.  
\v 29 Nduwi wokendi maa Jisas God kat ngambul…®nd…®. Ngambul…®nd…® maa nd…®na m…®ndama kapma vat t…®nd…®. Nd…®na waavwi n…®mbun. Nd…®na waavwi sawun m…®na l…®ga yiga kemba nda vla l…®nd…®.  
\v 30 Nat v…®l…®k pal…® kak kiyamb…®t. Nat nyan Moses. Nat nyan Ilaija. Mb…®k Jisasonala ngambul…®mb…®t.  
\v 31 Mb…®tno kemba nda vla l…®mb…®t. God wand…® maa ng…®ni Jisas Jeruslaemba weleilaa kiyandeya vak kat ngambul…®mb…®t.  
\v 32 Pitaogwi nat v…®l…®l…®k pal…® tat ndina m…®ni s…®ndu yil…®nd…®. M…®ni v…®ga kemba nda vat v…®ga Jisasogwinala l…®ga v…®l…®l…®k pal…® kat v…®ndi.  
\v 33 V…®l…®l…®k pal…® Jisas kat kwagala l…®mb…®t mala Pita Jisas kat wand…®. Njambwi nyan n…®n aywaa t…®nan apma vatna. Yisombale kuvuk kwukiyan…®n. M…®n kat k…®ta, Moses kat k…®ta, Ilaija kat k…®ta kwukiyan…®n waa maawupmba yelav…®tapman kwo wand…®  
\v 34 Pita wal…®nd…® maa mbaw ndaiga ndi kat kapmond…®. Kapmond…® mala Pitagwi nat v…®l…®l…®k pal…® vaaka l…®ndi.  
\v 35 Mbaw n…®nd…®mba kwundi yand…®, wutndi. Wan nyan wuna nyana. Nd…® kat solat s…®l…®gowun. Nd…®na nyaang…®t. Kapmond…® mala Pitagwi nat v…®l…®l…®k pal…® vaaka l…®ndi.  
\v 36 Kwundi wand…® mala mbaw wokend…®, Jisas kapmba kpma l…®nd…®, v…®ndi. T…®ga l…®ga v…®nja vat nat n…®mba kat ana mbutndi. Ng…®ni glei mbutndi.   
\s1 KAVLE WAAGAN TAVILA LA NYAN KAT JISAS KWUNATND∆ó  
\p
\v 37 Nat nandinya nduwimba l…®ga ndail…®ndi, n…®ma sakwat n…®mba Jisas kat yandi.  
\v 38 Ndina k…®ta nyan Jisas kat n…®ma kwundimba wand…®. Njambwi nyan m…®n kat wagalavat yawun. Wuna mat nyan av…® m…®la. Wuna k…®ta nyana. Nat nyangu kai.  
\v 39 Nd…® kat tavila la kavle waagan nd…® kat tavind…® maa n…®mamba walega wal…®gand…®. Kavle waagan nd…® kat viyand…® mala k…®pmamba ndalaa yuvut yiga nd…®na kwundi s…®pmia ndal…®gand…®. Kavle waagan nj…®mbla nj…®mbla wupma yil…®gand…®.  
\v 40 M…®na mbaapmamba la n…®mba kat wowun mala ndi ana al…®ps…®ga sav…®l…®ndi waa wand…® Jisas kat.   
\p
\v 41 Wand…® mala Jisas wand…®. Godna kwondu kat ana yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk. Godna kwondu al…®ps…®ga kwunakiyand…® waa maawupmba yelav…®pmak kat kai wangwuk. Ngwuk kat n…®ma sakwat nj…®mbla s…®mogwivat t…®l…®wun. S…®mogwiwa vak ana yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk waa ndi kat walaa wan nyan kat wand…®. M…®na nyan kwutaa agiya waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 42 Jisas wand…®, nd…®na ngayat kwutaa kalind…® maa kavle waagan wan mat nyan kat viyand…® mala k…®pmamba ndand…®. Jisas kavle waagan kat kai walaa wan mat nyan kat kwunataa nd…®na nyaek kat kwind…®.  
\v 43 Va n…®mba ng…®paliga ndalaa God kwondu mbund…® nyana waa wandi. Jisas kwuta vak va n…®mba aywaa wupma m…®na yl…®ndi. Ndi ng…®paliga ndaa l…®ndi mala Jisas nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat wand…®.  
\v 44 Ngwuk kat nyaang…®t k…®ta waigowun. Ngwuk yigumba awuk ngwula. Wun Godna vak s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan wun. Ng…®ni kan k…®pmana n…®mba wun kat kwutaa kavle vat yivat kaligiyandi waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 45 Mbutnda nyaang…®t ndi kwo wutndi. Nyaang…®tna angwa maawupmba ana yelav…®ka l…®ndi. Pagwula la nyaang…®t vla wutndi. Jisas kat n…®n kat nyaang…®tna angwa ambuk waa wagalavak kat vaaka l…®ndi.   
\s1 ANDA NYANA N∆óMA NYAN  
\p
\v 46 Jisasna mbaapma n…®mba awat sowat wal…®ndi. N…®na nyan anda nyana n…®ma nyan waa awat sowat wal…®ndi.  
\v 47 Jisas wal…®nja nyaang…®t ana wutnd…®. Ndina maawupmba yelav…®tnja vak v…®laa ngwaymba la mat nyan kwutaa katsolaa nd…®na ngwaymba taagand…®.  
\v 48 Taagalaa ndi kat wand…®. K…®ta nyan wun kat t…®ga kan nyan kat kwunatndeyan wun kat ay waa nyan kat kwunakiya nyan vla l…®gand…®. Ngwula k…®ta nyan wun n…®ma nyan ana wun. Wun nat n…®mba kat kwunat…®ga nyan wun waa wandeyan wan nyan ngwula n…®ma nyanat t…®giyand…®.   
\s1 JISASNA MBAAPMA N∆óMBA NAT NYAN KAT KAI WANDI  
\p
\v 49 Jisas wand…® mala Jon nd…® kat wand…®. Njambwi nyan m…®na s…® waga k…®ta nyan kavle waagan sav…®l…®nd…®, v…®n…®n. V…®laa wupma ke sav…®l…®l…®ga waa wan…®n. N…®na mbaapma nyan ana nd…®. Ngi kat t…®ga kai wan…®n waa wand…® Jon.  
\v 50 Wand…® maa Jisas wand…®. Nd…® kat kai waa manda kat wam…®n. Ana nglaatnd…®. N…®n kat kai walapman nyan n…®na k…®ta nj…®vwa nyana.   
\s1 SAMERIANA N∆óMBA JISAS KAT KAI WANDI  
\p
\v 51 God eand…® mala Jisas ny…®nangwutnat wokendeya nj…®mbla tamba ngway tologandi.  
\v 52 Nat n…®mba kat wand…® mala tata yindi. Ndi yiga Jisas s…®ndu kwandeya ngay v…®vat Sameriana k…®ta ngepma wuleindi.  
\v 53 Jisas yand…® mala kan ngepma n…®mba ngay k…®g…®nda kwivak kat kai wandi. N…®n kat kwagalalaa n…®na maama n…®mbana ngepma Jerusalem yigiyand…® waa yelav…®taa kai wandi.  
\v 54 Jisasna mbaapmamba la v…®l…®l…®k pal…® Jems, Jon kai vanja vak wutaa Jisas kat wamb…®t. Nyinangwupmba l…®ga ya kat wali maa ngaga yaa ndi kat v…®tnd…®, ng…®l…®giyandi waa wali waa Jisas kat wagalamb…®t.  
\v 55 Wamb…®t mala Jisas mb…®k kat v…®laa kai wand…®.  
\v 56 God wand…®, ndinyangu vatnyavat ana yawun. Ndi kat kwunapmak yawun waa wand…® maa wan ngepma kwagalalaa nat ngepmat yindi.   
\s1 KUVUT NYANGU JISASNA KWUPMBA YIVAT WANDI  
\p
\v 57 Ndi ava yamb…®mba wogwelaa yil…®ndi, nat k…®ta nyan yiga Jisas kat wand…®. Yimeya kava kava m…®na kwupmba yigiyowun waa wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®.  
\v 58 Kwap…®mba yet…®ga nda waangu valaa s…®ndu kwal…®gandi. Waavi n…®mbun ndina ngaymba kwal…®gandi. Wun Godna vak s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan wun s…®ndu kwaweya ngay kai waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 59 Jisas nat nyan kat v…®laa wuna kwupmba yagwa waa nd…® kat wand…®. Wand…® maa wan nyan Jisas kat wand…®. Njambwi nyan wuna nyaek wundumbu yind…®. Ngepma yilaa waangumba taagalaa yaigowun waa wand…® mala Jisas nd…® kat wand…®.  
\v 60 Wama vat ana nglaatnd…®. M…®na ngepma t…®ga kwo n…®mba ndi waangumba taagagiyandi. M…®n kai. M…®n God ndinyangu kat kwunat…®ga vak kava kava yiga mbukiyam…®n waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 61 Nat nyan Jisas kat yalaa wand…®. Njambwi nyan wuna ngaymba la n…®mba kat al…® ngwula yiga t…®gowun walaa m…®na kwupmba yaigowun waa wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®.  
\v 62 M…®n maawut v…®l…®l…®k yelav…®ka l…®ga nyan vla l…®gam…®n. Wan vak ana nglaatnd…®. Wan yelav…®t…®ma vak kwagalalapman yimeyan God v…®ga l…®ga kava ana wuleigiyam…®n.   
\c 10  
\s1 JISAS 70 N∆óMBA KAT AY WAND∆ó MAA NYAANG∆óT MBUPMAT TATA YINDI  
\p
\v 1 Ng…®ni njambwi nyan 70 n…®mba kat wand…® maa ndi ngepma ngepma v…®li v…®li yindi tata. Yingwa ngepma ng…®ni yigiyowun waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 2 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. yingweya ngepma ambugat vla l…®gand…®. N…®ma sakwat k…®l…®nja nda tamba ak wulaa l…®gand…®. S…®g…®kiya n…®mba kai. Ambugat v…®ga la njambwi nyan kat wagala ngwula. S…®g…®kiya n…®mba kat ay wand…®, yigiyandi waa wagala ngwula.   
\p
\v 3 Ngwutno ay ngwula. N…®ma waala mat sip sip kat val…®njeya vak vla yingweya ngepma n…®mba ngwuk kat kavle vat yigiyandi.  
\v 4 yimbwi mand…®t su ke kalingwa. Ava yamb…® yiga v…®ngweya n…®mba kat ke ngambuga. V…®ga kwagalalaa kwiyatapman aymba ngwuk.  
\v 5 Wuna ngay yagwa waa k…®ta nyan wandeyan ngwuk apma vak al…® ngwula walaa wulei.  
\v 6 Wuleingwa ngaymba la n…®mba ngwuk kat apma vat yinjeyan ndi kat apma vat al…® ngwula waa wangwa vak ndinamba t…®giyand…®. Ngwuk kat kavle vat yinjeyan wangwa nyaang…®t ndinamba ana l…®giyand…®. Wan nyaang…®t lungwamataa ngwula lak yaigand…®.  
\v 7 Wuleingwa ngaymba al…® ngwula. Ngay ngay ke yiga. Wuleingwa ngaymba l…®ga ngwuk kat kwil…®nja k…®g…®nda ngu ag…® ngwula. ngwuk nj…®vwa kwut…®ga n…®mba ngwuk. Ngwuk kat kwil…®njeya k…®g…®nda ngwula wenga vla l…®gand…®.   
\p
\v 8 Ngepma wuleilaa ngwuk kat kwil…®nja k…®g…®nda ag…® ngwula.  
\v 9 Ndina ngepmana yelogwen kat ta n…®mba kat kwunak ngwula. God ngwuk kat kwunatndeya vak tamba ngway tologand…® waa ndi kat ambuk.  
\v 10 K…®ta ngepma wuleingwuk, ngwuk kat kai wanjeyan ndina ngepma kwagala ngwula.  
\v 11 Ngepma alagumba t…®ga ngwutna man mbaw v…®vl…®laa ndi kat awamba. ngwuk kavle vat yingwuk. God ngwuk kat kwuntndeya vak ngwuk kat tamba ngway tologand…®, kai wangwuk. Ngi kat t…®ga n…®na man mbaw v…®vl…®l…®gan…®n waa awa.  
\v 12 Ng…®ni God kavle n…®mba kat s…®giya nandinya ng…®ni wan ngepma kavle yigiyand…®. Tamba la kavle vat ta ngepma Sodom wal…®nja ngepma kavle vat ya vak kat wan ngepma kavle vat yindeya vak kwulakiyand…®. Ngwuk kat woseka ana wowun.   
\p
\v 13 Nat ngepma v…®l…®l…®k k…®ngivat t…®gand…®. Kan ngepma v…®l…®l…®k Korasinogwio Betsaido. Kan ngepma n…®mba n…®ma sakwat n…®ma nj…®vwa kwutuwa nj…®vwa v…®laa nyaang…®t wupmak kat kai wandi. Nat ngepma v…®l…®l…®k Taiaogwio Saidono wuleilaa kwukwa n…®ma nj…®vwa kwukewan ndi nyaang…®t wukendi. Nyaang…®t wutaa kavle maawut kwagalalaa mand…®t kupi maawut yelav…®ka l…®gendi. N…®n tak n…®mamba kavle vat yin…®n waa yelav…®ka l…®gendi.  
\v 14 Ng…®ni God kavle n…®mba kat s…®giya nandinya Taiaogwio Saidona ngepma n…®mba kat n…®mamba ana s…®giyand…®. Korasinogwio Betsaidana ngepma n…®mba kat n…®mamba s…®giyand…®.  
\v 15 Kapaneam wal…®nja ngepma n…®mba ndino wupma. Ndi kupma yelav…®t…®gandi. N…®n apma vat t…®ga n…®mba n…®n. N…®n nyinangwut t…®ga n…®mba vla l…®gan…®n God ndi kat v…®laa kavle n…®mba ngwuk waa walaa ndi kat s…®laa ya v…®t…®ga kavamba taagagiyandi waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 16 Jisas walaa wundi 70 n…®mba kat wand…®. Ngwutna nyaang…®t wut…®ga n…®mba wuna nyaang…®t wut…®ga n…®mba vla l…®gandi. Wun kat kai wal…®ga n…®mba wun kat ay waa nyan kat kai wal…®ga n…®mba vla l…®gandi. Aywaa k…®ta vatna.   
\s1 70 N∆óMBA YILAA YANDI  
\p
\v 17 70 n…®mba yalaa solat s…®ga Jisas kat wandi. Njambwi nyan m…®na s…® waga kavle waagan sav…®l…®l…®n…®n, yindi. N…®na nyaang…®t wutndi waa wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®.  
\v 18 Seten kat kwulat…®ngwa vat v…®ga l…®gowun. Nd…® mbambala nyinangwupmba l…®ga njambwi nyan ana nd…®. Nd…® tamba ndaiga kavle kavamba l…®gand…®, v…®wun.  
\v 19 Ngwuk kat kwondu kwiwun. Kavle kamboy ngwuk kat val…®leyan ana kavle yigiyangwuk. Ngwuk kat kwiwa kwondu v…®ga l…®giyand…®. Seten kat kwulakiyangwuk. Nat kavle nda ana ngwuk kat kavle yigiyand…®. Ngwuk kat kwiwa kwondu v…®ga l…®giyand…®.  
\v 20 Kavle waagan ngwutna nyaang…®t wutnja vak kat yelav…®ka ke n…®mamba solat s…®ga. Wan n…®ma nda ana nd…®. nyinangwupmba l…®ga njambwi nyan n…®na s…® p…®l…®wutaa nyinangwutnat kaligiyand…® waa yelav…®ka n…®mamba solat s…®ga al…® ngwula. Wan n…®ma nda.   
\s1 JISAS ND∆óNA NYAEK KAT NGAMBUL∆óND∆ó  
\p
\v 21 T…®ga l…®ga Godna waagan Jisasna maawupmba ngwand…®l…®nd…® maa solat s…®ga nyaek kat wand…®. Nyaek wam…®n maa mbutuwa nyaang…®t kan k…®pmana nambuo l…®ga n…®mba wuka kwagala l…®gandi. Ana yelav…®t…®gandi. Wam…®n mala kwo n…®mba ndi nambu lapman n…®mba yelav…®t…®gandi. Yima vat apma vatna.  
\v 22 Nyaek, kwutuwa nj…®vwam…®namba aywaa klawun. Wuna angwa vat kan k…®pmana n…®mba ana v…®ga l…®gandi. M…®n m…®na nyana angwa vak v…®ga l…®gam…®n. Kan k…®pmana n…®mba m…®na angwa vak ana v…®ga l…®gandi. Wun k…®t nyan m…®na wuna nyaekna angwa vak v…®ga l…®gowun. M…®na angwa vak s…®mogwi luwa n…®mba ndino v…®ga l…®gandi waa nyaek kat walaa  
\v 23 nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat wand…®. Nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat ana pagwund…®. Nat kwo n…®mba kat pagwuga wand…®. V…®l…®ngwa vat apma vatna. V…®laa apma vat t…®l…®gangwuk.  
\v 24 Tamba la profet tamba la njambwi king v…®l…®ngwa vat ndi tamba vivat wandi. Ndi ana v…®ndi. Wut…®ngwa nyaang…®t ndi tamba wupmat wandi. Ana wutndi waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 SAMERIANA NYAN ND∆óNA MAAMA NYAN KAT KWUNATND∆ó  
\p
\v 25 Ndina ngepma vak v…®ga la nyan k…®ta Jisas apma nyaang…®t mbukiyand…®? E? Kavle nyaang…®t mbukiyand…®? Waa yelav…®taa Jisas kat k…®ta nyaang…®t wagaland…®. S…®mogwi l…®ga nyan, anda apma nj…®vwa kwutaa nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vak yiga yet…®weya vak klaigowun waa wagaland…®.  
\v 26 Wagaland…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Tamba Moses kwiya nyaang…®t angamak p…®l…®wutnd…®. Tamba v…®m…®n? E? Ana v…®m…®n? Waa wand…® maa wan nyan wand…®.  
\v 27 Tamba v…®wun. Kupma p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\li1 Ngwutna njambwi nyan Godna. Nd…® kat maawupmba yelav…®ka al…® ngwula. Nd…® kat solat as…® ngwula. Nd…® kat woviyaguga al…® ngwula. Avla ngwutna mbangi kwunat…®ngwa vak vla nat n…®mba kat wupma kwunak ngwula  
\p waa tamba p…®l…®wutnd…® Moses waa wand…® wan nyan.  
\v 28 Wand…® maa ngiyambak wama. Wupma yimeyan apma vat t…®giyam…®n waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 29 Kwo wagaland…® waa yelav…®pmband…® walaa nat nyaang…®t Jisas kat wagaland…®. Kwunakweya n…®mba anda n…®mba ndi waa wagaland…®.  
\v 30 Jisas wutaa nd…® kat wapuseput mbutnd…®. Judana k…®ta nyan Jerusalem kwagalalaa Jerikoat ndaind…®. Yil…®nd…® mala s…®kwut…®ga n…®mba nd…® kat yaa v…®laa nd…® kat viyaga nd…®na nda nd…®na waavwi s…®kwuka klalaa yindi. Nd…® kiya m…®na l…®nd…®.  
\v 31 T…®ga l…®ga God kat kwunt…®ga k…®ta nyan wan yamb…®mba yand…®. Yalaa nd…® kat v…®laa yamb…®na nat naang…®mba yind…®.  
\v 32 T…®ga l…®ga nat nyan Livaina yelang…® nyan wan yamb…®mba yand…®. Yalaa nd…® kat v…®laa yamb…®na nat naang…®mba yind…®.   
\p
\v 33 T…®ga l…®ga Sameriana k…®ta nyan wan yamb…®mba yand…®. Sameriana n…®mba ndi Judana maama n…®mba ndi. Viyanja Juda v…®laa nd…® kat maawut yelav…®ka l…®nd…®.  
\v 34 Nd…® kat yaa v…®laa nd…® kat viyanja nglaw marasin taagalaa waavwimba ngind…®. Ngilaa nd…®no donkina mbunimba nd…® kat kwutaa wokega taagalaa kalind…®. Haus pasindia kalind…®. Wan ngan nd…® kat v…®ga l…®nd…®.  
\v 35 Nat ngambi haus pasindia v…®ga la nyan kat dola v…®l…®l…®k kwilaa wand…®. Nd…® kat kwunaka v…®ga l…®giyam…®n. Nd…® kat kwunapmak nat sanya yaagimeyan yilaa yalaa m…®n kat awat kwigiyowun waa walaa yind…®. Waa Jisas wapuseput mbutaa wan nyan kat wand…®.   
\p
\v 36 Wan wapuseput mbukwa kuvut n…®mbana anda nyan nd…®na nda s…®kwukna nyan kat apma vat yind…® waa Jisas wagaland…® maa wan nyan wand…®.  
\v 37 Nd…® kat kunakna nyan apma vat ya nyana waa wand…® maa m…®n wupma yiga yet…® m…®la waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 MATA MARIA YAKWA LAGWA MB∆óT  
\p
\v 38 Yiga l…®ga ngepma k…®ta wuleindi. Wan ngepmana k…®ta lagwa Jisas kat l…®la ngayat yagwa walaa kalil…®. L…®la s…® Mata.  
\v 39 L…®la yakwa lagwana s…® Maria. Jisasngay wuleilaa nyaang…®t ngambul…®nd…®, Maria nd…®na man ngand…®mba ndaa l…®ga wut…®.  
\v 40 Mata ana kwo l…®l…®. L…® n…®mba sakwat nj…®vwa kwuka k…®g…®nda kwut…®l…®. K…®g…®nda kwuka Jisas kat yalaa wal…®. Njambwi nyan wun nj…®vwa kapma kwut…®gowun. Ana v…®ga l…®gam…®n? Wuna yakwa lagwa kat wam…®n mala yalaa wunagwinala nj…®vwa kwukiyal…® waa wal…® mata.  
\v 41 Wal…® maa Jisas wand…®. Mata n…®ma sakwat mand…®p mand…®p nda kat yelav…®ka l…®gany…®n.  
\v 42 Apma nda k…®ta ana yelav…®ka l…®gany…®n. Kan apma nda kat yelav…®ka l…®gal…®. Wuna nyaang…®t wupmak wal…®. L…® kat ke kai waa waa wand…® Jisas.   
\c 11  
\s1 GOD KAT NGAMBUNEYA VAT  
\p
\v 1 Jisas t…®ga God kat ngmabund…®. Tamba God kat ngambund…®, nd…®na mbaapma nyan nd…® kat yalaa wand…®. Njambwi nyan tat ngu yagula Jon nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat God kat ngambunjeya vat s…®mogwind…®. M…®no n…®n kat s…®mogwigiyam…®n waa wand…® maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®.  
\v 2 God kat ngambungweya nj…®mbla kupma awa.  
\li1 ‚ÄúNyaek, M…®na s…® kwutaa katsol…®gan…®n. Ng…®ni kan k…®pmamba l…®ga nimba  
\li1 kat v…®ga l…®m…®n maa m…®na kwundi wuka l…®njeyan apma vatna. Wan nj…®mbla kat kawiga l…®gan…®n.   
\li1
\v 3 Nandinya nandinya k…®neya k…®g…®nda agwi m…®la.   
\li1
\v 4 M…®n kat kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®neya vak ke kwuka. Kwagala. N…®no nat n…®mba n…®n kat kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®ngjeya vak ana kwut…®gan…®n. Kwagala l…®gan…®n. Kavle vat n…®n kat yaa kwutnad…® walaa wan…®n.‚Äù  
\p Waa wupma god kat ngambu ngwula.   
\p
\v 5-6 K…®ta nyana al…® nyan n…®nd…® ngan n…®ma ngan yand…®. Yaa nyan kat kwindeya nao k…®g…®nda kai. Ngi kat t…®ga nd…®na ngay kwagalalaa nat al…® nyana ngay k…®g…®nda kat y…®nd…®. Yilaa alagumba l…®ga laataa wand…®. Al…® nyan nat nyan wuna ngay yand…®. Nd…® kat kwiweya nao k…®g…®nda kai. Wungi kat yawun. Wun kat agwi wand…®.  
\v 7 Ngaymba l…®ga nyan wand…®. Manda kat wun kat n…®ma nj…®vwa kwim…®n. Ngayna mbaapmo tamba t…®v…®wun. Wun wuna nyan apma s…®ndu kwaan…®n. M…®n kat nao k…®g…®nda kwivat ana al…®ps…®ga laakiyowun waa wand…®.  
\v 8 Ngwuk kat wowun wand…® Jisas. Ngaymba ta nyan wuna al…® nyana yaa waa yelav…®taa ana laakiyand…®. K…®g…®nda kat yaa nyan nj…®mbla nj…®mbla wagala l…®ndeyan ngaymba la nyan nd…® laakiyand…®. Laataa nd…® kat nao k…®g…®nda kwigiyand…®.  
\v 9 Ngwuk kat wowun. God kat wagalangwuk maa kwigiyand…®. Nd…® kat kwaka wagalangweyan kwigiyand…®. Ngay mbapmo taamba viyal…®ga nyan vla nd…® kat wagalangweyan kwigiyand…®.  
\v 10 Wagalal…®ga nyan nd…® klaigand…®. Kwuka wagala l…®ga nyan klaigand…®. Ngay mbapmo taamba viyal…®ga nyan vla wagala l…®ga nyan nd…® klaigand…®.   
\p
\v 11 Ngwutna mat nyan k…®g…®nda kat wagalandeyan nd…® kat yuvut kamboykwigiyangwuk? Kai. Wupma ana kwigiyangwuk.  
\v 12 Nyaaga mband…® kat wagalandeyan nd…® kat m…®nj…® kwagwula kwigiyangwuk? Kai. Wupma ana kwigiyangwuk.  
\v 13 N…®n k…®pma l…®ga n…®mba apma maawut yelav…®ka l…®ga n…®mba ana n…®n. N…®na nyangu n…®n kat wagalanjeyan ndi kat s…®mblan ana kwil…®gan…®n. Apma vat kwil…®gan…®n. Ngwutna ny…®nangwupmba l…®ga nyaek nd…® apma maawut yelav…®ka t…®ga nyana. Nd…® kat wagalangweyan ngwuk kat apma nglei vat kwigiyand…®. Ngwuk kat nd…®na waagan kwigiyand…®.   
\s1 JISASO BIELSEBULO KITA NJ∆óVWA KWUT∆óMB∆óT WAA WANDI  
\p
\v 14 Jisas t…®gat kulumata ta kavle waagan sav…®l…®nd…® mala tavila la nyan nyaang…®t ngambund…®. Va n…®mba mand…®p mand…®p yelav…®tndi.  
\v 15 Nat n…®mba yelav…®ka wandi. Kavle njambwi nyan Seten waa Bielebul wal…®na nyan Jisas kat kwondu kwind…® maa kavle waagan kat sav…®l…®gand…® waa wandi.  
\v 16 Nat n…®mba Jisas kat yelav…®tndi. Nd…® God wand…®, nyinangwupmba t…®ga yaa nyana? E? Kai? Waa yelav…®taa nd…® kat wandi. M…®n n…®ma nj…®vwa kwupm…®n, yama kava yelav…®ka t…®giyan…®n waa wandi.  
\v 17 Maawupmba yelav…®t…®nja vak Jisas v…®laa ndi kat wand…®. K…®ta kavana n…®mba mbaapma v…®l…®l…®k s…®laa awat sowat s…®ga viyanjeyan ndi kavle yigiyandi. Ng…®l…®giyandi.  
\v 18 Setena n…®mba k…®ta vatna. Mbaapma v…®l…®l…®k s…®laa awat sowat s…®ga viyanjeyan ndi kavle yigiyandi. Bielsebul nd…® kat kwondu kwind…® maa kavle waagan sav…®l…®l…®gand…® waa wangwa nyaang…®t ana nglaatnd…®.  
\v 19 Bielsebul nd…® kat kwondu kwind…® maa kavle waagan kat sav…®lgand…® waa wun kat wal…®gangwuk. Ngwutna ngepmana nat n…®mba ndino sv…®l…®l…®gandi. N…®n God kwiya kwondumba sav…®l…®l…®ngan…®n waa wal…®ngandi. Wuno n…®mbun.  
\v 20 God n…®n nat kwunakiya vat tamba ngway tologand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga God wun kat kwondu kwind…® maa sav…®l…®l…®gowun.   
\p
\v 21 Kao l…®ga nyan n…®mba nda kwutaa nd…®na ngayna kwanda kwanda nda v…®ga l…®ndeyan wan nda kwo l…®giyand…®.  
\v 22 Nat kao mbund…® nyan yandeyan nd…® kat kwulataa nd…®na ngayna nda s…®kwuka kwutaa kalilaa nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat kansaga kwigiyand…®. Nd…®na n…®mbi nda aywaa kwutaa kaligiyand…®. Tak wan nyan yelav…®tnd…®. Kwuta luwa n…®mbi nda wuna nda kat v…®ga l…®gand…® waa yelav…®tnd…®.   
\p
\v 23 Wunogwinala k…®ta nj…®vwa kwutapman nyan wun kat kai wal…®ga nyana. Wunogwinala ndinyangu kat kwutaa wuna mbaapmamba taagalapman nyan nd…® kapma mbaapma nyana. Wuna mbaapmamba la n…®mba kat kwutaa kapma mbaapmamba taagavat t…®gand…®.   
\p
\v 24 Kavle waagan ndu nyan kat kwagalalaa kavle kava m…®na yiga yet…®giyand…®. Sindu kwandeya apma kava kwatevilaa l…®giyand…®. T…®ga l…®ga tak yetiwa nyan kat lungwamataa yigiyowun waa waigand…®.  
\v 25 Wupma walaa yilaa tavigiyand…®. Wan nyan maawut ngay yaguga kwunatnja vla l…®gand…®.  
\v 26 Ngi kat t…®ga nat kavle waagan s…®la v…®li kwut…® mala ndi aywaa taviga nd…®na maawupmba wuleigiyandi. Nat s…®lav…®li kavle waagana kavle vat kat kwulat…®gandi. Tavinja nyan tat samat kavle vat t…®nd…®. Ng…®ni aywaa tavindi mala wan nyan n…®mamba kavle t…®giyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 SOLAT S∆óNEYA VAT  
\p
\v 27 Jisas ngambul…®nd…®, n…®ma sakwat n…®mba wuka l…®ndi. T…®ga l…®ga taagwa k…®ta n…®ma kwundimba Jisas kat walega wal…®. M…®n kat kwukna taagwa m…®n kat mwunya ngu kwiya taagwa apma vat t…®ga tagwat waa wal…® maa Jisas wand…®.  
\v 28 Wupma kai. God waa nyaang…®t wutaa wan nyaang…®pmba yiga yet…®l…®ga n…®mba ndi apma ndu apma taagwa ndi waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 N∆óMA NJ∆óVWA AGWUT WAA JISAS KAT WANDI  
\p
\v 29 N…®ma sakwat n…®mba yisolaa l…®ndi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Kan mbambala glei l…®ga n…®mga ndi kavle n…®mba ndi. N…®ma nj…®vwa ana kwukiyowun. Tamba Jona God waa nyaang…®t mbutnda vla mbukiyowun.  
\v 30 Tamba Jona God waa vak Nineva wal…®nja ngepma n…®mba kat mbutnd…®. Wuno mbambala nglei l…®ga n…®mba kat God waa vak mbukiyowun.  
\v 31 Tamba kambangwapmba la njambwi kwin n…®na tamba la kin Solomon nd…® kat v…®vat yal…®. Nd…® apma nambuo l…®ga nyana waa wutaa yal…®. Mbambala wun yawun. Wun Solomon kat kwulat…®gowun. Wun njambwi nyan wun. Nd…® mat nyan nd…®. Mbambala t…®ga n…®mba njambwi nyanat tuwa vat ana yelav…®ka v…®ga l…®gandi. Ng…®ni yaiga nandinya kambangwapmba la njambwi kwin kavle vat yingwuk waa ngwuk kat waigal…®.  
\v 32 Nineva wal…®nja ngepmamba tamba la n…®mba ndino ng…®ni yaiga nj…®mbla ngwuk kavle vat yingwuk waa ngwuk kat waigandi. Ndi Jona mbuta nyaang…®t wutaa kavle maawut kwagalalaa mand…®pkupi maawupmba l…®ndi. Ngwuk lai. Wun Jona kat kwulat…®gowun. Wun njambwi nyan wun. Nd…® mat nyana. Mbutuwa nyaang…®t ana wukngwuk.   
\p
\v 33 K…®ta nyan lam sag…®lalaa ana pagwugiyand…®. Awmba ana naangagiyand…®. Njamb…®mba taagand…® mala ngay wuleigiyaa n…®mba v…®giyandi.  
\v 34 N…®no wupma. N…®na maawut lam vla l…®gand…®. N…®na maawut kavle vat yelav…®ka l…®neyan kavle vat l…®giyan…®n. Kulun walal…®ga kavamba man veila l…®ga nyan vla l…®giyan…®n.  
\v 35 Ngutna maawut samat apma vat yelav…®ka t…®gangwuk. Ke kwagalangwa wan vak.  
\v 36 Apma maawut yelav…®ka apma vat m…®na yiga yet…®ngweyan n…®mamba kemba l…®ga lam vla yet…®giyangwuk.   
\s1 FERISI KAVLE VATNA YET∆óL∆óNJA  
\p
\v 37 Jisas ngambul…®nd…® mala Ferisi k…®ta wand…®. Wuna ngaymba nao yaa ag…® wand…®. Wand…® maa ngay wuleilaa k…®nd…®.  
\v 38 Jisas nd…®na taamba ngu njangi lapman kwo k…®l…®nd…®. Ferisi v…®laa ng…®pal…®ga ndand…®.  
\v 39 Maawupmba yelav…®t…®nda vak v…®laa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Ngwuk Ferisi alagu mbang…® kat m…®na yelav…®t…®gangwuk. Angwula maawut ana yelav…®t…®gangwuk. Ngwuk kap plet n…®ma nj…®vwa kwuka ngu njangi l…®gangwuk. Ngwutna maawut kavle vak n…®ma sakwat t…®gand…®.  
\v 40 God mbang…® m…®na ana kwutnd…®. Maawut n…®mbun kwutnd…®. Ngwuk manda kat kavle vat yelav…®ka l…®ga ngwuk.  
\v 41 Ngwutna kwanda kwanda nda sanya lapman n…®mba kat kwingweyan apma vat t…®giyangwuk.   
\p
\v 42 Ngwuk Ferisi ngwuk kat miwa yiga l…®gowun. Ngwuk kavle yigiyangwuk. Ngwutna kamwin, ngwutna lomba, ngwutna nyangwa mbaapma tamba v…®li taagalaa God kat k…®ta mbaapma kwil…®gangwuk. Wan n…®ma nj…®vwa kwut…®ngwa. Ngwuk Godna apma vak kwagalalaa nd…® kat ana woviyaguga l…®gangwuk. God kat kwil…®ngwa vat kavle vat ana nd…®. God kat yelav…®tapman yet…®lingwa vak kavle vatna.   
\p
\v 43 Ngwuk Ferisi ngwuk kat miwa yiga l…®gowun. Ngwuk kavle yigiyangwuk. Yisolaa l…®nja ngay wuleilaa njambwi n…®mbana t…®g…®pmba ndaa l…®vat wal…®gangwuk. Nat n…®mba ngwuk kat ngepmamba v…®laa njambwi n…®mba ndi waa wanjangat wal…®gangwuk. Kavle vatna.  
\v 44 Ngwuk Ferisi ngwuk kat miwa yiga l…®gowun. Ngwuk tamba Moses kwiya nyaang…®t s…®mogwi l…®ga n…®mba ngwutno ngwuk kat miwa yiga l…®gowun. Ngwuk kavle yigiyangwuk. Ngwuk pagwunja mat mat vla l…®gangwuk. Mat mat tagumba veil…®gan…®n waa ana nat n…®mba yelav…®t…®gandi waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 45 Jisas wal…®nd…® maa ndina ngepma vat kat v…®ga la k…®ta nyan Jisas kat wand…®. S…®mogwi l…®ga nyan Ferisi kat kai wama nyaang…®t n…®no n…®na lak yal…®ngand…®. Wupma ana v…®ga l…®gam…®n? Waa wand…® mala Jisas nd…® kat wand…®.  
\v 46 Ngwutno ngwuk kat miwa yil…®gowun. Kavle yigiyangwuk. Ngwuk nat n…®mba kat n…®ma sakwat njambiya taagangwuk maa ndi n…®ma sakwat njsvwa kwut…®gandi. Ndi kat anan yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk. N…®ma sakwat nj…®vwa kwupandi walaa ndi kat nat njambiya ana taakagiyan…®n waa ana wal…®gangwuk.   
\p
\v 47 Ngwuk kat miwa yil…®gowun. Kavle yigiyangwuk. Ngwutna tamba la ngwak walanga God waa nyaang…®t mbuta n…®mba kat vatnyandi. Ngwuk ngwutnay…® profetna mat mat yelagal…®gangwuk. Ngwutna ngwak walagana maawut klalaa l…®gangwuk.  
\v 48 Ngwutna ngwak walanga profet kat vatnyanja vat apma vatna waa yelav…®t…®gangwuk. Vatnyandi maa ngwut mat mat yelagal…®gangwuk. Yelagalingwa vak v…®laa vatnyanja vat apma vatna waa yelav…®t…®ngwa vak v…®ga l…®gan…®n.   
\p
\v 49 Tamba yinja vak kat God tamba wand…®. ‚ÄúWuna nyaang…®t waiga profet aposel wowun maa yigiyandi. Profetna aposelna nat n…®mba kat vatnyagiyandi. Nat n…®mba kat nj…®ka waga waigandi‚Äù waa tamba wand…® God.  
\v 50 Tamba la profet vatnyanja vatna nglambi ngwutnamba t…®giyand…®.  
\v 51 Njambwi la nyan Ebel nd…® kat tat vatnyandi. Vatnyaga yiga ng…®ni Sekaraia kat vatnyandi. Nd…® Godna ngay wuleilaa God kat kwunat…®nja njamb…®mba ngwaymba l…®ga t…®nd…®, vatnyandi. Ndi kat vatnyanja vatna nglambi aywaa ngwutnamba tigiyand…®.   
\p
\v 52 Ngwuk njambia taagala l…®ga n…®mba ngwuk kat miwa yiga ligowun. Kavle yigiyangwuk. Apma vat klanjeya yamb…® ngwuk t…®v…®ngwuk. Wan apma vat ngwuk ana klangwuk. Nat n…®mba klavat yinjangat kai wangwukk.   
\p
\v 53 Jisas wal…®nd…® maa tamba Moses kwiya nyaang…®t s…®mogwi la n…®mbagwi Ferisio nd…® kat n…®ma sakwat nyaang…®t wagalandi.  
\v 54 Kavle nyaang…®t n…®n kat wandeyan nd…® kat kotmak kaligiyan…®n waa yelav…®ka n…®ma sakwat nyaang…®t wagalandi.   
\c 12  
\s1 FERISINA KAVLE VAK KAT V∆óGA L∆óGIYANGWUK  
\p
\v 1 N…®ma nglei sakwat n…®mba k…®ta kavamba yisolaa l…®ndi. Ngway ngwaymba l…®ga al…® man veiga l…®ndi. T…®ga l…®ga Jisas nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat wand…®. Wanda nyaang…®t nat n…®mba wutndi. Ferisina kavle vak v…®ga al…® ngwula. Ndina maawupmba t…®ga kavle vat pagwulaa kwo yet…®l…®gandi. Ngwuk wupma ke yiga.  
\v 2 Mbambala pagwunja nda ng…®ni kapmba l…®giyand…®. Ng…®ni aywaa v…®giyandi.  
\v 3 Mbambala pagwuga waigowun waa wangwa nyaang…®t ng…®ni aywaa wukiyandi. K…®ta nyan kat m…®na waigowun waa wangwa nyaang…®t ng…®ni aywaa wukiyandi.   
\s1 VAKNGWEYA NYAN  
\p
\v 4 Wuna al…® n…®mba ngwuk yigumba awuk ngwula. Ndu nyan kat kwo vatnya m…®na t…®ga n…®mba kat ke vakngwa.  
\v 5 Vakngweya nyan waigowun. Ndu nyan kat vatnyalaa ya v…®t…®ga kavamba taagal…®ga nyan kat vaaka al…® ngwula.   
\s1 GOD N∆óN KAT APMA VAT V∆óGA L∆óGAND∆ó  
\p
\v 6 K…®l…®nja mak waavi tambanat sen moni v…®l…®l…®k wenga kwiga klal…®gandi. God wundi mat waavi kat ana maawut t…®v…®l…®gand…®.  
\v 7 Ngwutno ngwutna n…®mb…® yuwina sakwat God v…®ga l…®gand…®. Ngwuk ke n…®mamba yelav…®ka l…®ngwa. Ngwuk mat waavi kat kwulat…®gangwuk.   
\s1 NAT N∆óMBA KAT GODNA NYAANG∆óT MBUTNEYA VAK  
\p
\v 8 Ngwuk kat wowun. Jisas Godna vak s…®mogwi l…®ga nyana waa nat n…®mba kat wangweyan ng…®ni God t…®ga kava wokelaa ensel kat waigowun. Ndi wuna nyangu ndi waa ngwuk kat t…®ga waigowun.  
\v 9 Nat n…®mba wun kat kai vanja nat n…®mba kat mbutnjeyan ng…®ni God t…®ga kava wokelaa ensel kat ndina s…® waga kai waigowun.   
\p
\v 10 Wun Godna vat s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan wun. K…®ta nyan wun kat kavle nyaang…®t wandeyan kavle vat yinda vak kat God al…®ps…®ga s…®l…®mbwigiyand…®. K…®ta nyan Godna waagan kat kavle nyaang…®t wandeyan kavle vat yinda vak kat God ana s…®l…®mbwigiyand…®.   
\p
\v 11 Ng…®ni ngwuk kat kavle vat yivat Juda yisola l…®nja ngay kaligyandi. Ngwuk kat kotmak jas kat kaligiyandi. Nat njambwi n…®mba ngwutna nyaang…®t wutnjangat kaligiyandi. Anda nyaang…®t waigowun waa n…®mamba ke yelav…®kngwa.  
\v 12 Wan njsmbla Godna waagan mbukngweya nyaang…®t ngwuk kat v…®s…®mogwigiyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 GOD N∆óN KAT APMA VAT V∆óGA L∆óGIYAND∆ó  
\p
\v 13 Wan n…®ma sakwat n…®mbana k…®ta nyan Jisas kat wand…®. S…®mogwi l…®ga nyan wuna yakwa nyan kat ambuk. Ana nyaek wundumbu yind…®. Nd…® kat kwinda nda wam…®n mala wun kat samat kwigand…® waa wand…® maa Jisas wand…®.  
\v 14 Wuna nj…®vwa ana nd…®. Mb…®tna nyaek kwiya nda kansaga kwil…®ga nyan ana wun waa nd…® kat walaa  
\v 15 n…®ma sakwat n…®mba kat wand…®. Nat nyana nda klavat n…®mamba ke yelav…®kngwa. Kwanda kwanda klanja nda n…®ma nda ana nd…® waa walaa ndi kat wapuseput mbutnd…®.   
\p
\v 16 N…®ma sanyo la nyan nd…®na ambugapmba k…®g…®nda n…®ma sakwat kwand…®.  
\v 17 Nd…® ambugat v…®laa yelav…®ntnd…®. Wuna k…®g…®nda n…®ma sakwat t…®gand…®. K…®g…®nda yisoga taagaluwa ngay maknat. Anda vapmba yigiyowun waa yelav…®taa wand…®.  
\v 18 Mbambala l…®ga mak nge sul…®laa mand…®p n…®ma ngay kwukiyowun. Kwutaa wuna k…®g…®nda wuna kwanda kwanda yisoga taagagiyowun.  
\v 19 Taagalaa apma vat t…®giyowun. Nj…®vwa kwutapman t…®ga nj…®mbla nj…®mbla kwo k…®g…®nda ngu k…®ga solat s…®giyowun waa wand…® maa God nd…® kat wand…®.  
\v 20 M…®n tungwengwan yiga l…®gam…®n. Wama nyaang…®t ana nglaatnd…®. Mbambala ngan kiyaigam…®n. Kiyam…®n, yisoga taagal…®ma nda nat nyan klaigand…® waa God wand…®, kiyand…®.  
\v 21 God kat yelav…®tapman k…®pmana kwanda kwanda m…®na yisoga taagal…®ga n…®mba k…®ngi vat t…®gandi. Wapuseput mbutuwa nyan vla l…®gandi waa Jisas mbuka l…®ga  
\v 22 nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat wand…®. Ngwuk k…®pmana nda kat n…®mamba ke yelav…®kngwa. Anda k…®g…®nda k…®giywoun. Anda waavwi kwusogiyowun waa n…®mamba ke yelav…®kngwa.  
\v 23 K…®g…®nda waavwi n…®ma nda ana nd…®.  
\v 24 Waavi yet…®ga vak kat yelav…®k ngwula. Ndi k…®g…®nda ana naanga p…®ka k…®l…®gandi. Ndi k…®g…®nda klaga ana yisoga taagal…®gandi. God ndi kat v…®ga l…®gand…®. God ndi kat v…®ga l…®ndan ngwuk kat apma vak v…®ga l…®giyand…®.  
\v 25 Ngwula k…®ta nyan tamb…® nyan t…®ga l…®vla mbund…® nyanat t…®giyowun waa wandeyan nd…® l…®vla mbund…® nyanat t…®giyand…®? Kai la. Ng…®ni t…®ga mand…®t mbang…® klaa ana t…®giyan…®n. N…®n wupma ana al…®ps…®ga t…®giyan…®n.  
\v 26 Ngwuk ana wan vak yigiyangwuk. Manda kat k…®g…®nda waavwi kat m…®na n…®mamba yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk.   
\p
\v 27 Mwe l…®ga vak kat yelav…®k ngwula. Ndi nj…®vwa ana kwut…®gandi. Ndi waavwi ana taval…®gandi. N…®an tamba la njambwi king Solomon nd…® apma waavwi kwusolaa l…®nd…®. Nd…®na waavwi mwena mbang…® kat ana kwulatnd…®. Mwena mbang…® apma nglei mband…® kat ana kwulatnd…®. Mwena mbang…® apma nglei mbang…®.  
\v 28 K…®pmamba avla wat…®ga nda s…®vla l…®l…®ga nda ana nd…®. Nat nandinya t…®nd…®, nat nandinya nat n…®mba kal…®taa ya sagaland…®, v…®ka ng…®l…®nd…®. Avla wat…®ga ndana mbang…® apma nglei mbang…®. God nd kat apma vak v…®ga l…®ga apma mbang…® kwind…®. Ngwuk k…®g…®nda waavwi kat ke n…®ma vak yelav…®ka kwaka l…®ngwa.  
\v 29-30 Ngepma ngepmamba la n…®mba k…®g…®nda waavwi kat m…®na kwat…®gandi. Wan ndagwinala t…®lapman yingweyan ngwutna ny…®nangwupmba l…®ga nyaek v…®laa kwigiyand…®.  
\v 31 Godna nda kat m…®na n…®mamba yelav…®ka l…®ngweyan k…®pmana nda ngwuk kat God kwigiyand…®.   
\s1 KWANDA KWANDA NDA NY∆óNANGWUPMBA YISOGA TAAGA NGWULA  
\p
\v 32 Ngwuk wuna mbaapmamba l…®ga n…®mba n…®mba sakwat n…®mba ana ngwuk. Ngwuk ke vakngwa. ngwutna nyaek ngwuk kat apma nglei vat v…®ga l…®gand…®.  
\v 33 Kwanda kwanda nda kwilaa sanya klalaa kwo l…®ga n…®mba kat agwi ngwula. Wupma yingweyan ngwutna ny…®nangwupmba l…®ga wenga nda n…®ma yigiyand…®. Ngwutna kwanda kwanda nda ny…®nangwupmba l…®ndeyan wovuna. S…®kwukiya n…®mba ana s…®kwukiyandi. Kalala ana k…®l…®kiyand…®.  
\v 34 Ngwutna kwanda kwanda nda ny…®nangwupmba l…®ndeyan ny…®nangwutna vak kat m…®na yelav…®ka t…®giyangwuk.   
\s1 NJAMBWI NYAN YAIGA NJ∆óMBLA KAT KAWIGA AL∆ó NGWULA  
\p
\v 35 Godna nj…®vwa kwuka yet…® ngwula. Njambwi nyan ngaga yaiga nj…®mbla kat kawiga al…® ngwula.  
\v 36 Kan k…®pmana njambwi n…®mbana nj…®vwa kwuta n…®mba ndina njambwi nyan kapti kat yind…®, yandeya nj…®mbla kat ndi ngaymba l…®ga kwo kawiga l…®ndi. Yand…® mala v…®laa ngayna mbapma lavwivat kwo kawiga l…®ndi. Kawiga l…®nja vla ngwutno ngwula njambwi nyan yaiga nj…®mbla kat kawiga al…® ngwula.  
\v 37 Yandeya nj…®mbla nd…®na nj…®vwa kwuta n…®mba nd…® kat kawiga l…®njeyan apma vatna. Kawiga l…®njeya vak v…®laa ndi kat k…®g…®nda klalaa ndi kat kapti kwuikiyand…®. Ndi ndaa l…®ga k…®giyandi.  
\v 38 Nd…® n…®nd…® ngan ngambi ngan yand…®, nd…®na nj…®vwa kwuta n…®mba s…®ndu kwalapman nd…® kat kawiga l…®njeyan apma nglei vatna.   
\p
\v 39 Nat ngay v…®ga la nyan s…®kwuta nyan yandeya nj…®mbla v…®gandan ana s…®ndu kwaind…®. Nd…® kat kawiga l…®gend…®. Nd…®na ngayna nda s…®kwutand…® walaa kawiga l…®gend…®.  
\v 40 Ngwutno kawiga al…® ngwula. Wun Godna vak s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan wun. Ng…®ni nat njamb…® ngaga yaweya nj…®mbla ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Ngi kat t…®ga nj…®mbla nj…®mbla kawiga l…®giyangwuk waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 GODNA NJ∆óVWA KWUTNEYA VAK  
\p
\v 41 Jisas wand…® mala Pita nd…® kat wand…®. Njambwi nyan wama nyaang…®t m…®na mbaapma n…®mba n…®n kat m…®na wam…®n? E? Wundi nat n…®mba kat wam…®n? Waa wagaland…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®.  
\v 42 Godna njsvwa kwuta n…®mba kat aywaa wan nyaang…®t wowun. Njambwi nyan nat n…®mba kat kwunatnjeya nj…®vwa kwind…®. Wan nj…®vwa kwagalalapman apma vapmba kwuka l…®njeyan wan apma vatna.  
\v 43 Njambwi nyan yaiga nj…®mbla nd…®na nj…®vwa apma vapmba kwuka l…®ndi, v…®ndeyan apma vatna waa waigand…®.  
\v 44 Njambwi nyan apma nj…®vwa kwuta vak v…®laa nj…®vwa kwuta nyan kat waigand…®.  
\v 45 Wuna njambwi nyan kwiyatapman ana yaigand…® waa nj…®vwa kwuta nyan yelav…®taa nat n…®mba kat kavle vat yiga k…®g…®ndagwi n…®ma ngu k…®ga tungwengwan yiga t…®ndeyan apma vak ana nd…®.  
\v 46 Wuna njambwi nyan mbambala ana yaigand…® waa wand…® mala yaigand…®. Yalaa nd…® kat viyaga nat kavle n…®mba kat yinjeya vla nd…® kat yigiyand…®.   
\p
\v 47 Njambwi nyana nj…®vwa kwuta nat n…®mba kupma agwut waa wanda vak wutaa nj…®vwa ana kwutndi. Kavle vat kwutndi. Njambwi nyan yalaa ndi kat n…®mamba viyaigand…®.  
\v 48 Njambwi nyan nj…®vwa kwuta nat n…®mba kupma agwut waa wanda vat ana wutndi. Wutapman t…®ga ndino kavle vat kwutndi. Njambwi nyan yalaa ndi kat n…®mamba ana viyaigand…®. Samat viyaigand…®. God n…®ma sakwat apma nyaang…®t kwila n…®mba ndi Godna nj…®vwa apma vat kwutapman y…®l…®njeyan God ndi kat n…®mamba viyaigand…®. God apma nyaang…®t kuvuk kwila n…®mba ndi Godna nj…®vwa apma vak kwutapman yil…®njeyan God ndi kat ana n…®mamba viyaigand…®. Samat viyaigand…®.   
\s1 JISAS YAND∆ó, WALEA L∆óNDI  
\p
\v 49 Kan k…®pma ngaga yalaa nj…®vwa kwutuwun mala nat n…®mba walea l…®giyandi. Mbambala samat walea l…®giyandi. V…®l…®gowun.  
\v 50 Samat t…®ga wun kat n…®ma vat yaigand…®. Mbambala n…®mamba yelav…®ka l…®gowun. Kan vak ng…®l…®nd…® maa ana n…®mamba yelav…®ka l…®giyowun. Kwo l…®giyowun.  
\v 51 Kan k…®pmana n…®mba kat kwutaa k…®ta mbaapmamba taagavat ana yawun. Yawun mala kapma kapma mbaapma s…®ga yet…®giyandi.  
\v 52 Ng…®ni k…®ta ngaymba la n…®mba mbaapma v…®l…®l…®k s…®giyandi. Tambanat n…®mba l…®njeyan kuvut n…®mba nat mbaapma s…®giyandi. V…®l…®l…®k pal…® nat mbaapma s…®giyamb…®t. Mbaapma s…®laa awat sowat walea l…®giyandi.  
\v 53 Nyaek nat mbaapma nyan nat mbaapma t…®giyamb…®t. Ny…®me nat mbaapma taagwa nyan nat mbaapma t…®giyamb…®t. Yaw nat mbaapma kang…®t nat mbaapma t…®giyamb…®t. Mbaapma s…®laa walea l…®giyandi.   
\s1 NG∆óNI YAIGA VAK  
\p
\v 54 Ngwuk yambun agwi v…®ga meik t…®mbu v…®ngweyan samat t…®ga meik ndaigiyand…® waa wal…®ngwuk maa ndal…®gand…®.  
\v 55 Kangan wal…®ga mwuk kwutnd…®, n…®na mbang…® n…®mamba kangan waigand…® waa wangwuk maa ngwutna mbang…® kangan wal…®gand…®.  
\v 56 Ny…®nangwuk k…®pma s…®mogwi l…®ga vak v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Waluwa ng…®ni yaiga nj…®mbla s…®mogwi l…®ga vat ana v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Manda kat mand…®p mand…®p yil…®gangwuk.   
\s1 NYAANG∆óT KWUNAKA NGAMBU NGWULA  
\p
\v 57 Ngwuk manda kat apma vat yelav…®tapman t…®gangwuk. Awuk ngwula.  
\v 58 Nat nyan m…®n kat kotmak kalingdeyan tak kot t…®nja ngay ke wuleiga. Ava yamb…® yiga l…®ga nyaang…®t kwunaka ngambu mb…®la. Kwunaka ngambulapman yimbeyan m…®n kat kwo kaligiyand…® kotmak. Jas wand…® maa plisman m…®n kat kwutaa kalabusmba taagiyand…®.  
\v 59 Ngwuk kat wowun. Kalabus kwiyatapman ana kwagalagiyangwuk. Jas wanda mbak ng…®l…®nd…® mala kwagalagiyangwuk.   
\c 13  
\s1 KAVLE MAAWUT KWAGALALAPMAN NYAN KAVLE YIGIYAND∆ó  
\p
\v 1 T…®ga l…®ga nat n…®mba yalaa tak njambwi nyan Pailat Galilina nat n…®mba kat vatnyanda vak Jisas kat mbutndi. Ndi God kat kwanda kwanda nda vatnyalaa God kat kwil…®ndi, vatnyand…® waa mbutndi Jisas kat.  
\v 2 Mbutndi mala Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Ngwuk angamak yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk. Ndi God kat n…®ma sakwat kavle vat yindi, Pailat ndi kat vatnyand…®? E? Ndina kavle vat Galilina nat n…®mbana kavle vak kat kwulatnd…®? E?  
\v 3 Kai luwa. Wupma kai. Ngwuk kat wowun. Ngwutna kavle maawut kwagalalapman yingweyan yinja vla yigiyangwuk.  
\v 4 Tak Sailoam wal…®nja kavamba la s…®vla ngay ndalaa tamba v…®li kiyeli s…®la kuvuk n…®mba kat vatnyand…®. Ndina kavle vat Jerusalemba la nat n…®mbana kavle vak kat kwulatnd…®? E? Ana kwulatnd…®?  
\v 5 Kai ana kwulatnd…®. Ngwuk kat wowun. Kavle maawut kwagalalapman yingweyan yinja vla yigiyangwuk.   
\s1 S∆óK WOGWULAPMAN MINA NYAANG∆óT  
\p
\v 6 Jisas ndi kat pagwuga la nyaang…®t mbutnd…®. K…®ta nyan fik wal…®nja mi nd…®na ambugapmba s…®k tund…®. T…®ga l…®ga mi s…®k s…®g…®pmak yand…®. Yand…®, ana s…®k wagwund…®.  
\v 7 Nd…®na nj…®vwa kwuta nyan kat wand…®…®. Yaa av…®. Wan mi naambi kuvuk ana s…®k wogwul…®gand…®. V…®levigowun. Kwulamba av…®k kan mi. Manda kat kwo l…®ga k…®pmana kwiya m…®na k…®ga kiyagiga l…®giyand…® waa wand…® maa nd…®na nj…®vwa kwuta nyan wand…®.  
\v 8 Njambwi nyan kan naambi mi kwo l…®giyand…®. Angwamba waangu valaa bulmakauna ndi taagagiyowun.  
\v 9 Yaiga naambi s…®k anagand…® kwaiga. S…®k kwalapman yindeyan v…®kiyowun waa wand…®.   
\s1 NJ∆óVWA LAPMAN NANDINYAMBA JISAS TAAGWA K∆óTA KWUNATND∆ó  
\p
\v 10 Nj…®vwa lapman nandinya Jisas Juda yisolaa l…®nja ngay wuleilaa ndi kat nyaang…®t mbut…®ndi.  
\v 11 Kavle waagan tavila la taagwa k…®ta l…®l…®. Kavle waagan tavila l…®la mbuni kavle vat yind…®. S…®landa s…®landa yet…®l…®. Al…®ps…®ga ana savagu yet…®l…®.  
\v 12 Jisas l…® kat v…®laa yagwa wand…®, yal…®. Yal…® mala Jisas wands…®. Ny…®na mbang…®mba l…®ga yelogwen k…®ngiyan kai waa sav…®luwa waa walaa  
\v 13 nd…®na taamba l…®la mbunimba taagand…®, savagu laat…®. Savagu laataa Godna s…® kwutaa katsol…®l…®.  
\v 14 Yisola l…®nja ngay v…®ga la nyan v…®laa kai waa nj…®ka l…®nd…®. Jisas nj…®vwa lapman nandinyamba nj…®vwa kwutnd…® waa yelav…®ka nj…®ka l…®nd…®. Nd…® laataa yisolaa la n…®mba kat wand…®. Nj…®vwa kwutneya nandinya s…®la k…®ta kwo l…®gand…®. Wan yelogwen kat t…®ga n…®mba nandinya s…®la k…®ta yandi maa kwunatndeyan wovuna. Nj…®vwa lapman nandinya kai. Ana nglaatnd…® waa wand…® maa Jisas wand…®.  
\v 15 M…®n kavle vat yelav…®ka l…®gam…®n. M…®na maawut ana nglaatnd…®. Nj…®vwa lapman nandinya n…®na ngepma n…®mba aywaa ndina bulmakau donki tunja yaaw s…®vugilaa ngu k…®njangat kalil…®gandi. Ngwutno n…®mbun kalil…®gangwuk. Wan kavle vat ana nd…® waa wal…®gandi.  
\v 16 Kat taagwa n…®na ngepma lagwat. L…® Ebrahamna yelang…® lagwat. Seten wand…® maa naambi taamba v…®li kiyeli sela kuvuk l…®la mbang…®mba yelogwern ngila l…®ndi. Mbambala nj…®vwa lapman nandinya wowun maa yelogwen ng…®l…®nd…®. Bulmakau donki kat ndina yaaw s…®vugingwa vla wuno wupma wupma l…® kat tula la yelogwen s…®vugiwun. Kavle vakna yima waa wun kat manda kat wal…®gangwuk waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 17 Wand…® mala Jisas kat kai wala njambwi n…®mba nyaang…®t kai. Wup yindi. Nat kwo la n…®mba Jisas ya vat v…®laa apma vatna wal…®ndi.   
\s1 MASTET WAL∆óNJA MI S∆óKNAGWI YISNA PAGWULA LA NYAANG∆óT  
\p
\v 18 Jisas wand…®. God ndinyangu kat v…®ga la vak anda vak vla l…®gand…®. Anda nda vla l…®gand…®.  
\v 19 Nd…® mastet wal…®nja s…®k vla l…®gand…®. Wan s…®k mak glei nda. K…®ta nyan wan s…®k klalaa nd…®na ambugapmba tund…®, n…®ma mi wokend…®. Wokend…®, waavi n…®ma sakwat nd…®na sand…®mba veilaa l…®ndi waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 20 Jisas nat njamb…® wand…®. God ndinyangu kat v…®ga la vak anda nda vla l…®gand…®.  
\v 21 Nd…® yis vla l…®gand…®. Bret-nao kwut…®ga taagwa yis kuvuk klalaa wit milmba taagal…®, bret-nao n…®man wokend…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 GOD V∆óGA LA KAVA WULEINJEYA VAK  
\p
\v 22 Jisas Jerusalemat yiga ngepma ngepma nyaang…®t kwiga yil…®nd…®.  
\v 23 Yiga l…®ga k…®ta nyan nd…® kat wand…®. N…®ma sakwat n…®mba ana ndi nyinangwuk wuleigiyaa. Wovuna? waa wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®.  
\v 24 Wuleinjeya suwi yamb…® n…®ma t…®vwiya ana l…®. N…®ma nj…®vwa kwuka wuleigiyangwuk. N…®ma sakwat n…®mba wuleivat waigandi. Ana weleigiyandi.  
\v 25 T…®ga l…®ga wan ngayna nhjambwi nyan laataa mbapmo tiv…®giyand…®. T…®v…®nd…® maa ngwuk alagumba l…®ga taamba viyaa waigangwuk. Njambwi nyan njambwi nyan n…®n kat suwi lavwi waa waigangwuk. Wangwuk mala njambwi nyan waigand…®. Ngwuk anda n…®mba ngwuk. Ngwula n…®ndama ana v…®ga l…®gowun waa waigand…®.  
\v 26 Wand…® maa n…®n tak m…®nogwinala nao k…®ga la n…®mba n…®n. N…®na ngepma yalaa n…®n kat nyaang…®t mbut…®m…®n waa waigangwuk.  
\v 27 Wukngwuk maa njambwi nyan nat njamb…® waigand…®. Ngwuk kat woseka ana wowun. Ngwutna m…®ndama ana v…®ga l…®gowun. Ngwutna ngepma ana v…®ga l…®gowun. Ngwuk kavle n…®mba ngwuk. Ay ngwula waa waigand…® ngwuk kat.  
\v 28 Ngaymba la n…®mba v…®giyangwuk. Ebraham, Aisak, Jekop, tamba la profet wuleindi, v…®giyangwuk. Ndi God v…®ga la kava tamba wuleindi. N…®n alagumba kwo l…®gan…®n waa yelav…®taa nglaga n…®mbi ngliaka l…®giyangwuk.  
\v 29 Woli agwi, yambun agwi, kambangwat agwi, malingwat agwi t…®ga n…®mba yalaa God v…®ga la kava wuleilaa ndaa l…®ga nao k…®g…®nda k…®ga l…®giyandi.  
\v 30 N…®n nat n…®mba kat kwulat…®gan…®n waa mbambla yelav…®t…®gangwuk. Ng…®ni yaiga nj…®mbla ngwuk kat kwulakiyandi.   
\s1 JISAS JERUSALEMBA LA N∆óMBA KAT N∆óMA MAAWUT YELAV∆óKA L∆óND∆ó  
\p
\v 31 Wan nandinya nat Ferisi Jisas kat yalaa wandi. Wan kava kwagala m…®la. Njambwi nyan Herot m…®n kat vatnyavat t…®gand…® waa wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®.  
\v 32 Herot nd…® woseka wal…®ga nyana. Nd…® kat yiga ambuk ngwula. Mbambala nj…®vwa kwuka kavle waagan sav…®l…®ga yelogwen kat ta n…®mba kat kwunakiyowun. Ng…®ni kwutuwa nj…®vwa ng…®l…®nd…®, kwo l…®giyowun.  
\v 33 Wungi kat t…®ga wan kava ana kwagalalaa yigiyowun. Mbambala nj…®vwa kwuka kumba l…®giyowun. Godna nyaang…®t mbut…®ga n…®mba ndi kat kwo kavamba ana vatnyal…®gandi. Jerusalemba m…®na vatnyal…®gandi. Wupma yiga ambuk ngwula nd…® kat waa Jisas ndi kat walaa Jerusalemba la n…®mba kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka wand…®.   
\p
\v 34 Ngwuk Jerusalemba la n…®mba ngwuk tamba la profet kat vatnyal…®gangwuk. God wand…®, ngwuk kat yaa n…®mba kat vatnyal…®ngwuk. Ngan nyaaga l…®la nyangu kat l…®la wiyo pulumba yapmola kwal…®. Yapmola vak vla ngwuk kat kwutaa wuna mbaapmamba taagavat wowun. Ngwuk kai wangwuk.  
\v 35 Kai wangwuk, God ngwuk kat kwagaland…® mala ngwutna kavle vat kwo l…®giyand…®. Samat t…®ga wun kat ana v…®giyangwuk. Ng…®ni ngwutna ngepma wuleiwun maa wun kat v…®laa waigangwuk. Apma vat yam…®n. God wand…®, yam…®n waa waigangwuk.   
\c 14  
\s1 JISAS MBANG∆ó WUTA LA NYAN KAT KWUNATND∆ó  
\p
\v 1 Nj…®vwa lapman nandinya njambwi la Ferisi Jisas kat wand…® maa nd…®na ngay nao k…®vak wuleind…®. Nao k…®vak yaa nat n…®mba Jisas angamak yigiyand…® waa yelav…®ka nd…® kat v…®ga l…®ndi.  
\v 2 T…®ga l…®ga mbang…® wuta la nyan Jisas kat yand…®, v…®nd…®.  
\v 3 V…®laa Ferisiogwi Moses kwiya nyaang…®t s…®mogwi la n…®mba kat wand…®. Njivwa lapman nandinyamba kan nyan kat kwunakweyan wovuna? E? Kavlea? Waa wand…®.  
\v 4 Wand…® maa awat ana wandi. Jisas nd…® kat kwutaa kwunataa ay wand…®, yind…®.  
\v 5 Yind…® maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Nj…®vwa lapman nandinya ngwula donki bulmakau waangumba ndainjeyan yiga klokaligiyangwuk waa wand…® maa  
\v 6 ndi ana al…®ps…®ga awat wandi.   
\s1 K∆óTA NYAN AVLA ND∆óNA S∆ó KWUTAA KE KATSOGA  
\p
\v 7 Jisasogwinala nao k…®vat yaa n…®mba njambwi ta n…®mbana t…®l…®ga kavamba ndaa l…®vat nj…®vwa kwuka yi ya l…®ndi. Yinja vak v…®laa Jisas ndi kat pagwula la nyaang…®t mbutnd…®.  
\v 8 K…®ta nyan k…®g…®nda kwutaa wand…®, nd…®na ngaymba k…®vat yingweyan njambwi l…®ga n…®mba t…®l…®ga kavamba ke ndaa l…®ga. Njambwi l…®ga n…®mba t…®l…®ga kavamba ke ndaa l…®ga. Njambwi nyan nao k…®vat yandeyan  
\v 9 m…®n kat yagwa waa nyan njambwi nyan kat kwutaa ndaa l…®ma kayamba kaligiyand…®. Kalilaa m…®n kat waigand…®. Ndaa l…®ma t…®g…®t kwagalalaa kumba mat t…®g…®pmba yaa al…®. Kan njambwi nyan ndaa l…®ma t…®g…®tmba ndaa l…®giyand…® waa wand…® maa n…®mamba wup yiga nat kavamba yiga ndaa l…®giyam…®n.  
\v 10 K…®ta nyan k…®ginda kwutaa wand…®, nd…®na ngaymba k…®vat yingweyan mat t…®ga n…®mba t…®l…®ga kavamba ndaa al…® ngwula. Wupma ndaa l…®meyan m…®n kat yagwa waa nyan m…®n kat waigand…®. Ndaa l…®ma t…®g…®t kwagalalaa kalat yagwa. Njambwi t…®g…®tmba ndaa l…®giyam…®n. Wand…® mala yim…®n, nat n…®mba v…®laa m…®na s…® kwutaa katsogiyandi waa pagwula la nyaang…®t mbutaa nyaang…®tna angwa ndi kat mbutnd…®.  
\v 11 Avla ngwutna s…® kwutaa katsongweyan nat n…®mba v…®laa viyesendagiyandi. Avla ngwutna s…® viyesendangweyan nat n…®mba v…®laa katsogiyandi waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 N∆óMA K∆óG∆óNDA KWUKNGWEYA VAT  
\p
\v 12 Yagwa wuna ngaymba yaa ag…® waa wanda nyan kat Jisas wand…®. N…®ma k…®g…®nda kwupmeya nj…®mbla m…®na al…® n…®mba kat m…®na yagwa waa ke waa. M…®na yelang…® n…®mba, ngepma n…®mba, n…®ma sanyo t…®ga n…®mba kat m…®na yagwa waa ke waa. Ndi kat yagwa wameyan ng…®ni m…®n kat yaa ag…® waa waigandi.  
\v 13 N…®ma k…®g…®nda kwupmeya nj…®mbla sanya lapman n…®mba, man kavle ya n…®mba, yelogwen kat ta n…®mba, m…®ni v…®lapman n…®mba kat yaa ag…® ngwula waa awa.  
\v 14 Ndi ng…®ni awat yaa ag…® waa ana waigandi. Wupma yimeyan ng…®ni yaiga nandinya kiya n…®mba laakiya nandinya God m…®n kat awat apma vat yigiyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 N∆óMA K∆óG∆óNDA KAT PAGWULA LA NYAANG∆óT JISAS MBUTND∆ó  
\p
\v 15 Wundi n…®mbana k…®ta nyan Jisas waa nyaang…®t wutaa wand…®. God v…®ga la kava wuleilaa ndaa l…®ga k…®neya nj…®mbla apma vat t…®giyan…®n waa wand…®.  
\v 16 Wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. K…®ta nyan n…®ma k…®g…®nda kwutaa n…®ma sakwat n…®mba kat wand…®.  
\v 17 K…®vat t…®nja nj…®mbla nd…®na nj…®vwa kwuta n…®mba kat wand…®, yagwa ngwula k…®g…®nda tamba kwuka t…®gan…®n, t…®gand…® waa yiga wandi.  
\v 18 Wandi maa yavak kat aywaa kai wandi. Nat nyan wand…®. Wun kupi k…®pma klawun. Yiga v…®giywoun. Wun ana al…®ps…®ga yaigowun wand…®.  
\v 19 Nat nyan wand…®. Wun bulmakau tamba v…®li klawun. Yiga v…®giyowun. Wun bulmakau tamba v…®li klawun. Yiga v…®giyowun. Wun ana al…®ps…®ga yaigowun waa wand…®.  
\v 20 Nat nyan wand…®. Wun mbambala glei taagwa klawun. Wun ana al…®ps…®ga yaigowun waa wand…®.   
\p
\v 21 Ana al…®ps…®ga yaigan…®n waa wanja vak nj…®vwa kwuta nyan nd…®na njambwi nyan kat yiga mbutnd…®. Mbutnd…® maa nmjambwi nyan nd…®na maawupmba ndi kat nj…®ka l…®nd…®. Nj…®ka l…®ga nd…®na nj…®vwa kwuta nyan kat wand…®. kwiyatapman yiga kava kava man veilapman n…®mba, yelogwen kat ta n…®mba, sanya lapman n…®mba, m…®ni v…®lapman n…®mba ndi kat aywaa wam…®n, yaandi waa wand…® njambwi nyan.  
\v 22 Wand…®, yiga wand…®, yandi. Yandi maa nj…®vwa kwuta nyan njambwi nyan kat wand…®. Aywaa yandi. Ngay ana taat…® waa wand…® maa  
\v 23 njambwi nyan wand…®. kava kava, kwap…®, ndinyangu lapman kava, kwo kavamba yiga wam…®n, k…®ta nyan k…®ta nyan yaandi. Wuna ngay taatangat wowun.  
\v 24 Tak yagwa wawa n…®mba ndi ana k…®giyandi luwa waa wand…® njambwi nyan waa mbutnd…® Jisas.   
\s1 MAAWUPMBA YELAV∆óTAA JISASNA KWUPMBA AY  
\p
\v 25 N…®ma sakwat n…®mba Jisas la kavamba yaa yisolaa l…®ndi, Jisas ndi kat nyaang…®t mbut…®nd…®.  
\v 26 Mbuka wand…®. K…®ta nyan wuna kwupmba yavat yindeyan nd…®na nyaek ny…®me, taagwa, nyangu, yakwa n…®mbana nyaang…®t wupmak kat kai walaa wuna kwupmba yaigand…®. Wuna kwupmba yalaa wunai waa nyaang…®pmba nj…®vwa kwukiyand…®.  
\v 27 Vatnyanjeya n…®mba diwai kros walalaa kalinja vla ngwuk kat vatnyanjeyan nd…®na mala.   
\p
\v 28 K…®ta nyan svla nge kwupmat wandeyan ana kwo kwukiyand…®. Yigumba yelav…®taa ngayna nda aywaa kwunaka taagalaa kwukiyand…®.  
\v 29 Yelav…®tapman kwo kwutndeyan apma vak ana kwukiyand…®. Kwaal…®k m…®na tawga kwagalagiyand…®. Nat n…®mba nd…® kat v…®laa nj…®kiyandi.  
\v 30 Wan nyan kwo yelav…®tapman s…®mblan kwutnd…®. Ana al…®ps…®ga aywaa kwukiyand…® waa nj…®ka waigandi.   
\p
\v 31 K…®ta njambwi king nat king kat waleavat t…®ndeyan tak yelav…®kiyand…®. Wuna soldia 10,000 m…®na l…®gand…®. Nd…®na soldia 20,000 n…®mba ndi. Ndi kat anda vapmba kwulaiyowun waa yelav…®taa s…®vat yigiyand…®.  
\v 32 Ndi kat ana al…®ps…®ga kwulakiyowun waa walaa nd…® s…®vat ana yigiyand…®. nd…®na nj…®vwa kwuta n…®mba kat wand…® maa yiga nat king kat k…®mb…®t kwukiyandi. Ana waleagiyandi.   
\p
\v 33 Ngwulo wupma l…®gangwuk. Wuna kwanda kwanda nda aywaa kwagalagiyowun waa yelav…®tapman yingweyan wuna kwupmba yaga wuna nj…®vwa ana al…®ps…®ga kwukiyangwuk.   
\s1 K∆óL∆óNJA SOL NYINGI YIL∆óGA VAT NG∆óL∆óND∆ó  
\p
\v 34 K…®l…®nja sol apma nda. Nd…®na nyingi yil…®nda vat ng…®l…®ndeyan apma nda ana nd…®. Tamba kavle yind…®. Nj…®vwa kai.  
\v 35 Nat kavle ya nda ambukapmba yaagineyan ambugatna nda apma vak laakiyand…®. Nyingi lapman sol wupma kai. Ambugapmba ana yaagil…®gan…®n. nyingi lapman sol n…®n kwo yaagil…®gan…®n. Nj…®vwa kai. Wawa nyaang…®t yigumba wuka maawupmba yelav…®k ngwula waa wand…® Jisas.   
\c 15  
\s1 S∆óL∆óWOKNA SIP SIP PAGWULA LA NYAANG∆óT  
\p
\v 1 Takis sanya kla la n…®mbo nat kavle n…®mbo Jisas mbuta nyaang…®t wupmat yandi.  
\v 2 Moses kwiya nyaang…®t s…®mogwi la n…®mbo Ferisio v…®laa wandi. Wan kavle n…®mba kat manda kat kai walapman yil…®gand…®. Wuna nyaang…®t yaa awut waa manda kat bndi kat wal…®gand…®. Ndinogwinala manda kat nao k…®l…®gand…®. Ana nglaatnd…® waa wandi.   
\p
\v 3 Wandi maa ndi kat pagwula la nyaang…®t mbutnd…®.  
\v 4 Ngwula k…®ta nyan sip sip ndumi tambanat t…®ga sip sip k…®ta kwo kava yiga s…®l…®wotndeyan nat sip sip kat kwagalalaa yiga kwakiyand…®. kwaka yiga v…®laa kwukiyand…®.  
\v 5 Sip sip kat kwutaa nyaambupmba walalaa solat s…®ga kiyaigand…®.  
\v 6 Ngepma wuleilaa nd…®na al…® n…®mba kat waigand…®. Wunogwinala solat as…® ngwula. Wuna s…®l…®wokna sip sip v…®laa kwutaa walalaa kiyawun waa waigand…®.  
\v 7 Ngwuk kat wowun. Kavle vat yiga yet…®l…®ga k…®ta nyan kavle maawut kwagalalaa mand…®p kupi maawupmba yet…®ndeyan ny…®nangwupmba l…®ga n…®mba wupma n…®mamba solat s…®giyandi. Ny…®nangwupmba l…®ga n…®mba apma maawut s…®ka apma vat yiga yet…®l…®ga n…®ma sakwat n…®mba kat v…®laa ana n…®mamba solat s…®giyandi. Samat samat solat s…®giyandi waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 S∆óL∆óWEOKNA SANYA PAGWULA LA NYAANG∆óT  
\p
\v 8 Jisas ndi kat nat pagwula la nyaang…®t mbutnd…®. Taagwa k…®ta sanya tamba v…®li m…®na taagal…®, l…®nd…®. K…®ta s…®l…®wot…®. L…® lam sag…®l…®laa ngayat yaguga kwakiyal…®.  
\v 9 V…®laa l…®la al…® n…®mba, ngepma n…®mba kat waigal…®. Wunogwinala solat as…® ngwula. S…®l…®wokna sanya tamba v…®laa klawun waa waigal…®.  
\v 10 Ngwuk kat wowun. Godnonala ny…®nangwupmba t…®ga ensel kavle4 vat ta nyan nd…®na kavle vat kwagalandeyan ndi wupma solat s…®giyandi waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 KWAND∆ó NYAN NYAEK KAT KWAGALALAA YIND∆ó  
\p
\v 11 Jisas ndi kat wapuseput mbutnd…®. K…®ta nyan nondanyan v…®l…®l…®k ta nyana.  
\v 12 Mat nyan nyaek kat wand…®. Ng…®ni kiyam…®n, kalaweya kwanda kwanda nda mbambala agwi m…®la waa wand…® maa nyaek mb…®k kat kansaga kwind…®.  
\v 13 T…®ga l…®ga nd…®na kwanda kwanda nda aywaa kwuka naangalaa s…®vla kavat yind…®. Yilaa t…®nda kavamba nd…®na sanya aywaa kwuka yaagiga kavle vat yet…®nd…®.  
\v 14 Nd…®na sanya ng…®l…®ndi maa t…®nda k…®pma k…®g…®nda lapman t…®nd…®. Nd…®no k…®g…®nda kat v…®levilaa l…®nd…®.  
\v 15 Kan k…®pmana k…®ta nyan kat v…®laa nj…®vwa nd…®namba kland…®. Nd…®na mbak kat k…®g…®nda kwiga v…®ga l…®nd…®.  
\v 16 Nd…® k…®g…®nda kai. Nd…® kat ana kwil…®ndi. Mbak kat kwil…®nda mi s…®k k…®vat wand…®.   
\p
\v 17 T…®ga l…®ga nd…®na maawupmba yelav…®tnd…®. Wun manda kat kumba kavle vat yet…®gowun. Wuna nyaekna nj…®vwa kwut…®ga n…®mba ndi k…®g…®nda n…®ma sakwat t…®gand…®. Wun k…®g…®nda tapman t…®ga kiya m…®na l…®gowun.  
\v 18 Kan kava kwagalalaa wuna nyaek t…®ga kava yiga nd…® kat waigowun. Wun m…®n kat kavle vat yiwun. Wun God kat kavle vat yiwun.  
\v 19 Ngi kat t…®ga m…®na nyanat ng…®ni ana l…®giyowun. Wam…®n maa m…®na nj…®vwa kwut…®ga nyanat t…®giyowun waa waigowun waa yelav…®tnd…®.  
\v 20 Yelav…®taa kan kava kwagalalaa nyaek t…®ga ngepmat yind…®. Ngepma ana wuleind…®, s…®vlamba l…®nd…®, nyaek nd…® kat v…®nd…®. V…®laa n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka p…®l…®ga yiga nd…® kat taamba kwutaa nyambupmba viyand…®.  
\v 21 Kwutnd…® maa nyan nd…® kat wand…®. Nyaek m…®n kat kavle vat yiwun. God kat kavle vat yiwun. Ngi kat t…®ga ng…®ni m…®na nyanat ana l…®giyowun waa wand…® maa nd…®na nyaek wand…®.  
\v 22 Wupma ke waa waa walaa nd…®na nj…®vwa kwuta n…®mba kat wand…®. Apma waavwi kwutaa nd…® kat agwi ngwula. Apma taamba ring kalalaa nd…®na taambamba kwuso. Apma man su klalaa nd…®na mamba kwuso.  
\v 23 Apma nyan bulmakau vatnyalaa k…®g…®nda agwut ngwula. N…®n solat s…®ga kapti kwukiyan…®n.  
\v 24 Wuna nyan tak kiya nyan vla l…®nd…®, nd…® kat ana v…®ga l…®wun. Nd…® tamba yalaa l…®gand…®. Tat s…®l…®wotnd…®. Mbambala tamba yalaa l…®gand…® waa wand…® maa solat s…®ga k…®g…®nda kwutndi.   
\p
\v 25 Njambwi nyan ambugapmba nj…®vwa kwuka l…®ga nj…®vwa ng…®l…®nd…®, ngay yand…®. Ngay ngwaymba l…®ga mbangu veinja vak wutnd…®.  
\v 26 Wutaa nd…®na nyaekna nj…®vwa kwuta nyan kat mandana wutuwa waa wand…®.  
\v 27 Wand…® maa wand…®. m…®na sambu tamba yand…®. Yand…® maa m…®na nyaek apma nyan bulmakau vatnyand…® k…®g…®nda kwupmat. Yanda vak kat solat s…®ga vatnyand…® waa wand…® nj…®vwa kwuta nyan.  
\v 28 Nyamwun wutaa t…®pmwigwula yiga ngay wuleivak kat kai wand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga nd…®na nyaek wogwend…® nd…® kat wagalavat.  
\v 29 Wagaland…® mala nyaek kat wand…®. naambi n…®ma sakwat wama nj…®vwa m…®na kwut…®wun. M…®n kat ana kavle vat yiwun. M…®n kat ana kai wowun. Wuna al…® n…®mba kat k…®g…®nda kwukwangat mat meme ana vatnyalaa wun kat kwim…®n.  
\v 30 Wuna sambu nd…® kat kwima sanya s…®k yamb…®s…®k yiga yaagind…®. yand…® maa nd…® kat apma nyan bulmakau vatnyam…®n. Ana nglaatnd…® waa wand…®.   
\p
\v 31 Wand…® mala nyaek wand…®. Nj…®mbla nj…®mbla wunogwinala t…®l…®gam…®n. Kiyawun maa wuna nda aywaa klaigam…®n.  
\v 32 M…®na sambu wupma kai. Nd…® tamba kiyand…® waa yelav…®ka l…®wun. Mbambala kwo l…®gand…®. Tat s…®l…®wotnd…®. Mbambala tamba yalaa l…®gand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga solat s…®ga k…®g…®nda kwutneyan kavle vat ana nd…® waa wand…® nyaek waa mbutnd…® Jisas.   
\c 16  
\s1 KNJVWA KWUTA NYAN KAVLE SAVLE KWUTNDA VAK  
\p
\v 1 Jisas nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat wand…®. Tamba n…®ma sanya la nyan t…®nd…®. Wand…® mala nat nyan nd…®na nj…®vwa kat v…®ga l…®nd…®. Nat n…®mba njambwi nyan kat wandi. M…®na nj…®vwa v…®ga l…®ga nyan kavle savle kwut…®gand…® waa wandi, njambwi nyan nd…®na nj…®vwa v…®ga la nyan kat wand…®.  
\v 2 Kavle savle kwut…®m…®n waa wandi, wutwun. Kwut…®ma vak wun kat ambuk. Mbupm…®n mala s…®ga naguga v…®giyowun. S…®ga naguga v…®laa ng…®ni wuna nj…®vwa kwukiyam…®n? E? Ana kwukiyam…®n? Waa njambwi nyan wand…®.   
\p
\v 3 Wand…® maa nj…®vwa kwuta nyan maawupmba yelav…®tnd…®. Nd…® kat mbukweyan kavle vat kwutuwa vak v…®laa wun kat kai waigand…®. Wun angamak yigiyowun. Wun ava lapman t…®ga ambugatna nj…®vwa ana al…®ps…®ga kwukiyowun. Wun wup yigiyowun nat nyan kat k…®g…®nda kat wagalaweyan waa yelav…®ka l…®ga yindeya vat yelav…®tnd…®.  
\v 4 Yiweya vak yiwun mala wun kat kai y wand…® maa nat n…®mba wun kat k…®g…®nda kwigiyandi waa yelav…®tnd…®.  
\v 5 Tat sanyo ta nyananamba nat n…®mba dinau klandi. Nj…®vwa kwuta nyan wundi n…®mba kat yagwa wand…®, yandi. Yandi maa ndi kat k…®ta nyan k…®ta nyan wand…®. Tat ta nyan kat m…®na dinau angamak sakwat t…®gand…® waa wand…®.  
\v 6 Wand…® maa 100 dram wel wand…®. Wand…® maa nd…® kat wand…®. Tamba m…®na dinau kwusenda taagagowun. 50 dram wel m…®na kwigiyam…®n waa nj…®vwa v…®ga la nyan wand…®.  
\v 7 Nat nyan kat m…®na dinau angamak sakwat t…®gand…® waa wand…® maa 100 bek rais wand…®. Wand…® maa tamba m…®na dinau kwusenda taagagowun. 80 bek rais m…®na kwigiyam…®n waa wand…®.   
\p
\v 8 Yinda vak njambwi nyan wutaa wand…®. Apma vak kwunapm…®n. M…®n kat kai wowun maa nat n…®mba dinau kusenda taagama n…®mba ng…®ni m…®n kat ndinai k…®g…®nda kat v…®ga l…®giya waa wand…® njambwi nyan waa wand…® Jisas. Jisas ndi kat nat samat nyaang…®t wand…®. Kan k…®pmana n…®mba ndi nambuo l…®ga n…®mba ndi. Nat n…®mba kat kwunat…®njan ngwuk wuna mbaapma n…®mba ngwuk kat kwulat…®gandi.   
\p
\v 9 Ngwuk wuna mbaapma n…®mba ngwuk kat wowun. Mbambala kan k…®pmamba l…®ngwan ngwutna sanya apma nj…®vwamba agwuk ngwula. S…®mblan ke yaagiga. K…®pmana sanya ngwuk kat nj…®mbla nj…®mbla ana l…®giyand…®. Apma nj…®vwa kwuka l…®ngweyan sanya ng…®l…®nd…® maa ng…®ni ny…®nangwupmba yiga apma vak nj…®mbla nj…®mbla t…®giyangwuk.   
\p
\v 10 Nat nyan mat nj…®vwa apma vat kwut…®ndeyan wan nyan n…®ma nj…®vwa apma vat kwukiyand…®. Nat nyan mat nj…®vwa kavle vat kwut…®ndeyan wan nyan n…®ma nj…®vwa kavle vat kwukiyand…®.  
\v 11 Kan k…®pmamba l…®ngwan kavle savle nj…®vwa kwukngweyan ng…®ni ny…®nangwut wokengwuk mala God ngwuk kat apma n…®ma nj…®vwa ana kwigiyand…®.  
\v 12 Mbambala k…®pmamba l…®ngwan Godna nj…®vwa kavle savle kwuka l…®ngweyan ng…®ni ny…®nangwut wokelaa God ngwuk kat kwindeya nj…®vwa apma vat ana kwukiyangwuk.   
\p
\v 13 K…®ta nyan ana v…®l…®l…®k pal…®na nyaang…®t wuka nj…®vwa kwukiyand…®. Nat k…®ta nyan kat kai walaa nat nyana nyaang…®t m…®na wukiyand…®. Ngwut kan k…®pmana nj…®vwa kwuka Godna nj…®vwa kwuka k…®ta k…®ta ana kwukiyangwuk waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 GOD WAA NYAANG∆óTNA VAK  
\p
\v 14 Kumba la Ferisi ndi k…®pmana nda kat m…®na yelav…®ka l…®ndi. Jisas waa nyaang…®t wutaa nd…® kat nj…®t…®ndi.  
\v 15 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Nat n…®mba ngwutna s…® kwutaa katsonjangat woviyaguga l…®gangwuk. Ngwutna kavle maawut God v…®ga l…®gand…®. Kan k…®pmana n…®mba woviyaguga t…®nja vak kat God ana woviyaguga l…®gand…®. God nd…® kai wal…®gang…® kan vak kat.   
\p
\v 16 Moses kwiya nyaang…®t profet waa nyaang…®t God n…®n kat tak kwind…®. Ng…®ni ngu yagula Jon laataa God n…®n kat kwunataa v…®ga l…®ndeya vak mbut…®nd…®. mbut…®nd…® mala ngepma ngepmamba la n…®mba kan vak klavat s…®mblan n…®ma nj…®vwa kwut…®ndi.   
\p
\v 17 God tak kwiya nyaang…®t ana ng…®l…®giyand…®. Ana kwo vala t…®giyand…®. K…®pma ny…®nangwut ng…®ni ng…®l…®giyand…®. God tak kwiya nyaang…®t ana ng…®l…®giyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 TAAGWA KAT KE KWAGALANGWEYA  
\p
\v 18 Jisas wand…®. K…®ta nyan nd…®na taagwa kat kwagalalaa nat taagwa klandeyan kavle vatna. Yamb…®s…®k yil…®nja vak vla yil…®nd…®. Nat nyan nd…®na taagwa kwagaland…® maa wat taagwa nat nyan klandeyan nd…®no kavle vatna. yamb…®s…®k yil…®nja vak vla yil…®nd…® nd…®no waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 SANYO LA NYANO LASARASO  
\p
\v 19 Jisas ndi kat nyaang…®t mbutnd…®. N…®ma sakwat sanyo la nyan t…®nd…®. Nd…® apma nglei waavwi kwuso l…®nd…®. Nandinya nandinya n…®ma k…®g…®nda apma k…®g…®nda m…®na k…®l…®nd…®.  
\v 20 Nat nyan sanya lapman nyan t…®nd…®. nd…®na s…® Lasaras. Nd…® sanya kat nat n…®mba kat yawiga wand…®. Sanya lapman nyan ngwutnyala pulumba ndaa l…®nd…®. Nd…®na mbang…® kawia n…®ma sakwat k…®l…®nd…®.  
\v 21 K…®lamb…®nja nao k…®vak kwo kawiga l…®nd…®. Waala nd…® kat yalaa nd…®na kawiya l…®k viyenga k…®l…®ndi.   
\p
\v 22 T…®ga l…®ga sanya lapman nyan kiyand…®. kiyand…®, ensel nd…® kat kwutaa Ebraham ta kavat kalindi. Sanya la nyan nd…®no kiyand…®, waangumba vaangundi.  
\v 23 Vaangundi, nd…® ya v…®t…®ga kavat yind…®. Nd…®na mbang…® n…®mamba kangan wand…®, Ebrahamagwi Lasaraso s…®vlamba l…®mb…®t, v…®nd…®.  
\v 24 Nd…® Ebraham kat n…®ma kwundi walega wand…®. Ebraham, wuna ngwak wun kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®k. Wam…®n maa Lasaras nd…®na s…®t taamba ngumba taagalaa yaa wuna t…®gatmba taagand…®. Wuna mbang…® n…®mamba kangan wal…®gand…® waa wand…® maa Ebraham nd…® kat wand…®.   
\p
\v 25 Walanga, tak k…®pmamba l…®man apma nda m…®na klal…®m…®n. lasaras nd…® kavle nda m…®na klal…®nd…®. Mbambala nd…® apma vat t…®gand…®, m…®n kavle vat t…®gam…®n.  
\v 26 Ana n…®nd…®mba n…®ma ndandang…® kwaand…®. M…®n kat yindeya yamb…® kai. N…®n kat yameya yamb…® kai. Ndandang…® kwaand…® waa wand…® Ebraham. Wand…® maa sanyo la nyan wand…®.   
\p
\v 27 Ngwak, k…®ta nyaang…®t m…®n kat wagalagiyowun. Lasaras kat wam…®n maa wuna nyaekna ngay yigand…®.  
\v 28 Kan ngaymba wuna yakwa ndu tambanat t…®gandi. Ndi kat mbutnd…® maa wutaa tuwa kavle kava ana yaigandi waa wand…® maa Ebraham nd…® kat wand…®.   
\p
\v 29 Tamba Moses kwiya nyaang…®t profet waa nyaang…®t ng…®l…®ga. Kan nyaang…®t wutaa kavle vat kwagalalaa t…®ma kavle kava ana yigiyandi waa wand…®, sanya la nyan wand…®.  
\v 30 Walanga Ebraham wupma kai. Wuna yakwa ndu tambanat tamba la nyaang…®t ana wukiyandi. K…®ta nyan kiyalaa laataa ndi kat mbutndeyan ndi kavle maawut kwagalalaa mand…®p kupi maawut klalaa apma vat yiga yet…®giyandi waa wand…®.  
\v 31 Wand…® mala Ebraham nd…® kat wand…®. Wama vak ana nglaatnd…®. Tamba Moses kwiya nyaang…®t profet mbuta nyaang…®t wupmak kat kai wanjeyan k…®ta nyan kiyalaa laataa ndi kat yiga mbutnjeyan nd…®no nd…® kat wupmak kat kai waigandi waa wand…® Ebraham waa mbutnd…® Jisas.   
\c 17  
\s1 NG∆óNI YAIGA KAVLE VAT  
\p
\v 1 Jisas nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat wand…®. Ng…®ni yaiga kavle vat yand…® maa nat n…®ma sakwat n…®mba kavle maawupmba yelav…®ka kavle savle yiga yet…®giyandi. Wan kavle vat yaigand…®. Wan ng…®ni yaiga kavle vat kwivat yal…®ga nyan nd…® kat miwa yigowun. Nd…® kavle nyanat t…®giyand…®.  
\v 2 Wan kavle vat kwivat yaiga nyan wand…® maa wuna mbaapma n…®mbana maawut kavle yigiyand…®. Tak nd…®na mbanj…®ge n…®ma kambak yaawmba tulaa nyingi ngumba yaaginjeyan wovuna. Ngumba yaaginjeyan ng…®ni wuna mbaapma n…®mbana maawut ana kavle yigiyand…®.   
\p
\v 3 Ngwuk kavle vat kwivat yaiga nyan yeta vak vla wupma ke yet…®ngwa. Ngwuk apma vak yet…® ngwula. Ngwula mbaapmamba la k…®ta nyan ngwuk kat kavle vat yindeyan nd…® kat awa. Kavle vat yim…®n waa awa. Wangwuk maa wovun wangwuk. Ngwuk kat kavle vat yuwa vat tamba kwagalawun waa wandeyan ngwuk kat kavle vat yinda vak kat maawut ke yelav…®ka. Kwagala ngwula.  
\v 4 Nandinya k…®ta s…®la v…®li njamb…® ngwuk kat kavle vat yilaa kavle vat yuwa vat kwagalagiyowun waa wandeyan kavle vat yil…®nda vak kat kwagala ngwula. Ke yelav…®kngwa waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 JISAS KAT MAAWUPMBA YELAV∆óKA KWUTA L∆óNJA VAK  
\p
\v 5 Jisasna mbaapma n…®mba nd…® kat wandi. M…®na nyaang…®t kat maawupmba yelav…®ka kwuta l…®na vak matna. N…®na maawut kwunapm…®n mala n…®man yigiyand…® waa wandi maa Jisas wand…®.  
\v 6 Wuna nyaang…®t maawupmba yelav…®ka kwutaa l…®ngweya vat tagula vatna. Tagula ava l…®ga vatna. Mastet wal…®nja mi s…®k mak glei nda. Tundi, n…®ma ava yil…®gand…®. Wuna nyaang…®t kat kwutaa l…®ngwa vak mastet wal…®nja s…®k vla t…®ndeyan n…®ma nglei nj…®vwa kwukiyand…®. Wangwuk mala kan t…®ga v…®l…®ngwa mi avla p…®taa nyingi nguat yigiyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 GODNA NJ∆óVWA KWUT∆óNA VAT  
\p
\v 7 Jisas wand…®. Ngwutna k…®ta nyan kwanda kwanda nda vla l…®ga nj…®vwa kwo kwuta nyan t…®ndeyan wam…®n maa nandinya ambugatna nj…®vwa kwupmat yigiyand…®. Kwutaa bulmakau kat yuwi kal…®taa kwigiyand…®. Nglaambu nj…®vwa ng…®l…®laa kwagalalaa yand…®, nd…® kat k…®g…®nda kwukiyam…®n? Ndaa l…®ga yaa ag…® waa waigam…®n? Kai. Wupma ana waigam…®n.  
\v 8 Kupma waigam…®n. M…®n wuna k…®g…®nda kwutaa kiyaa taagam…®n k…®lu. K…®wun maa ng…®ni k…®giyam…®n waa nd…® kat waigam…®n.  
\v 9 Wama nj…®vwa kwutnd…® maa nd…® kat s…®vu k…®giyam…®n? Kai luwa. Wan nj…®vwa kwuta nyan m…®na kwanda kwanda nda vla l…®gand…®.  
\v 10 N…®no n…®mbun. God wanda nj…®vwa aywaa kwutaa nd…® kat waigan…®n. N…®n n…®ma sakwat nj…®vwa ana kwutn…®n. Apma vak ana kwutn…®n waa waigan…®n.   
\s1 KAAWIA K∆óLA TAMBA V∆óLI N∆óMBA KAT JISAS KWUNATND∆ó  
\p
\v 11 T…®ga l…®ga Jisas Jerusalemat yind…®. Yinda ava yamb…® k…®pma angang…® t…®mb…®k n…®nd…®mba yind…®. Nat naang…® Galili wal…®nja k…®pma. Nat naang…® Sameria wal…®nja k…®pma.  
\v 12 Ngepma wuleilaa ndina mbang…® aywaa kaawia k…®la tamba v…®li n…®mba s…®vlamba l…®ndi, v…®nd…®.  
\v 13 Ndi nd…® kat v…®laa n…®ma kwundimba wandi. Jisas, njambwi nyan m…®n, n…®n kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®p m…®la waa wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®.  
\v 14 Ay ngwula. Ngwutna mbang…® kwo l…®giyand…®. God kat kwunat…®ga nyan kat ngwutna mbang…® s…®magangwuk mala apma vat t…®ngwa vak nat n…®mba kat mbukiyand…® waa wand…®, yindi. Yil…®ndi maa ndina mbang…® apma vat t…®nd…®.  
\v 15 Ndina k…®ta nyan nd…®na mbang…® kwo l…®nda vak v…®laa lungwamataa yiga n…®ma kwundimba Godna s…® kwutaa katsond…®.  
\v 16 Wan nyan yalaa Jisas kat s…®vu k…®vat kwali man s…®laa nd…® kat s…®vu k…®nd…®. Nd…® Sameriana kapma ngepma nyana.  
\v 17 Jisas wand…®. K…®ta nyan m…®na ana kwunakwun. Tamba v…®li n…®mb…® andamapba l…®ngandi.  
\v 18 Ndi Godna s…® katsovat ana lungwamataa yandi. Kan kapma ngepma nyan m…®na yand…® waa walaa nd…® kat wand…®.  
\v 19 M…®n laataa ay m…®la. Wuna nyaang…®t wutaa maawupmba yelav…®ka kwutaa l…®ma vak m…®n kat kwunatnd…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 GOD NDINYANGU KAT V∆óGA L∆óNDEYA VAK YAIGAND∆ó  
\p
\v 20 God ndinyangu kat v…®ga l…®ndeya vak anda nj…®mbla yaigand…® waa Ferisi wagalandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. God ndinyangu kat v…®ga l…®ndeya vat m…®nimba ana v…®giyan…®n.  
\v 21 K…®ta nyan ana yand…® v…®laa waigand…®. Angwiyan yaa v…®gowun waa ana waigand…®. God ndinyangu kat v…®ga l…®ndeya vak ngwutna maawupmba l…®gand…® waa ndi kat walaa nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat wand…®.  
\v 22 Ng…®ni yaiga nj…®mbla n…®ma sakwat kavle vat yaigand…®. Ngwuk kat kwunapmak Godna vak s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan kwakiyangwuk. Wun ana yaigowun.  
\v 23 Nat n…®mba ndino kwaka waigandi. Ngiya yaa. Anguvelia yaa waa waigandi. ndina nyaang…®t ke wuka. Ndina kwupmba ke yiga waa ngwuk kat wowun.  
\v 24 Wun Godna vak s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan ngwuk kat kwunapmak yaweyan vlap vlap wand…®, ya vla yaigowun. Yaweya nj…®mbla kava kava kembagiyand…®.  
\v 25 Tak wun kat n…®ma vak yaigand…®. Mbambala l…®ga n…®mba tak wun kat kai waigandi.   
\p
\v 26 Ndinyangu kat Godna vak s…®mogwiga kwunapmat yaweya nj…®mbla kan k…®pmana n…®mba tamba Noa ta nj…®mblamba kavle vat yiga yet…®nja vla yiga yet…®giyandi.  
\v 27 Tamba God kat yelev…®tapman nao ngu k…®ga taagwa klaga kwo yet…®ndi. T…®ga l…®ga Noa njaamb…®t kund…® maa n…®ma sambiyangu yand…®, kiyandi.  
\v 28 Tamba la nyan Lot ta nj…®mbla wupma l…®ndi. Ndi nao ngu kwo k…®ndi. Wenga kwilaa klandi. Ambugatna nj…®vwa kwo kwutndi. Ngay kwo kwutndi.  
\v 29 T…®ga l…®ga Lot Sodom wal…®nja ngepma wogwend…® mala ny…®nangwupmba la ya v…®t…®ga kambak ngepma ndaind…®, ndi kiyandi.  
\v 30 Ndinyangu kat Godna vak s…®mogwiga ndi kat kwunapmak yaweya nj…®mbla wan vak t…®giyand…®.   
\p
\v 31 Wan yaiga nj…®mbla sambangemba l…®giya nyan ana ndaigiyand…® nd…®na ngaymba l…®ga kwanda kwanda klavat. Kwo yigiyand…®. Ambugapmba t…®giya nyan nd…®no nd…®na kwanda kwanda klavat ana yaigand…®. Kwo yigiyand…®.  
\v 32 Tamba la nyan Lot nd…®na taagwa kavle vat yila vak kat yelav…®k ngwula.  
\v 33 Wan yaiga nj…®mbla k…®ga nyan nd…®na mbang…® nd…®na nda kat yelav…®ka l…®ndeyan nd…® kavle yigiyand…®. K…®ta nyan nd…®na mbang…® nd…®na nda kat yelav…®tapman yindeyan nd…® kwo l…®giyand…®.   
\p
\v 34 Wan yaweya nj…®mbla ngay k…®ta ndu v…®l…®l…®k kwaigamb…®t. Yalaa nat nyan kat kwutaa kaligiywoun. Nat nyan t…®giyand…®.  
\v 35 Wan yaweya nj…®mbla taagwa v…®l…®l…®k k…®ta kavamba nj…®vwa kwukiyamb…®t. Yalaa nat taagwa kat kwutaa kaligiywoun. Nat taagwa t…®giyal…®.  
\v 36 (Ndu v…®l…®l…®k ambugapmba l…®giyamb…®t. Yalaa nat ndu kat kwutaa kaligiyowun. Nat ndu t…®giyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.)   
\p
\v 37 Wand…® mala nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba nd…® kat wagalandi. Wama kavle vak anda kavamba kak kiyaigand…® waa wagalandi, Jisas wand…®. Nat t…®giya kavamba k…®ta nda wundumbu yilaa njangu veil…®nd…®, ambugavi v…®laa nj…®ngwenga l…®ga ndaiga veilaa k…®giyandi waa wand…® Jisas.   
\c 18  
\s1 KAVLE JASNA WAPUSEPUT  
\p
\v 1 Jisas ndi kat pagwula la nyaang…®t mbutnd…®. God kat nj…®mbla nj…®mbla wagala l…®njangat mbutnd…®. God kat wagalal…®nja vak kwagala lapman yinjangat mbutnd…®.  
\v 2 Tamba nat ngepmamba jas k…®ta l…®nd…®. Nd…® God waa nyaang…®t ana wuka l…®nd…®. Nat n…®mbana nyaang…®t ana wut…®nd…®.  
\v 3 Kan ngepmamba la talagwa nd…® kat yalaa wal…®. K…®ta nyan wun kat kavle vat yil…®gand…®. Nd…® kat kai awa wal…®.  
\v 4 Nd…® l…®la nyaang…®t ana wutnd…®. L…® nj…®mbla nj…®mbla yiga wal…®l…®. T…®ga l…®ga kavle jas wand…®. God waa nyaang…®t ana wuka l…®gowun. Nat n…®mbana nyaang…®t ana wuka ligowun.  
\v 5 Wat talagwa n…®ma sakwat njamb…® wun kat wal…®l…®. L…®la nyaang…®t nat njamb…® wupmak kat wuna mbang…® k…®l…®pang…® yigand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga l…® kat kavle vat yila nyan kat kai waigowun waa wand…® kavle jas waa mbutnd…® Jisas.  
\v 6 Mbutaa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Kavle jas waa nyaang…®t kat yelav…®k ngwula.  
\v 7-12 God nd…® kavle nyan ana nd…®. Nd…®na n…®mba nd…® kat nandinya ngan wagalanjeyan ndi kat kavle vat ya n…®mba kat God kai waigand…®. Nd…® ana wutapman kwo kawiga l…®giyand…®.  
\v 13 Nat nyan takis sanya klal…®ga nyan s…®vla kavamba l…®ga nambu s…®landalaa God kat wand…®. Avla nd…®na s…® l…®ga nambu s…®landalaa God kat wand…®. Avla nd…®na s…® viyesendaga mawlava viyaga wand…®. Wun kavle nyan wun. Kavle vat yiluwa vak kat ke yelav…®ka waa God kat wand…® waa mbutnd…® Jisas. Mbutaa ndi kat wand…®.   
\p
\v 14 Ngwuk kat wowun. God takis sanyo klal…®ga nyan waa nyaang…®t wutaa nd…® kat wand…®. Kavle vat yil…®ma vak kat ana yelav…®ka l…®gowun. Kwagalagiyowun waa God wand…®. Wand…® maa nd…®na ngayat yind…®. Ferisi wupma kai. God Ferisina kavle vak ana kwagaland…®. Yinja vla n…®no wupma. N…®n avla n…®na s…® viyesendaneyan God kwutaa katsogiyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 MAT NYANGU JISAS KAT KIYANJA WUPUSEPUT  
\p
\v 15 Nat n…®mba ndina mat nyangu kat Jisas kat kiyal…®ndi. Ndina mbang…®mba taamba taagandangat kiyal…®ndi. Jisasna mbaapma n…®mba kiyal…®njangat kai wa wandi. Ke kiya waa wandi.  
\v 16 Kai wandi mala Jisas wupma ke waa mat nyangu agiya wand…®. Mat nyangu wuna lak yaandi. Ndi kat kai ke waa. God v…®ga l…®ga n…®mba Godna mat nyangu vla l…®gandi.  
\v 17 Ngwuk kat wowun. Mat nyangu nyaang…®t wutaa maawupmba yelav…®ka n…®mamba kwutaa l…®gandi. Kwutaa l…®nja vak vla ngwuk kwutapman yingweyan God v…®ga l…®ga kava ana wuleigiyangwuk waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 APMA VAT KLANEYA YAMB∆ó  
\p
\v 18 Kan ngepmana njambwi nyan Jisas kat yalaa wand…®. Nyaang…®t s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan m…®n apma nyan m…®n. Anda nj…®vwa kwutaa nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vak yet…®weya vak klaigowun waa wand…® mala Jisas nd…® kat wand…®.  
\v 19 Apma nyan m…®n waa manda kat wun kat wam…®n. K…®pmamba l…®ga n…®mba apma nyan ana l…®gand…®. Apma nyan k…®ta l…®gand…®. Nd…® Godna.  
\v 20 Tamba Moses kwiya nyaang…®t v…®ga l…®gam…®n. Yamb…®s…®k yil…®nja vak ke yiga. Nat nyan kat ke vatnyaga. Nat nyana nda ke s…®kwuka. Nyaang…®t woseka ke waa. Nyaek ny…®mena nyaang…®t awuk waa tamba Moses p…®l…®wutnd…®. M…®n wupma yigiyam…®n waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 21 Mat nyan t…®ga wupma yil…®wun waa Jisas kat wand…®.  
\v 22 Jisas wanda nyaang…®t wutaa nd…® kat wand…®. Apma vat k…®ta ana yim…®n. M…®na kwanda kwanda nda aywaa kwilaa sanya klalaa sanya lapman n…®mba kat agwi m…®la. Kwilaa wuna kwupmba yagwa. Wupma yimeyan m…®na nyinangwupmba l…®ga wenga nda n…®ma sakwat t…®giyand…®. Ng…®ni ny…®nangwut yilaa klaigam…®n waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 23 Nd…® Jisasna nyaang…®t wutaa nd…®na mbang…® k…®l…®pang…® yind…®. Nd…® Jisasna nyaang…®t wutaa nd…®na mbang…® k…®l…®pang…® yind…®. Nd…® n…®ma sakwat kwanda kwanda ta nyana.   
\p
\v 24 Nd…®na mbang…® k…®l…®pang…® yinda vak Jisas v…®laa wand…®. N…®ma sakwat sanya la nyan God v…®ga l…®ga kava wuleivat yindeyan n…®ma nj…®vwa.  
\v 25 N…®ma kamel waavwi taval…®nja nilna yamb…® vla wuleivat yindeyan n…®ma nj…®vwa. N…®ma sakwat sanya la nyan God v…®ga l…®ga kava wuleivat yindeyan n…®ma nglei nj…®vwa. Kamel wuleigiya nj…®vwa kat kwulat…®gand…® waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 26 Jisas waa nyaang…®t wuta n…®mba wandi. God v…®ga l…®ga kava k…®ta nyan anda vapmba wuleigiyand…®. Yamb…® kai kava k…®ta nyan anda vapmba wuleigiyand…®. Yamb…® kai waa wandi mala Jisas wand…®.  
\v 27 Ndi ndina nj…®vwamba ana wuleigiyandi. God ndi kat kwutaa kaliga taagagiyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 28 Pita laataa wand…®. N…®n kwanda kwanda nda aywaa kwagalalaa m…®na kwupmba yin…®n waa wand…®.  
\v 29 Wand…® maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. K…®ta nyan wuna kwupmba yavat nd…®na ngepma, nyaek ny…®me, nyangu, yakwa n…®mba kat kwagalandeyan  
\v 30 mbambala apma wenga nda klaigand…®. Ng…®ni nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat yindeya vat klaigand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 KIYALAA LAAKIYOWUN WAA WAND∆ó JISAS  
\p
\v 31 Jisas nd…®na taamba v…®li kiyeli v…®l…®l…®k mbaapma n…®mba kat wand…®. Jerusalemat wokegat. Wun Godna vak s…®mogwiya nyan yiweya vak kat tamba la profet p…®l…®wutndi. Tamba p…®l…®wutnja vak mbambala glei tamba kak kiyal…®gand…®.  
\v 32 Wun kat kwutaa Juda ana ndi nat n…®mba kat kaligiyandi. Wun kat nj…®ka waigandi. Wun kat kavle vat yiga s…®pmiya saga l…®giyandi.  
\v 33 Wun kat viyaga vatnyagiyandi. Kiyalaa nandinya kuvuk t…®ga laakiyowun waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 34 Nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba mbuta nyaang…®t wutaa nyaang…®tna angwa ana yelav…®ka l…®ndi. Anda vak kat wal…®gand…® waa yelav…®ka l…®ndi.   
\s1 M∆óNI V∆óLAPMAN NYAN KAT JISAS KWUNATND∆ó  
\p
\v 35 Wata yilandi. Yiga Jeriko wal…®nja ngepma ngwaymba yil…®ndi. Way ava yamb…®mba m…®ni v…®lapman nyan ndaa l…®nd…®. Ndaa l…®ga sanya kat yawil…®nd…®.  
\v 36 N…®ma sakwat n…®mba yal…®ndi, wutnd…®. Wutaa nada kakna waa wagaland…®, mbutndi.  
\v 37 Jisas Nasaret nyan ngi yaa. Nd…®na kwupmba n…®ma sakwat n…®mba yal…®ndi, wukam…®n waa mbutndi.  
\v 38 M…®ni v…®lapman nyan n…®ma kwundimba walega wand…®. Jisas Devitna yelang…® nyan m…®n wun kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®p m…®la waa walega wand…®.  
\v 39 Jisasogwinala tata yila n…®mba nd…® kat kai wandi. Makayak ke waa wandi. Nd…® ndina nyaang…®t ana wutnd…®. Nd…® walega wand…®. Jisas Devitna yelang…® nyan m…®n wun kat maawut yelav…®p m…®la waa wand…®.  
\v 40 Jisas tamata nd…® kat kwutaa agiya wand…®. Kiyandi maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®.  
\v 41 Manda yawangat wam…®n waa wand…®, njambwi nyan wuna m…®ni kwunapmangat wowun waa wand…®.  
\v 42 Jisas wand…®. M…®ni v…®giyam…®n. Njambwi nyanat tuwa vat m…®na maawupmba yelav…®t…®ma vak m…®n kat kwunatnd…® waa wand…® maa  
\v 43 nd…®na m…®ni v…®nd…®. M…®ni v…®ga Jisasna kwupmba yiga Godna s…® kwutaa katsond…®. Va n…®mba ndino Godna s…® kwutaa katsondi.   
\c 19  
\s1 SAKIAS WAL∆óNJA NYAN  
\p
\v 1 Yiga l…®ga Jeriko wal…®nja ngepma wuleindi.  
\v 2 Kan ngepmamba Sakias wal…®nja nyan yet…®nd…®. Nd…® takis sanya klal…®ga n…®mbana njambwi nyana. Nd…® n…®ma sakwat sanya la nyana.  
\v 3 Jisas yand…®, nd…® kat v…®vat yind…®. Nd…® anda vat t…®ga nyana waa yelav…®taa nd…® kat v…®vat yind…®. N…®ma sakwat n…®mba yisolaa t…®ndi, ana v…®nd…®. Nd…® tamb…® nyana.  
\v 4 Yindeya yamb…®mba tata p…®l…®ga yiga Jisas yindeya yamb…® waymba la sikamoa wal…®nja mi wokelaa kawiga kwand…®.  
\v 5 Jisas wan angwa mimba yaga yisoga v…®nd…®. V…®laa wand…®. Sakias kwiyatapman ndai m…®la. Mbambala ngan m…®na ngaymba kwaigowun waa wand…® maa  
\v 6 Sakias kwiyatapman ndailaa solat s…®ga Jisas nd…®na ngayat kalind…®.  
\v 7 Nat n…®mba v…®laa wal…®ndi. Jisas kavle vat yind…®. Sakias kavle nyana. Manda kat nd…®na ngaymba kwavat yigand…® waa wal…®ndi.  
\v 8 Ngaymba l…®ga Sakias Jisas kat wand…®. Njambwi nyan kavle yetuwa vak kwagalagiywoun. Wuna kwanda kwanda nda mbaapma v…®l…®l…®k taagalaa nat mbaapma sanya lapman n…®mba kat kwigiyowun. Woseka waa klawa sanya awat ndi kat aynat njamb…® kwigiywoun waa wand…® mala Jisas nd…® kat wand…®.  
\v 9 Mbambala kavle vat kwagalalaa apma vat klam…®n. Tamba la nyan Ebraham apma vat yinda vla yil…®gam…®n.  
\v 10 Wun Godna vak s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan wun. Wun kavle n…®mba kat kwaka kwunapmak ngaga yawun kan k…®pma. Apma n…®mba kai waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 YILAA YA KINGNA PAGWULA LA NYAANG∆óT  
\p
\v 11 Jisas waa nyaang…®t wutndi maa ndi kat pagwula la nyaang…®t mbutnd…®. Ndi Jerusalem ngwaymba t…®ga, nd…®nogwi l…®ga n…®mba yelav…®tndi. Samat t…®ga Jisas laataa njambwi nyana nj…®vwa kwuka ngepma ngepmana n…®mba kat v…®ga l…®giyand…® waa yelav…®tndi. Yelav…®tnja vak wutaa Jisas yelav…®tnd…®. Yelav…®tnja vak ana nglaatnd…®. Samat t…®ga njambwi nyana nj…®vwa ana kwukiyowun. Ng…®ni kwukiyowun waa yelav…®taa Jisas ndi kat pagwula la nyaang…®t mbutnd…®. Mbuka wand…®.  
\v 12 Tamba s…®vla kavamba la sanyo la nyan nd…®na angwa ngepma kwagalalaa nat kavat yivat wand…®. Yindfa ngepmana njambwi nyan wand…® maa nd…®na angwa ngepmana njambwi nyanat t…®giyand…®. Ngi kat t…®ga nd…® kat wagalavat yind…®.  
\v 13 Nd…®na kat k…®ta nyan k…®ta nyan 20 dola 20 dola kwigiyowun. Ngwuk sanyamba nj…®vwa kwukiyangwuk. Ng…®ni ngwuk kat v…®vat yaigowun waa walaa yind…®.   
\p
\v 14 Yind…® mala nd…®na nagwa ngepmamba la n…®mba wandi. Wan nyan n…®na njambwi nyanat t…®ndangat nj…®ka kai wan…®n. Nat n…®mba kat wandi maa sanyo la nyana kwupmba yilaa nd…® kat v…®laa mbutndi. M…®na angwa ngepma ndina njambwi nyanat t…®mangat nj…®ka kai wandi waa mbutndi.   
\p
\v 15 T…®ga l…®ga sanyo la nyan yand…®. Nat ngepmana njambwi nyan wand…® maa njambwi nyanat t…®nd…®. Yalaa nd…®na nj…®vwa kwuta n…®mba kat yagwa wand…®. Ngwuk kat kwiwa sanya angamak sakwat t…®gand…® waa wagaland…®,  
\v 16 tat ta nyan laataa wand…®. Kwima 20 dola nj…®vwa kwukwun, tamba n…®man yind…®. 200 dola ngi l…®ga waa wand…®. Njambwi nyan wand…®.  
\v 17 Apma vak nj…®vwa kwupm…®n. M…®n kat mat nj…®vwa apma vat kwut…®m…®n. Ngi kat t…®ga ngepma tamba v…®li v…®ga l…®giyam…®n waa wand…®.   
\p
\v 18 Nat nyan laataa wand…®. Njambwi nyan wun kat kwima 20 dola nj…®vwa kwukwun tamba n…®man yind…®. Mbambala 100 dola t…®gand…® waa wand…®,  
\v 19 njambwi nyan wand…®. m…®n ngepma tambanat v…®ga l…®giyam…®n waa wand…®.  
\v 20 Nat nyan laataa wand…®. Wun kat kwima 20 dola ngiyan t…®ga. Waavwimba ngilaa pagwuwun.  
\v 21 M…®n kat vaaka l…®wun. M…®n kao mbund…® nyan m…®n. Nat nyan yisoga taaganda nda m…®na kao s…®g…®t…®gam…®n. Ngi kat t…®ga kwo pagwuwun, t…®gand…® waa wand…® maa  
\v 22 njambwi nyan wand…®. M…®n kavle vat y…®m…®n. Kao mbund…® tuwa vak v…®ga l…®gam…®n. Nat nyan yisoga taaganda nda kwo klaluwa vak v…®ga l…®gam…®n. Nat nyan ambugapmba tunda nda kwo s…®g…®tuwa vak v…®ga l…®gam…®n.  
\v 23 Sanya manda kat kwo kwuta l…®m…®n. Bengmba taagageman samat n…®man yigend…®. Kavle vat yim…®n waa walaa  
\v 24 kumba la nat nyan kat wand…®. Nd…®na 20 dola kwutaa 200 dola l…®ga nyanat agwi waa wand…®,  
\v 25 nat n…®mba wandi. Wama vak ana nglaatnd…®. 200 dola tamba kwutaa l…®gand…®. Manda kat nat 20 dola nd…® kat agwi wam…®n waa wandi.   
\p
\v 26 Njambwi nyan wand…®. Kavle vat ana nd…®. Yiluwa vat k…®ngiyand…®. Kwutaa la nyan nd…® kat kwigiyowun. Kwutapman nyan nd…®na mat nda nd…®namba klalaa n…®ma sakwat kwuta la nyan kat kwil…®gowun.  
\v 27 Wun kat tak kai waa n…®mba n…®na njambwi nyanat ana l…®giyand…® waa wun kat waa n…®mba kat kwutaa agiya. Kiyalaa ndi kat v…®ga l…®wun, vatnyagiyangwuk waa wand…® njambwi nyan waa mbutnd…® Jisas.   
\s1 JISAS JERUSALEM WULEIND∆ó  
\p
\v 28 Wapuseput mbutaa Jisas Jerusalemat wokend…®. Nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba nd…®na kwupmba wokendi.  
\v 29 Yiga l…®ga Betfasi wal…®nja ngepma Betani wal…®nja ngepma ngwaymba l…®ndi. Oliv wal…®nja nduwi ngwaymba l…®ga Jisas nd…®na mbaapmamba la v…®l…®l…®k pal…® kat tata ay wand…® maa tata yimb…®t.  
\v 30 Jisas mb…®k kat wand…®. Ngwaymba l…®ga ngepma wulei mb…®la. Wuleilaa yaawmba ng…®nja donki v…®giyamb…®k. Nd…® nyan donkia. Nd…®na mbunimba ndu nyan ana ndaa l…®nd…®. Nd…® kat yaaw njalataa agiya.  
\v 31 K…®ta nyan mb…®k kat manda kat yaaw njalat…®gamb…®t waa wandeyan nd…® kat awamba mb…®t. Njambwi nyan wand…® maa njalat…®gaa waa awa waa Jisas wand…® maa yimb…®k.   
\p
\v 32-33 Ngepma wuleilaa Jisas waa kwanda kwanda v…®mb…®t. V…®laa donkina yaaw njalat…®mb…®t maa donki v…®ga la nyan yalaa wand…®. Manda kat yaaw njalat…®gamb…®k waa wand…® maa  
\v 34 njambwi nyan wand…®, njalat…®gaa wamb…®t.  
\v 35 Nd…® kat walaa Jisas kat kalimb…®t. Donkina mbunimba ndina alagu waavwi taagal…®ndi, Jisas donkina mbunimba ndaa l…®nd…®. Ndaa l…®ga Jerusalemat yindi.  
\v 36 Yil…®nja ava yamb…® nat n…®mba ndina alagu waavwi taagal…®ndi donki veindangat.  
\v 37 Oliv wal…®nja nambu nduwimba l…®ga ngepma ndaivat yil…®ndi, nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba n…®ma sakwat yalaa n…®ma kwundimba solat s…®ga Godna s…® kwutaa katsol…®ndi. Tak Jisas n…®ma nj…®vwa kwunata nj…®vwa kwutnd…®, v…®laa solat s…®l…®ndi.  
\v 38 Kupma wal…®ndi. God wand…® maa Jisas n…®na kingat t…®vat yand…®. Apma vatna. Ny…®nangwupmba l…®ga njambwi nyan n…®n kat apma vat yind…®. Nd…®na s…® kwutaa katsol…®gan…®n waa wal…®ndi.   
\p
\v 39 Wal…®nja nyaang…®t wumba la Ferisi wutaa Jisas kat wandi. S…®mogwi l…®ga nyan m…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat makayak waa awamba m…®n waa wandi.  
\v 40 Wandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Ndi kat wupma makayak waga waweyan kan t…®ga kambak wuna mbaapma n…®mba wal…®ga vak waigandi waa Jisas ndi kat wand…®.   
\p
\v 41 Ngepma ngwaymba l…®ga ngepma v…®laa ngepma n…®mba kat n…®ma maawut yelav…®ka nglaga wand…®.  
\v 42 Tak apma vat yiga yet…®njeya vak ana v…®ga l…®ngwuk. Mbambala ngepma wuleiwun, v…®ga l…®ngweya wovuna. Ana v…®ga l…®giyangwuk. V…®l…®gowun. Ngwuk m…®ni v…®lapman n…®mba vla l…®gangwuk.  
\v 43 Ng…®ni yaiga nj…®mbla ngwuk kat s…®vat yil…®ga n…®mba yaigandi. Yalaa ngepma wegwuga waangu vigiyandi. Vandi maa ana ngepma wogwegiyangwuk.  
\v 44 Ngwuk kat aywaa s…®giyandi. N…®ma n…®mba mat nyangu taagwa aywaa s…®giyandi. Ngepma sul…®giyandi. Sul…®ndi maa ngay kambak nat kambatna tagumba ana l…®giyand…®. Kapma kapma l…®giyandi. God wand…® maa ngwuk kat kwunapmat ywwa vak v…®lapman t…®l…®gangwuk. Ngi kat t…®ga kavle vat ngwuk kat yagand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 45 Ngepma yilaa Godna ngay wuleind…®. Kan ngaymba nat n…®mba wenga kwiga klal…®ndi. Jisas wuleilaa ndi kat kwutaa k…®kliga wand…®.  
\v 46 Tamba wan ngay kat God wand…® maa p…®l…®wutndi.  
\li1 Wuna ngay wuleia n…®mba wun kat ngambuvat  
\li1 wuleigiyandi waa wand…® God  
\p waa tamba p…®l…®wutndi. Ngwuk wupma kai. Nat n…®mbana nda s…®kwuka wenga kwiga klal…®gangwuk waa ndi kat wand…®.   
\p
\v 47 Jisas nandinya nandinya Godna ngay wuleilaa nyaang…®t mbut…®nd…®. God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mba, Moses kwiya nyaang…®t s…®mogwi la n…®mba, nat njambwi n…®mba ndi Jisas kat vatnyavak yelav…®ka l…®ndi.  
\v 48 Vatnyanjeya vak ana yelav…®ka l…®ndi. Nat n…®ma sakwat n…®mba Jisas waa nyaang…®t wupmat woviyaguga l…®ndi. Njambwi n…®mba wundi n…®mba kat vaaka l…®ga Jisas kat vatnyanjeya vat ana yelav…®ka l…®ndi.   
\c 20  
\s1 KANDA WAND∆ó MALA NJ∆óVWA KWUT∆óGAM∆óN WAA JISAS KAT WAGALANDI  
\p
\v 1 Nat nandinya Jisas Godna ngay wuleilaa ndinyangu kat wan apma nyaang…®t mbut…®nd…®. Mbut…®nd…® mala God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mba, Moses kwiya nyaang…®t s…®mogwi la n…®mba, nat njambwi n…®mba nd…® kat yalaa wandi.  
\v 2 Kanda wand…® maa nj…®vwa kwuka nyaang…®t mbut…®gam…®n waa wandi maa wand…®.  
\v 3 Wun kat tamba wagalangwuk. Ngwuk kat k…®ta nyaang…®t wagalagiyowun. Awat wangwuk maa ngwuk maa ngwuk kat awat waigowun.  
\v 4 Ngu yagula Jon kanda wand…® maa ndinyangu kat ngu yagul…®nd…®. God wand…®? E? K…®pmana nyan wand…®? Waa ndi kat wagaland…®.  
\v 5 Wagaland…® maa ndi awat sowat ngambul…®ndi. God wand…®, Jon ndinyangu kat yagul…®ndi waa waneyan nd…® n…®n kat waigand…®. Ngwuk manda kat yagulapman t…®gangwuk waa waigand…®.  
\v 6 K…®pmana nyan wand…® maa Jon dinyangu kat yagul…®nd…® waa waneyan kan n…®ma sakwat n…®mba kambak yaagiga n…®n kat vatnyagiyandi. Wundi n…®ma sakwat n…®mba yelav…®t…®gandi. Jon God waa nyaang…®t mbut…®nd…® waa yelav…®ka l…®gandi waa awat sowat ngambulaa Jisas kat wandi.  
\v 7 Ana v…®ga l…®gan…®n waa wandi.  
\v 8 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Ngwuk kat wagalawa nyaang…®t ana awat wangwuk. Wuno wun kat wagalangwa nyaang…®t ana awat waigowun. Wand…®, nj…®vwa kwutuwa nyana s…® ana mbukiyowun waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 AMBUGAT KAT V∆óGA LA KAVLE N∆óMBA  
\p
\v 9 Jisas kumba la n…®mba kat pagwula la nyaang…®t mbut…®nd…®. Tamba la k…®ta nyan ambugat kwutnd…®. Kwutaa nat n…®mba kat v…®ga l…®njangat walaa s…®vla kavat yind…®.  
\v 10 Kwanda kwanda p…®l…®nja nj…®mbla nd…®na nj…®vwa kwuta nyan kat wand…®, ambugatna nat nda klavat yind…®. Ambugat yand…®, v…®ga la n…®mba nd…® kat viyaga savl…®ndi. Ambugatna nda ana kland…®.  
\v 11 T…®ga l…®ga ambugatna njambwi nyan nd…®na nj…®vwa kwuta nat nyan kat wand…®, yind…®. Yind…®, nd…® kat nj…®ka waga viyaga savl…®ndi, yind…®. Ambugatna nda ana kland…®.  
\v 12 T…®ga l…®ga ambugatna njambwi nyan nd…®na nj…®vwa kwuta nat nyan kat wand…®, yind…®. Nd…®no nd…® kat viyaga sav…®l…®ndi.  
\v 13 T…®ga l…®ga njambwi nyan yelav…®tnd…®. Wun angamak yigiyowun. Wuna nyan k…®ta l…®gand…®. Nd…® kat wowun maa yigiyand…®. Wuna nyanat t…®nda vak v…®laa nd…®na nyaang…®t wukiyandi waa yelav…®taa ay wand…®.  
\v 14 Ambugat v…®ga la n…®mba nyan v…®laa wandi. Ambugatna njambwi nyan kiyand…®, wan nyan ambugat kaligand…®. Nd…® kat vatnyaneyan n…®na lak klaigan…®n waa walaa nd…® kat savl…®laa vatnyandi.  
\v 15 Ambugatna njambwi nyan wutaa ndi kat yalaa vatnyagiyand…®. Ndi ng…®ni ambugatna nj…®vwa ana kwukiyandi. Njambwi nyan wand…® maa nat n…®mba kwukiyandi waa wand…® maa wuta n…®mba wandi. God n…®n kat n…®ma vat yiland…® waa wandi.   
\p
\v 16-17 Wandi maa Jisas wand…®. N…®ma vak yigiyand…® luwa. God ng…®ni ndinyangu kat yigiya n…®ma vak tamba la n…®mba p…®l…®wutndi. Kupma p…®l…®wutndi.  
\li1 Kambapmba ngay kwuta n…®mba nat kambak ngaymba  
\li1 taagavak kat kai walaa yaagindi. God yalaa  
\li1 yaaginja kambak kwutaa m…®ndama ngemba taagand…®.   
\li1
\v 18 K…®ta nyan kan kambak kat kai walaa man  
\li1 veindeyan nd…® ndaiga kavle yigiyand…®. Kambak ana  
\li1 kavle yigiyand…®. Tagula kambakna. Kan kambak  
\li1 ndaiga k…®ta nyan kat viyandeyan nd…® mbaw vla l…®ga  
\li1 n…®mamba nd…® kavle yigiyand…®  
\p waa tamba p…®l…® wutndi waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 19 God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mbo Moses kwiya nyaang…®t s…®mogwi la n…®mbo wutaa Jisas kat waleal…®ndi. Ndi wutaa yelav…®tndi. God ng…®ni ngwuk kat n…®ma vak yigiyand…® waa n…®n kat wupuseput mbuka wand…® walaa yelav…®taa Jisas kat waleal…®ndi. Walea l…®ga nd…® kat vaaka l…®ga nd…® kat ana kwutaa kalindi.   
\s1 TAKIS SANYA AGWI NGWULA WAA WAND∆ó JISAS  
\p
\v 20 Njambwi n…®mba Jisas yiga mbut…®nda vak yiga wuka v…®ga l…®ndi. Wandi mala ndina mbaapma n…®mba Jisas kat wagalvat yindi. Wagalangwuk mala nd…® kavle nyaang…®t awat wandeyan nd…® kat kwutaa kotmak kali ngwula waa wandi, yindi. Jisas kat yilaa m…®na mbaapma s…®vat yan…®n waa nd…® kat woseka wandi.  
\v 21 Nd…® kat woseka waga wal…®ndi. Njambwi nyan mbut…®ma nyaang…®t apma nyaang…®tna. V…®l…®gan…®n. Kan k…®pma n…®mbana nyaang…®t ana wutaa ndina kwupmba yil…®gam…®n. M…®n God waa nyaang…®t m…®na savagu but…®gam…®n. M…®n God waa nyaang…®t m…®na savagu mbut…®gam…®n. V…®l…®gan…®n.  
\v 22 M…®n kat k…®ta nyaang…®t wagalagiyan…®n. Gavmana njambwi nyan Sisa nd…® kat takis sanya kwineyan wovuna? E? Kai? Waa woseka wandi.  
\v 23 Woseka wagalanja vak v…®ga nd…®na maawupmba yelav…®taa wand…®. Manda kat wun kat wagalangwuk.  
\v 24 Wun kat sanya agwi wand…®, kwindi. Jisas sanya kwutaa l…®ga ndi kwa waa wand…® maa Sisanana wandi.  
\v 25 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Kat sanya Sisana nda. Takis sanya kat wagalandeyan nd…®na nda nd…® kat agwi ngwula. Godna nda God kat kwigiyangwuk waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 26 Wanda nyaang…®t wutaa kavle vat v…®lapman t…®ga ng…®paliga ndalaa kwundi awat ana wandi.   
\s1 SADYUSI JISAS KAT WAGALANDI  
\p
\v 27 Sadyusi wal…®nja mbaapmana nat n…®mba Jisas kat wagalavat yandi. Kiya n…®mba ng…®ni ana laakiyandi waa ndina mbbapma n…®mba yelav…®ka l…®ndi.  
\v 28 Yalaa wandi. Njambwi nyan, tamba Moses n…®n kat p…®l…®wutnd…®. Nyamwun wat taagwa kat klalaa nyan tapman t…®ga l…®ga kiyandeyan nd…®na sambu wat taagwa klalaa nyan njaang…® waa p…®l…®wutnd…® Moses.  
\v 29 Tamba yakwa ndu s…®la v…®li t…®ndi. Ndina njambwi nyan taagwa klalaa nyan tapman t…®ga l…®ga kiyand…®.  
\v 30 Kiyand…®, nd…®na kwupmba la nyan kland…®. T…®ga l…®ga nd…®no nyan tapman t…®ga kiyand…®.  
\v 31 Kiyand…® maa nd…®na kwupmba la nyan kuvuk wan nyan wat taagwa kat kland…®. T…®ga l…®ga nyan tapman t…®ga kiyand…®.  
\v 32 Ndi aywaa kiyandi mala wat taagwa kiyal…®.  
\v 33 Wundumbu ya n…®mba laatnjeya nj…®mbla kana taawat t…®giyal…®. Tat ndu s…®la v…®li l…® kat kalandi waa Jisas kat wagalandi.   
\p
\v 34 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Kan k…®pmamba t…®ga n…®mba ndi taagwa klal…®gandi.  
\v 35 God woviyaguga t…®nda n…®mba ndi nyinangwut wokegiyandi. Ng…®ni kiya n…®mba laakiyandi. Ndi ny…®nangwupmba l…®ga taagwa ana klal…®gandi.  
\v 36 Ndi ana wundumba yigiyandi. Ensel yet…®nja vla yet…®giyandi. Ndi kiyalaa laataa Godna nyanguat t…®giyandi.  
\v 37 Kiya n…®mba ng…®ni laaiyandi. Moses wupma mbuka p…®l…®wutnd…®. Tamba Moses ya v…®t…®ga mi v…®laa God kat wand…®. Ebraham Aisak Jekop m…®na kwundi wuka l…®gandi. M…®n ndina njambwia waa tamba wand…® Moses.  
\v 38 God kiya l…®ga n…®mbana njambwi nyan ana nd…®. Nd…® kwo l…®ga n…®mbana njambwi nyana. Ngi kat t…®ga Ebraham Aisak Jekop ana kiyalaa l…®gandi. Kiyalaa laatndi. V…®l…®gan…®n waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 39 Moses kwiya nyaang…®t s…®mogwi la nat n…®mba wutaa wandi. Njambwi nyan ngiyambak wama waa wandi.  
\v 40 Wandi maa nat n…®mba nd…® kat wagalavak kat vaaka l…®ndi.   
\s1 KRAIST DEVITNA NJAMBWIA  
\p
\v 41 T…®ga l…®ga Jisas ndi kat wagaland…®. Kraist wal…®na nyan God wand…®, ndinyangu kat kwunapmak yaa nyan nd…® Devitna mat nyana waa manda kat wal…®gandi. Ana nglaatnd…® wal…®nja vak.  
\v 42 Devit nd…®no Sam wal…®nja nyaang…®pmba God Kraist kat wanda nyaang…®t p…®l…®wutnd…®.  
\li1 God wuna njambwi kat wand…®. Nj…®vwa kwagalalaa  
\li1 wuna yaagindan naang…®mba kwo ndaa al…® m…®la.   
\li1
\v 43 ndaa l…®m…®n maa m…®n kat kao yil…®ga n…®mba m…®n kat  
\li1 t…®ga kwulakiyowun waa God wand…®  
\p waa p…®l…®wutnd…® Devit.  
\v 44 Devit Kraist kat waga wuna njambwi waa p…®l…®wutnd…®. Kraist Devitna mat nyana waa manda kat wal…®gandi waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 MOSES KWIYA NYAANG∆óT S∆óMOGWI LA N∆óMBANA KAVLE VAK  
\p
\v 45 Jisas nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat wand…®. Nat n…®mba ndino wutndi.  
\v 46 Moses kwiya nyaang…®t s…®mogwi la n…®mba yet…®nja vla ke yet…®ngwa. Kavle vatna yet…®nja. Ndi apma nglei waavwi kwusoga n…®ma sakwat n…®mba t…®ga kava yil…®gandi. N…®ma sakwat n…®mba ndi kat ngwuk apma n…®mba waa wanjangat yil…®gandi. Yisolaa l…®nja ngay wuleilaa nujambwi n…®mba ndaa l…®la kavamba ndaa l…®gandi. N…®ma k…®g…®nda ta ngay wuleilaa njambwi n…®mba ndaa l…®la kavamba ndaa l…®gandi.  
\v 47 Ndi talagwana kwanda kwanda nda s…®kwut…®gandi. Kapmba laataa God kat s…®vla nyaang…®t ngambul…®gandi nat n…®mba v…®njangat. Ng…®ni yaiga nj…®mbla God ndi kat n…®ma vat yigiyand…®.   
\c 21  
\s1 SANYA LAPMAN TALAGWA GOD KAT SANYA KWIL∆ó  
\p
\v 1 Jisas Godna ngaymba l…®ga God kat sanya kwil…®ga n…®mba kat v…®nd…®. Nat n…®ma sanya la n…®mba n…®ma sakwat sanya kwindi, v…®n…®d…®.  
\v 2 T…®ga l…®ga sanya lapman talagwa yalaa mat sanya v…®l…®l…®k kwil…®.  
\v 3 Jisas l…® kat v…®laa wand…®. Kat sanya lapman talagwa nat n…®mba kat kwulaka kwil…®.  
\v 4 Nat n…®mba n…®ma sanyo l…®ga sakwat kwindi. L…® sanya lapman t…®ga l…®la sanya aywaa kwil…®. K…®g…®nda klaleya nat sanya kai waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 GODNA NGAY NG∆óNI SUL∆óGIYANDI  
\p
\v 5 Godna ngaymba l…®ga nat n…®mba wandi. Kan ngay apma ngaya. Apma kambapmba kwutndi. Nat n…®mba apma yelaga nda kwil…®ndi, taagandi ngaymba waa wandi maa Jisas wand…®.  
\v 6 V…®l…®ngwa ngay ng…®ni yaiga nj…®mbla sul…®giyandi. Sul…®ndi maa nat kambak nat kambakna tagumba ana l…®giyand…®. Aywaa sul…®giyandi waa Jisas wand…®.   
\s1 NG∆óNI N∆óMA SAKWAT KAVLE VAT T∆óGIYAND∆ó  
\p
\v 7 Wand…® maa nd…® kat wandi. Njambwi nyan wama vak anda nj…®mbla yaigand…®. Anda nda tak v…®neya. V…®laa wanda vak k…®ngiyan tamba ngway tologa waigan…®n waa wagalandi maa Jisas wand…®.  
\v 8 Ng…®ni n…®ma sakwat n…®mba yalaa wun Kraist wun waa woseka waigandi. Ndi kat ke wukngwa. N…®ma sakwat n…®mba yalaa ng…®ni l…®ga vat tamba ngway tolagand…® waa woseka waigandi. Ndi kat ke wukngwa. Ndina kwupmba ke yiga.  
\v 9 Ng…®ni n…®ma sakwat n…®mba kao yil…®nja vak wukiyangwuk. Nat ngepma n…®mba kat s…®l…®nja vak wukiyangwuk. Wutaa mand…®p mand…®p ke yelav…®kngwa. Kan vak tak yaigand…®. Ng…®ni l…®ga nandinya wata.   
\p
\v 10 Nat ngepma nat ngepma kat s…®vat laakiyandi. Nat kava nat kava kat s…®vat laakiyandi.  
\v 11 Kava kava n…®ma y…®nau kwukiyand…®. Nat n…®mba k…®g…®nda lapman t…®ga kiyaigandi. Nat ngepma ndina n…®mba aywaa yelogwen kat t…®giyandi. Ny…®nangwupmba l…®ga nda v…®laa nat n…®ma sakwat n…®mba vaakiyandi.   
\p
\v 12 Wan wawa vak yalapman t…®nd…®, tat ngwuk kat kwutaa viyaigandi. Ngwuk kat kavle vat yigiyandi. Ngwuk kat kotmak yisolaa l…®nja ngay kaligyandi. Ngwuk kat kalabusmba taagagiyandi. Wuna nj…®vwa kwukngwuk maa ngwuk kat kwutaa kotmak njambwi n…®mba kat kaligiyandi.  
\v 13 Ngwuk kat kwutaa kalinja vak v…®laa nat n…®mba waigandi. Ndi kwutaa kalia n…®mba Godna nj…®vwa kwut…®gandi waa waigandi.  
\v 14 Ngwuk kat kotmak kal…®njeya nj…®mbla ndi kat awat wangweya vak n…®mamba ke yelav…®kngwa.   
\p
\v 15 Awat wangweya nyaang…®t wuna lak kwigiyowun. Ngwuk kat mbukweya nyaang…®t waigangwuk. Wangwuk, wutaa ngwuk kat kai wal…®ga n…®mba ana ngwuk kat kwulakiyandi.  
\v 16 Ngwutna nyaek ny…®me, yakwa n…®mba, ngepma n…®mba, al…® n…®mba ngwuk kat kai walaa kotmak kaligiyandi. Ngwutna nat n…®mba kat kalilaa vatnyagiyandi.  
\v 17 Wuna nj…®vwa kwut…®ngwangat nat n…®ma sakwat n…®mba ngwuk kat kai waigandi.  
\v 18 Ngwuk kat kavle yindi maa ngwuk kavle kavat ana yigiyangwuk. Apma kavat yilaa apma vat t…®giyangwuk.  
\v 19 Ng…®ni yaiga nj…®mbla wun kat kwagalalapman yingweyan nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat yet…®ngweya vat klaigangwuk waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 JERUSALEM WAL∆óNJA NGEPMA KAVLE YIGIYAND∆ó  
\p
\v 20 Jisas wand…®. Nat ngepmana kao yil…®ga n…®mba Jerusalem yalaa ngepma wegwundi, v…®laa Jerusalem kavle yi m…®na l…®gand…® waa yelav…®k ngwula.  
\v 21 Judia wal…®nja n…®ma k…®pmamba l…®giya n…®mba aywaa nduwiat ay ngwula. Ngwuk aywaa Judia kwagala ngwula. Wan yaiga nj…®mbla nat ngepma n…®mba Judia mbaa yalandi.  
\v 22 Ng…®n kavle n…®mba kat s…®giyowun waa God wand…®, tamba la n…®mba p…®l…®wutndi. Yaiga nj…®mbla nd…® s…®giyand…®.  
\v 23 Wan nj…®mbla nyan t…®ga ndi taagwa kat n…®ma miwa yiga t…®gowun. Wan nj…®mbla nyan mbambala glei kwukna ndi taagwa mwunya k…®l…®ga ndi nyangu kat miwa yiga l…®gowun. Kan kava n…®ma sakwat n…®ma vat t…®giyand…®. God ndinyangu kat n…®mamba s…®giyand…®.  
\v 24 Nat n…®mba kat yapmba kal…®ka vatnyagiyandi. Nat n…®mba kat kandi kwutaa kaligiyandi. Kalindi maa kava kavamba yet…®giyandi. Juda ana ndi nat n…®mba Jerusalem kat v…®ga l…®giyandi. V…®ga l…®njeya s…®va ng…®l…®nd…®, Juda lungwamataa yaa v…®ga l…®giyandi.   
\s1 GODNA NYAN YAIGA NJ∆óMBLA  
\p
\v 25 Nya, mbak, s…®ngwut mand…®p mand…®p mbang…® ny…®nangwupmba t…®nd…®, v…®giyandi. V…®laa ng…®paliga ndaigandi. K…®pmamba l…®giya nda n…®mbun v…®laa ng…®paliga ndaigandi. Kava kavamba n…®ma sakwat n…®ma vak t…®giyand…®. Mand…®p mand…®p maawut yelav…®ka l…®giyandi.  
\v 26 N…®ma sakwat wan vak v…®laa vaaka l…®giyandi. Ny…®nangwupmba l…®ga nda, nya, mbak, s…®ngwut yil…®nja yamb…® kwagalalaa mand…®p mand…®p yigiyandi.  
\v 27 T…®ga l…®ga wun Godna vak s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan t…®mbumba ngaga yawun, v…®giyangwuk. Wun n…®ma kwonduo t…®ga nyan vla yaigowun. Wun kat v…®laa nd…® n…®ma nyana waa waigandi.  
\v 28 Wan nda kak kiyand…®, ngwuk wuna mbaapma n…®mba solat as…® ngwula. Wan nda kak kiyand…®, ndi apma vat t…®giyandi waa ndi kat walaa  
\v 29 s…®mogwi l…®ga wapuseput mbutnd…®. Fik wal…®nja mio nat mi kat yelav…®k ngwula.  
\v 30 Nd…®na kupi kwin wogwendeyan nya n…®mamba s…®giyand…® waa yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk. Ngwutna ngepma vatna.  
\v 31 Wawa nyaang…®t k…®ta vatna. Wawa vat v…®laa God ngaga yalaa n…®n kat v…®ga l…®ndeya nj…®mbla tamba ngway tologand…® waa yelav…®k ngwula.   
\p
\v 32 Ngwuk kat wowun. Tak mbambala kan k…®pmamba l…®ga n…®mba ndi ana ng…®l…®giyandi. Tak wawa vak t…®nd…®, v…®laa ng…®l…®giyandi.  
\v 33 Ng…®ni ny…®nangwuk k…®pma ng…®l…®giyand…®. Wawa nyaang…®t ana ng…®l…®giyand…®. Kwo l…®giyand…®. V…®giyandi.   
\s1 YIGUMBA AV∆ó NGWULA  
\p
\v 34 Ngwuk avla ngwula maawut kat yigumba av…® ngwula. Wawa nyaang…®t kat maawut ke t…®v…®ga. N…®mamba n…®ma ngu k…®ga tungwengwan yiga ke l…®ngwa. Wan k…®pmana nda kat m…®na ke yelav…®kngwa. Wan k…®pmana nda kat m…®na yelav…®ka l…®ngweyan wan yaiga nda pagwuga yaigand…®. Ana v…®giyangwuk.  
\v 35 Kan k…®pmamba t…®giyaa kwo n…®mba ndi kat pagwuga yaigand…®. Ndi ana tak v…®giyandi.  
\v 36 Ngwuk wan yaiga vak kat kawiga al…® ngwula. Kawiga l…®ga God kat wagala ngwula. N…®n kat ava kwim…®n maa wan kavle vat ana n…®n kat kavle yigiyand…® waa God kat wagala ngwula. Wun Godna vak s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan wun. Ng…®ni wun yaweya nj…®mbla God ngwuk kat v…®laa apma n…®mba ngwuk waa wamband…® walaa God kat wagala ngwula waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 37 Nandinya nandinya Jisas Godna ngay wuleilaa ndi kat nyaang…®t mbut…®nd…®. Ngan wogwelaa Oliv wal…®nja nduwi wokelaa s…®ndu kwand…®.  
\v 38 Ngambi glei n…®ma sakwat n…®mba Godna ngay wuleindi Jisas waiga nyaang…®t wupmat wuleindi.   
\c 22  
\s1 JISAS KAT S∆óNJANGAT JUDAS KAMWIN KWIND∆ó  
\p
\v 1 Yis tapman bret-nao k…®l…®nja pesto pasova wal…®nja pesto tamba ngway tologand…®.  
\v 2 God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mbagwi Moses kwiya nyaang…®t s…®mogwi la n…®mbogwi Jisas kat vatnyavat t…®ndi. Jisas kat woviyaguga la n…®ma sakwat n…®mba kat vaaka l…®ga anda vapmba nd…® kat vatnyagiyan…®n waa yelav…®ka l…®ndi.   
\p
\v 3 Jisasna mbaapmamba la tamba v…®li kiyeli v…®l…®l…®k n…®mbana k…®ta nyan Judas Iskeriot Seten nd…® kat tavind…® mala kamwin kwivat yind…®.  
\v 4 God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mbagwi soldiana njambwi n…®mba kat yind…®. Yilaa Jisas kat vatnyangweya vat v…®s…®mogwigiyowun waa wand…®.  
\v 5 Wand…®, wutaa solat s…®l…®ndi. Nd…® kat sanya kwindi, vatnyangjeya vak kat ngambul…®ndi.  
\v 6 Jisas kapma l…®nd…®, nd…® kat kwutaa kalingweya vat v…®s…®mogwigiyowun waa wand…® Judas.   
\s1 PASOVANA K∆óG∆óNDA KWUPMAK KAT YIMB∆óT  
\p
\v 7 Yis tapman bret-nao k…®l…®nja nandinya yand…®. Wan naninya nyan sip sip kat vatnyandi k…®vat.  
\v 8 Jisas Pitogwi Jon kat wand…®. Yiga k…®g…®nda agwup mb…®la. Kwupmb…®k, k…®mban…®n waa wand…®, wamb…®t.  
\v 9 Anda kavamba kwukiyaa waa wamb…®t, Jisas wand…®.  
\v 10 Ngepma wuleilaa ngu awmba tulaa kwutaa yila nyan kat v…®giyamb…®t. Nd…®na kwupmba ay mb…®la. Wuleindeya ngaymba v…®laa wuleimba mb…®t.  
\v 11 Wan ngayna njambwi nyan kat awa mb…®la. Njambwi nyan wand…®. Wunogwi wuna mbaapma n…®mbo pestona k…®g…®nda k…®neya kava andamba l…®gand…® waa wand…® waa awamba mb…®t.  
\v 12 Wamb…®t maa awlak ngemba l…®ga kava v…®s…®mogwigiyand…®. Wan kava t…®g…®t njamba t…®giyand…®. Wan kava wuleilaa k…®g…®nda agwup mb…®la waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 13 Wand…® maa yimb…®t. Jisas waa nyaang…®t vla t…®nd…®, v…®mb…®t. Wanda kava wuleilaa k…®g…®nda kwupmb…®k.   
\s1 JISAS ND∆óNA MBAAPMA N∆óMBA KAT K∆óG∆óNDA KWIND∆ó  
\p
\v 14 Pasovana k…®g…®nda k…®l…®nja nj…®mbla tamba yand…®. Yand…®, Jisasna tamb v…®li kiyeli v…®l…®l…®k n…®mba Jisasogwio k…®ta vat ndaa l…®mb…®t k…®g…®nda k…®vat.  
\v 15 Ndaa l…®ndi, Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Kan pestona k…®g…®nda tak ngwutnogwinala kuwa vak apma vatna. Wun woviyaguga l…®gowun. Ng…®ni n…®ma sakwat n…®ma vak wuna lak yaigand…®.  
\v 16 Kan pestona k…®g…®nda nat njamb…® ana k…®giywoun. Kiyalaa God v…®ga l…®ga kava wuleilaa nat njamb…® pestona k…®g…®nda k…®giyowun waa walaa  
\v 17 wain wal…®nja n…®ma ngu l…®ga aw kwutaa God kat s…®vu k…®ga ndi kat kwiga wand…®. Kanjaga ag…® ngwula.  
\v 18 Wun ng…®ni n…®ma ngu ana k…®giyowun. Kiyalaa God v…®ga l…®ga kava wuleilaa nat njamb…® k…®giyowun waa wand…®.  
\v 19 Bret-nao kwutaa God kat s…®vu k…®ga l…®mbalaguga ndi kat kwiga wand…®. Kan wuna mbanga kwiwa. Ngwuk kat kwunapmak wuna mbang…® kwigiyowun. Kan bret-nao k…®ga ngwuk kat kwunakweya vak kat yelav…®k ngwula waa wand…®.  
\v 20 K…®g…®nda k…®ndi maa nat njamb…® wain wal…®nja n…®ma ngu l…®ga aw kwutaa wand…®. Kan ngu God ndinyangu kat kwil…®ga kupi nyaang…®tna. Wuna yelogwen ngwuk kat t…®ga ndaind…®, wan kupi nyaang…®t t…®giyand…®.   
\p
\v 21 Ngwuk awuk ngwula. Wun kat s…®njangat kamwin kwiya nyan kumba n…®nogwinala k…®ta vat t…®gand…®.  
\v 22 Wun ndinyangu kat Godna vak s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan wun. Ng…®ni yiweya vak tamba God v…®nd…®. Pagwula la vat ana nd…®. Wun kat s…®njangat kamwin kwiya nyan nd…® kat n…®mamba miwa ay ngwula waa wand…® mala  
\v 23 ndi awat sowat ngambul…®ndi. Nd…® kat s…®njangat kamwin kwiya nyan anda nyana waa sowat ngambul…®ndi.   
\s1 JISASNA MBAAPMA N∆óMBA NJAMBWI N∆óMBAT T∆óVAT WANDI  
\p
\v 24 Jisasna mbaapma n…®mba walega ngambul…®ndi. N…®na anda nyan n…®na mbaapmana njambwi nyanat t…®giyand…® waa walega ngambul…®ndi.  
\v 25 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Juda ana ndi nat n…®mba ndina njambwi n…®mba t…®gandi. Ndina njambwi n…®mba nat n…®mba kat n…®mamba nj…®ka viyaga vi…®ga l…®ga n…®na nj…®vwa agwuk ngwula waa wal…®ngandi. Wundi mat n…®mba kat kwunapmak v…®ga l…®gan…®n waa woseka wal…®ngandi njambwi n…®mba.  
\v 26 Ndina njambwi n…®mba v…®ga l…®nja vak ngwuk wupma nat n…®mba kat ke v…®ga l…®ngwa. Ngwutna k…®ta nyan njambwi nyanat t…®vat wandeyan mat nyan yet…®l…®ga vak vla yet…®giyand…®. Nat n…®mbana kwundi wuka ndina nj…®vwa kwut…®ga nyan nd…® njambwi nyanat t…®giyand…®.  
\v 27 Kan k…®pmana n…®mba wawa vak vla ana yelav…®t…®gandi. Ndi kupma yelav…®t…®gandi. K…®g…®nda kwutaa kansaga kwila nyan kwo ndaa l…®ga k…®g…®nda ka nyana kwupmba l…®gand…® waa yelav…®t…®gandi. Ngwuk yelav…®tnja vak wupma ke yelav…®kngwa. Wuno wupma ana yelav…®…®gowun. Wuna nj…®vwa kwukngwangat ana yawun. Ngwutna nj…®vwa kwupmat yawun.   
\p
\v 28 Wun kat kavle vat yindi, ngwuk wun kat ana kwagalangwuk. Wunogwinala k…®ta vat yet…®ngwuk.  
\v 29 Ngi kat t…®ga nat n…®mba kat v…®ga l…®ngweya kwondu ngwuk kat kwigiyowun. Wuna nyaek wun kat kwinda kwondu ngwuk kat kwigiyowun.  
\v 30 Ng…®ni God v…®ga l…®ga kava wuleilaa ndinyangu kat v…®ga l…®giyowun. Kan kava kwukweya n…®ma k…®g…®nda wunogwinala k…®giyangwuk. Ngwuk Judana taamba v…®li kiyeli v…®l…®l…®k yelang…® n…®mba kat v…®ga l…®giyangwuk waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 PITA, WUN KAT KAI WAIGAM∆óN WAA WAND∆ó JISAS  
\p
\v 31 Jisas Pita kat wand…®. Saimon, m…®no nat mbaapma n…®mbo Seten ngwuk kat kavle maawut kwivat wand…®. Ngwuk kat n…®ma vat yivat wand…®.  
\v 32 Wun God kat m…®n kat t…®ga wagalagiyowun. M…®na maawupmba kwutaa l…®ma vak mbaa kwagalalam…®n waa God kat wagalawun. Yimeya kavle vat yilaa wan kavle vat kwagalalaa m…®na mbaapma n…®mbana maawut kat kwunakiyam…®n waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 33 Wand…® maa Pita wand…®. N…®ma nyan, yimeya kavle vat manda kat wam…®n. M…®n kat kwutaa kalabusmba taagandeyan m…®nogwinala yigiyowun. M…®n kat vatnyanjeyan wuno wun kat vatnyagiyandi. Ana vaaka l…®gowun waa wand…® Pita  
\v 34 Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Pita m…®n kat nyaang…®t k…®ta waigowun. Awup m…®la. Jisas kat ana v…®gowun waa woseka waigam…®n. Njamb…® kuvuk waigam…®n. Wam…®n mala tak nyaaga viyaigand…® waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 Y∆óMBWI SANYA YAK KAT JISAS WAND∆ó  
\p
\v 35 Jisas nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat wand…®. Tak ngwuk kat wowun mala y…®mbwi sanya man su kalilapman kwo yingwut. Yingwa nj…®mbla k…®ta nda kat kwaka yingwuk? Wagaland…® maa kai waa wandi.  
\v 36 Wandi maa wand…®. Ng…®ni wupma kai. K…®ta nyan y…®mbwi t…®ndeyan kwutaa kaligiyand…®. Sanya l…®ndeyan kwutaa kaligiyand…®. Yak tapman t…®ndeyan alagu waavwi kwilaa sanya klalaa yak k…®ta kaligand…®.  
\v 37 Tamba la n…®mba God waa nyaang…®t p…®l…®wutnja vak wuna lak yaigand…®. Kavle n…®mba kat yil…®nja vak vla Kraist kat yil…®ndi waa tamba p…®l…®wutndi. Wan p…®l…®wutnja vak vak wuna lak yaigand…® waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 38 Wand…® maa nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba wandi. Njambwi nyan n…®n yak v…®l…®l…®k kwutaa l…®gan…®n waa wandi, wan ngiyambak wand…®.   
\s1 OLIV WAL∆óNJA NDUWI WOKELAA GOD KAT WAL∆óND∆ó  
\p
\v 39 Ngepma wogwelaa Oliv wal…®nja nduwi wokend…®. Nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba nd…®na kwupmba wokendi.  
\v 40 Nduwi wokelaa nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba kat wand…®. Ngwutna maawut kavle vat mbaa yilandi waa God kat wagala ngwula waa walaa  
\v 41 ndi kat kwagalalaa samat yind…®. S…®vla ana l…®. Yilaa kwali mamba s…®laa God kat wal…®nd…®.  
\v 42 Nayaek, wam…®n maa wuna lak yaiga kavle vat ana yaigand…®. Wawa vapmba ke yiga. M…®na maawupmba ay. Walapman yimeyan m…®na s…®pana waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 43 (Jisas wal…®nd…® maa ny…®nangwupmba l…®ga ensel ngaga yalaa Jisas kat kwondu ava kwind…®.  
\v 44 Jisas n…®ma vak yelav…®ka l…®ga God kat n…®mamba wagalal…®nd…®. Wagalal…®ga nd…®na mbang…® kangan wand…®, n…®ma waang…®t sawnd…®.)   
\p
\v 45 Wagalalaa laataa nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba ta kavat yind…®. S…®ndu kwandi, v…®nd…®.  
\v 46 V…®laa ndi kat wand…®. Manda kat s…®ndu kwal…®gangwuk. Laataa God kat wagala ngwula. Ngwutna maawut kavle vat mbaa yiland waa wagala ngwula waa Jisas ndi kat s…®vululaa wand…®.   
\s1 JISAS KAT KWUTAA KALINDI  
\p
\v 47 Jisas wal…®nd…® maa n…®ma sakwat n…®mba yandi. Jisasna mbaapmamba la nyan Judas nd…® tata yand…®. Nat n…®mba nd…®na kwupmba yandi. Jisas kat nd…®na k…®pmwi wus…®pmak yand…®.  
\v 48 Jisas nd…® kat wand…®. Judas wun Godna vat s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan wun. Wun kat kwutaa kalinjangat wus…®kam…®n? Waa Jisas wand…® maa  
\v 49 nd…®na mbaapma n…®mba Jisas kat yinjeya vak v…®laa wandi. Njambwi nyan yak kwutaa ndi kat viyagat? Waa wandi, ndina  
\v 50 k…®ta nyan yak kwutaa laataa God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi nyana nj…®vwa kwut…®ga nyana waan kal…®tnd…®. Yaagindan naang…®mba t…®ga waan kal…®tnd…®.  
\v 51 Jisas wupma ke yiga waa walaa waan ta kava taamba taaga kwunatnd…®.   
\p
\v 52 Kwunataa God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mbagwi, Godna ngay v…®ga l…®ga n…®mbo, Judana njambwi n…®mba kat Jisas wand…®. Yak mi kwutaa waleavat yal…®gangwuk. S…®kwut…®ga nyan kat kwut…®nja vla wun kat kwupmak yal…®gangwuk. Manda kat wupma yal…®gangwuk.  
\v 53 Tak nandinya nandinya ngwutnogwinala Godna ngaymba l…®l…®wun. Tak wun kat kalivat ana yal…®ngwuk. Ngwuk kavle n…®mba wun kat kwulakngweya nj…®mbla mbambala waa wand…® Jisas.   
\s1 PITA JISAS KAT KAI WAND∆ó  
\p
\v 54 Jisas kat kwutaa God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi nyana ngayat kalindi. Tata yindi, Pita ng…®ni la yil…®nd…®. Nd…®na ngwaymba ana yil…®nd…®.  
\v 55 Kwo alagumba l…®ga n…®mba mbang…® ya tolapmak ya sal…®ndi. Sal…®laa k…®ta vat ndaa l…®nd…®.  
\v 56 Ndaa l…®nd…® maa kan ngayna nj…®vwa kwuta taagwa nyan k…®ta nd…®na m…®ndama v…®ga wal…®. Kan nyan tak Jisasogwio t…®nd…® waa wal…®.  
\v 57 Wal…® maa Pita wand…®. Taagwa nyan kai. Jisas kat ana v…®ga l…®gowun waa wand…®.  
\v 58 T…®ga l…®ga nat nyan Pita kat v…®laa wand…®. M…®n Jisasna mbbapma nyan m…®n? Waa wagaland…® maa Pita kai wand…®.  
\v 59 Samat t…®ga nat nyan Pita kat v…®laa wand…®. Wan nyan tak Jisasogwionala t…®nd…®. V…®wun. Mb…®t k…®ta ngepma nyan mb…®t. Galili nyan mb…®t waa wand…® maa Pita nd…® kat wand…®.  
\v 60 Wan angamak waam…®n. Nd…® kat ana v…®ga l…®gowun waa wand…® maa tak nyaaga viyand…®.  
\v 61 Viyand…® maa Jisas Pita kat lungwamaka v…®nd…®. V…®nd…®, tak Jisas Pita kat wanda nyaang…®t kat Pita yelav…®tnd…®. Tak wun kat kuvut njamb…® kai waigam…®n. Wam…®n maa tak nyaaga viyaigand…® waa wanda vak Pita yelav…®ka l…®nd…®.  
\v 62 Yelav…®ka l…®ga Pita n…®mamba nglaga wogwend…®.   
\s1 JISAS KAT NJ∆óKA WAGA VIYAL∆óNDI  
\p
\v 63 Jisas kat kwuta la n…®mba nd…® kat nj…®ka waga taambamba viyal…®ndi.  
\v 64 Nd…®na m…®ni waavwi ngilaa m…®ndamamba viyaga wal…®ndi. Tamba la profet mbutnja vla m…®n kat viyal…®ga nyana s…® ambuk waa kasega wal…®ndi.  
\v 65 Nat n…®ma sakwat kavle vat ndi kat yil…®ndi.   
\s1 JUDANA NJAMBWI N∆óMBA KOT WUT∆óNDI  
\p
\v 66 Ngambi ndand…®, Judana njambwi n…®mba yisolaa l…®ndi. God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mba, Moses kwiya nyaang…®t s…®mogwi la n…®mba aywaa yisolaa l…®ga Jisas n…®n kat agiya wandi.  
\v 67 Jisas wuleind…® maa nd…® kat wagalandi. M…®n God wand…®, yaa nyan m…®n? Kraist m…®n? Waa wagalandi maa Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Wun Kraist wun waa wagewan ngwuk ana wukengwuk.  
\v 68 Ngwuk kat nyaang…®t k…®ta wagalagewan ngwuk ana awat wagengwuk. Wun kat ana kwagalangwuk, kwo yigiyowun. Manda kat wagalangweya vat awat waigowun. Kai wowun.  
\v 69 Wun Godna vak s…®mogwi l…®ga nyan wun. Ng…®ni God t…®ga kava yilaa nd…®na yaagindan naang…®mba ndaa l…®wun, wun kat nd…®na kwondu kwigiyand…® waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 70 Wand…® maa wandi. M…®n Godna nyan m…®n? Wandi 70 maa ngiyambak wangwa waa wand…® Jisas.  
\v 71 Wand…® maa wandi. Nat n…®mba nyaang…®t mbutnjangat ana waigan…®n. Wun Godna nyan wun waa ngiyambak kavle vat mbuta waa wandi.   
\c 23  
\s1 JISAS KAT PAILATNA NGAYAT KALINDI KOTMAK KAT  
\p
\v 1 Yisola la n…®mba laataa Jisas kat kwutaa Pailat wal…®nja njambwi nyana ngayat kalindi.  
\v 2 Kalilaa Pailat kat wandi. Nd…® Juda kat kavle maawut kwil…®gand…®. Njambwi nyan Sisa kat takis sanya ke kwiga waa wal…®ngand…®. Sisa njambwi king ana nd…®. Wun njambwi king, Kraist wun waa wal…®gand…® waa Pailat kat woseka wandi.  
\v 3 Wandi mala Pailat Jisas kat wagaland…®. M…®n Judana njambwi king m…®n waa wagaland…®, Jisas wand…®. M…®n m…®nay…® wupma waa.  
\v 4 Pailat God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mbogwi nat n…®mba kat wand…®. Jisas nd…® kavle vat ana yind…®. V…®ga l…®gowun waa wand…® Pailat.  
\v 5 Wand…® maa ndi n…®ma kwundimba walega wandi. Kai Judana ngepma ngepma yiga kavle maawut ksil…®gand…®. Galili laataa yiga kavle maawut kwiga kumba t…®na kavat yand…® waa Pailat kat walega wand…®.   
\s1 JISAS KAT HEROTNA NGAYAT KALINDI KOTMAK KAT  
\p
\v 6 Galili laataa waa wal…®nja nyaang…®t wutaa Pailat ndi kat wagaland…®. Nd…® Galili nyana waa wagaland…®, awa wandi.  
\v 7 Njambwi nyan Herot Galili n…®mba kat v…®ga l…®gand…® waa yelav…®taa Jisas kat kwutaa Herotna ngayat kali ngwula waa wand…®. Wan njimbla Herot Jerusalemba t…®nd…®. Sivla kavat ana kalindi.   
\p
\v 8 Kalindi, Herot Jisas kat v…®laa solat s…®l…®nd…®. Tak Jisas kwuta n…®ma nj…®vwa wutnd…®. Nd…® kat vivat woviyaguga l…®nd…®. Jisas kwuta n…®ma nj…®vwa k…®ta Herot v…®vat woviyaguga t…®nd…®.  
\v 9 Nd…® Jisas kat n…®ma sakwat nyaang…®t wagaland…®. Jisas nd…® kat ana awat wand…®.  
\v 10 God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mbogwi Moses kwiya nyaan…®t s…®mogwi la n…®mbo laataa n…®ma kwundimba Jisas kat kavle nyaang…®t ngambundi.  
\v 11 Herotnogwi nd…®na soldia dino Jisas kat nj…®t…®ndi. Njambwi n…®mba kwusol…®nja apma waavwi nd…® kat kasega kwusondi. Kwusolaa Pailatnat kalindi.  
\v 12 Tamba Pailatnogwio Herotnogwi walaa l…®mb…®k. Wan nandinya k…®mb…®k kwupmb…®k.   
\s1 JISAS KAT DIWAI KROSMBA KAALAGIYANGWUK WAA WAND∆ó PAILAT  
\p
\v 13 Pailat wand…® maa God kat kwunat…®ga njambwi n…®mba, Judana nat njambwi n…®mba, nat n…®mba yaa yisolaa l…®ndi.  
\v 14 Yandi maa Pailat ndi kat wand…®. Wan nyan Juda kat kavle maawut kwil…®gand…® waa walaa wun kat kiyangwuk. Nd…® kat wagalalaa wangwa vat kavle yinda vat ana v…®ga l…®gowun. Nd…® kavle vat ana yind…®.  
\v 15 Wowun maa Herotnat kalingwuk Herot nd…®no kavle vat yinda vat ana v…®ga l…®nd…®. Nd…® kavle vat and yind…®. Nd…® kat manda kat vatnyavat wangwuk. Ana nglaatnd…®.  
\v 16 Ngi kat t…®ga nd…® kat viyalaa kwagalgiyowun waa wand…® Pailat.  
\v 17 Kan Pailatna vatna naambi naambi pestona nj…®mbla kalabusmba la k…®ta nyan kat kwagalal…®nd…®.   
\p
\v 18 Kwagalgiyowun waa wand…® maa ndi wandi. Kai nd…® kat ke kwagalaga. Nat nyan Barabas nd…® kat kwagala m…®la waa wandi.  
\v 19 Wan nyan Barabas tamba gavman kat kao yil…®nd…®. Kao yiga l…®ga k…®ta nyan kat vatnyand…®, kalabusmba nd…® kat taagandi.  
\v 20 Wandi maa Pailat Jisas kat kwagalavat ndi kat nat njamb…® wand…®.  
\v 21 Ndi walega wandi. Diwai krosmba nd…® kat kaala. Diwai krosmba nd…® kat kaala waa walega wandi.  
\v 22 Pailat laataa ndi kat kuvut wan njamb…® wand…®. Kavle vat yinda vat anda vatna. Kavle vat yinda vat ana v…®ga l…®gowun. Nd…® kavle vat ana yind…®. Nd…® kat manda kat vatnyagiyowun. Nd…® kat viyalaa kwagalagiyowun waa wand…® maa  
\v 23 ndi n…®ma kwundimba walega wal…®ndi. Nd…® kat diwai krosmba kaala waa wal…®ndi. God kat kwunata njambwi n…®mbogwi nat n…®mba walega wal…®nja vat Pailat kat kwulatndi.  
\v 24 Nd…® kat kalilaa ngwutna maawupmba vatnyagiyangwuk waa Pailat wand…®.  
\v 25 Tamba gavman kat kao l…®ga nat nyan kat vatnya la nyan kalabusmba t…®ga nyan Pailat wand…® maa nd…® kat kwagalandi. Juda wandi maa nd…® kat kwagalandi. Jisas ndi kat kwind…®.   
\s1 JISAS KAT DIWAI KROSMBA KAALANDI  
\p
\v 26 Jisas kat kwutaa kaliga nat k…®ta nyan kat v…®ndi. Nd…®na s…® Saimon. Nd…®na ngepmamba l…®ga Jerusalemat yal…®nd…®, v…®ndi. Nd…® kat kwutaa kiwai kros nd…®na nyambupmba taagandi, walalaa kalind…®. Nd…® Jisasna kwupmba yiga walalaa kalind…®.   
\p
\v 27 N…®ma sakwat n…®mba ndu lagwa nd…®na kwupmba yiga nglal…®ndi.  
\v 28 Jisas lungwamaka taagwa kat v…®ga wand…®. Judana taagwa ngwuk wun kat ke ngla l…®ngwa. Ngwuk avla angla ngwula. Ngwutna nyangu kat angla ngwula.  
\v 29 Ng…®ni yaiga kavle nj…®mbla kupma waigandi. Nyan kwutapman taagwa, nyan mwunya kwilapman taagwa apma vat t…®gandi waa ng…®ni waigandi.  
\v 30 Ng…®ni yaiga kavle nj…®mbla njduwi kat waigand…®. N…®n kat ndaiga teg…®l…®nd…®, wundumba yigiyan…®n. Mat nduwi kat waigandi. N…®n kat kapmand…®, pakwulaa apma vat t…®giyan…®n waa waigandi.  
\v 31 Wun kavle vat ana yiwun. Mbambala wun kat n…®ma vat yil…®gandi. Ngwuk kavle vat yil…®ngangwuk Ng…®ni ngwuk kat n…®ma vat yigiyandi. Ngwuk kat yinjeya n…®ma vat n…®mana. Mbambala wun kat yil…®nja n…®ma vak matna waa wand…® Jisas.   
\p
\v 32 Jisasogwinala kavle vat ykla mb…®t nyan kalindi. Mb…®k kat vatnyavat kalindi.  
\v 33 Nambu ava wal…®nja kava yalaa Jisas kat diwai krosmba kaalandi. Kavle vat yila mb…®t nyan mb…®k kat angang…®mba kaalandi, l…®mb…®t.  
\v 34 Kaalandi maa Jisas God kat wand…®. Nyaek wun kat kavle vat yil…®nja vak kwagala m…®la. Ndina maawut ana yelav…®ka l…®gandi waa wand…®. Nat n…®mba satu kasega kwulata nyan Jisasna waavwi kland…®.  
\v 35 N…®ma sakwat n…®mba yisoga v…®l…®ndi. Judana njambwi n…®mba ndino v…®l…®ndi. V…®ga kasega wal…®ndi. Jisas nat n…®mba kat kwunapmat t…®nd…®. Mbambala manda kat avla nd…®na mbang…® ana kwunat…®gand…®. Nd…® God wand…®, yaa nyan ana nd…®. Nd…® Kraist ana nd…® waa kasega wal…®ndi.  
\v 36 Soldia ndino kasendi. Kavle njangu veil…®ga ngu Jisas k…®nda kat kwil…®ndi.  
\v 37 Kwiga wal…®ndi. M…®n Judana king ana m…®n waa kasega wandi.  
\v 38 Diwai krosmba nyaang…®t p…®l…®wutaa taagandi. Nd…® Judana kinga waa p…®l…®wutaa taagandi.   
\p
\v 39 Kavle vat yila mb…®t nyana k…®ta nyan diwai krosmba l…®ga Jisas kat kasega wand…®. M…®n Kraist t…®geman avla m…®na mbang…® kwunataa an kat kwunakem…®n waa kasega wand…®.  
\v 40 Nat naang…®mba la nyan nd…® kat kai walaa wand…®. Manda kat wupma wal…®gam…®n God kat ana vaaka l…®gam…®n? M…®n ana kiyaigam…®n?  
\v 41 Kavle vat yiliangat vatnyagiyandi. Nd…® wupma kai. Nd…® kavle vat ana yind…® waa nat nyan kat walaa Jisas kat wand…®.  
\v 42 Njambwi nyan kingat t…®meya nj…®mbla wunkat maawut ke t…®v…®ga waa wand…® maa Jisas nd…® kat wand…®.  
\v 43 M…®n kat woseka ana wowun. Mbambala wunogwinala nyinangwupmba t…®giyam…®n waa wand…®.   
\s1 JISAS LAMBA WUNDUMBU YIND∆ó  
\p
\v 44 Nya n…®ndi namb…®t…®, kulun wand…®. Kulun walaa t…®ga l…®ga 3 klok nglaambu ng…®l…®nd…®, nya s…®nd…®.  
\v 45 Kulun wand…®, Godna ngay njambia la kava t…®v…®nda n…®ma waavwi avla ng…®l…®tnd…®.   
\p
\v 46 Jisas n…®ma kwundimba walega wand…®. Nyaek wowun mala wuna wundumbu m…®nai l…®ga kavat yigand…® waa walaa wundumbu yind…®.   
\p
\v 47 V…®ga la njambwi soldia kiyanda vak v…®laa Godna s…® kwutaa katsolaa wand…®. Wan nyan kavle nyan ana nd…®. Apma vat yeta nyana waa wand…®.   
\p
\v 48 Yalaa va n…®mba v…®laa kavle vat yindi wandi. Ndina maawut viyal…®nd…®, yindi.   
\p
\v 49 Jisasna al…® n…®mbogwi Galilimba l…®ga nd…®na kwupmba ya tagwo s…®vlamba laataa l…®ga v…®l…®ndi.   
\s1 JISASNA S∆óM WAANGUMBA TAAGANDI  
\p
\v 50 Judana njambwi nyan k…®ta l…®nd…®. Nd…®na s…® Josep. Nd…® apma nyana. Nd…® God waa nyaang…®pmba yet…®l…®ga nyana.  
\v 51 Tat Judana njambwi n…®mba yisolaa Jisas kat vatnyagiyam…®n waa wanja nj…®mbla nd…® kat kai wand…®. Nd…®na ngepma Arimatia. Nd…® God ndinyangu kat v…®ga l…®ndeya nj…®mbla kat kawiga l…®nd…®.  
\v 52 Wan nyan Pailat ta ngay wuleilaa Jisasna s…®m kat wagaland…®.  
\v 53 Nd…® wokelaa kwutaa klanda kal…®nd…® k…®pmat. Klanda kalilaa waavwimba mbaataa kaliga kambapmba vanja waangumba taagand…®. Kan waangumba tak ndu nyana s…®m ana taagandi. Kupi waangua.  
\v 54 Nd…®na s…®m waangumba taaganda nandinya nj…®vwa lapman nandinya kat kwanda kwanda kwunat…®nja nandinya.   
\p
\v 55 Galilimba l…®ga Jisasna kwupmba yaa taagwa Josepna kwupmba yiga taaganda waangu v…®ndi.  
\v 56 V…®laa lungwamataa yindi. Nd…®na s…®mba salapmat apma njangu weil…®ga ngwaat klavat yindi. Yilaa nat nandinya ana yandi. Nj…®vwa lapman nandinya. Ndi kwo l…®ndi. Tamba Moses kwiya nyaang…®pmba kwo l…®ndi.   
\c 24  
\s1 JISAS KIYALAA L∆óGA LAATND∆ó  
\p
\v 1 Sande ngambi ngan wat taagwa laataa tak yisoga taaganja apma njangu veil…®ga ngwaat kwutaa waanguat yindi. Nat taagwa ndino yindi.  
\v 2 Tak waangu t…®v…®nja kambak kwo kavamba t…®nd…®, v…®ndi. Waangu ana t…®v…®nd…®.  
\v 3 Waangu wuleilaa njambwi nyan Jisasna s…®m ana v…®ndi.  
\v 4 Mand…®p mand…®p yelav…®taa sawun mbang…® waavwi kwusolaa la mb…®t v…®l…®l…®k pal…® kat v…®ndi. Mb…®tna waavwi kemband…®.  
\v 5 V…®laa vaaka l…®ga nambu s…®landalaa l…®ndi. V…®l…®l…®k pal…® ndi kat wamb…®t. Kan kava kiyala n…®mbana kava. Kumba kwo l…®ga nyan kat manda kat kwat…®gangwuk.  
\v 6 Nd…® kumba ana l…®gand…®. Tamba laataa yind…®. Tak Galilimba t…®ga ngwuk kat mbut…®nda nyaang…®t ana yelav…®ka l…®gangwuk?  
\v 7 Tak Jisas ngwuk kat wand…®. Wun ndinyangu kat kwunat…®ga nyan. Wun kat kavle n…®mba kwutaa diwai krosmba kaalagiyandi. Kiyalaa l…®ga kuvuk wan nandinya laakiyowun waa tamba ngwuk kat wand…® waa wamb…®t.  
\v 8 Wamb…®t maa tak Jisas wanda nyaang…®t kat yelav…®tndi.  
\v 9 Waangu kwagalalaa lungwamataa yiga Jisasna mbaapmamba la tamba v…®li kiyeli k…®ta n…®mba kat mbutndi. Nat n…®mba n…®mbun kat mbutndi.  
\v 10 V…®laa mbuta taagwa k…®k…®yak Magdala wal…®nja ngepmamba lat Maria, Joana, Jemisna nyime nat Maria, nat taagwa. Ndi v…®laa Jisasna mbaapma n…®mba kat mbutndi.  
\v 11 Mbutndi, wutaa woseka wandi waa yelav…®tndi.  
\v 12 (Pita wutaa laataa waanguat p…®l…®ga yind…®. Yilaa tamb…®lalaa yisolaa v…®nd…®. S…®m ana v…®nd…®. Tat mbaatnja waavwi m…®na t…®nd…®, v…®nd…®. V…®laa mand…®p mand…®p yelav…®taa yind…®.)   
\s1 EMEAS YIL∆óNJA YAMB∆óMBA JISAS KAT V∆óMB∆óT  
\p
\v 13 Jisasna mbaapma nyan v…®l…®l…®k Jerusalem kwagalaa Emeas wal…®nja ngepmat yimb…®t. Wan ngepmana yamb…® s…®vla ana nd…®. Mail s…®la v…®li m…®na l…®nd…®.  
\v 14 Yiga l…®ga Jerusalemba ta vak kat ngambuga yil…®mb…®t.  
\v 15 Ngambuga yil…®mb…®k, Jisas mb…®la ngwaymba mb…®logwio k…®ta vat yal…®nd…®.  
\v 16 Jisas kat m…®ni m…®na v…®mb…®t. Ana yelav…®pmb…®k. God mb…®k kat mand…®p maawut kwind…®.   
\p
\v 17 Jisas mb…®k kat wand…®. Yiga l…®ga manda vak kat mbang…® k…®l…®pang…® yiga ngambul…®gamb…®t waa wand…®,  
\v 18 v…®l…®lk pal…®na k…®ta nyan wand…®. Nd…®na s…® Kliopas. Jerusalemba t…®ga mbambala nglei yam…®n? Jerusalemba ta vak ana wupm…®n? Waa wand…® maa Jisas wand…®.  
\v 19 Anda vatna. Ana wukwun waa wand…®, wamb…®t. Jisas nd…® Nasaret nyan nd…® God waa nyaang…®t mbuta nyan. Nd…® profetna. Nd…® apma nyaang…®t ndinyangu kat mbut…®nd…®. Ndi kat n…®ma nj…®vwa kwuka ndi kat kwunat…®nd…®.  
\v 20 God kat kwunt…®ga njambwi n…®mbo n…®na ngepmana nat njambwi n…®mbo nd…® kat kwutaa vatnyavak kalindi. Kalilaa nd…® kat kiwai krosmba kaalandi.  
\v 21 Tak yelav…®tn…®n. N…®n Juda kat kwunapmak yand…® waa yelav…®ka t…®n…®n. Wupma kai. Nd…® kat vatnyandi. Nangaytmba vatnyandi.  
\v 22 N…®na mbaapmana taagwa mbambala ngambi ngan waangu la kava yilaa yalaa n…®n kat mbunja nyaang…®t wutaa ng…®paliga nda n…®n.  
\v 23 Nd…®na s…®m waangumba ana l…®gand…®. Kwo waangua. Ensel v…®l…®l…®k n…®n kat tamba laataa yind…® waa wamb…®t maa wundi lagwa yaa n…®n kat mbutndi.  
\v 24 Mbutndi maa n…®na mbaapmana nat n…®mba waangu yilaa v…®ndi. Taagwa woseka ana wandi. Kwo waangua. Jisas kat kwatevila l…®ndi waa Jisas kat wamb…®t.   
\p
\v 25 Wamb…®t maa Jisas mb…®k kat wand…®. Mb…®la maawut yigumba ana yelav…®ka l…®gamb…®t. Tamba la profet p…®l…®wutnja nyaang…®t maawupmba ana kwutaa l…®gamb…®t. Maawupmba ana yelav…®k l…®gamb…®t.  
\v 26 Tamba p…®l…®wutndi. Kraist nd…® tat kiyaigand…®. Kiyalaa apma kava t…®ndeya kava yigiyand…® waa tamba p…®l…®wutndi waa mb…®k kat walaa  
\v 27 tamba Moseso profetno nat n…®mbo Kraist kat p…®l…®wutnja nyaang…®t aywaa mb…®k kat mbutnd…®.   
\p
\v 28 Yiga l…®ga Emeas wal…®nja ngepmat yandi. Jisas mb…®k kat kwagalalaa yivat wand…®.  
\v 29 Mb…®k kai wamb…®t. Tamba ngana. Anogwinala s…®ndu kwalinjeya ngaymba kwaigam…®n waa wamb…®t maa ngay wuleindi.  
\v 30 Kig…®nda k…®vat yindi. Yiga Jisas bret-nao klalaa God kat s…®vu k…®laa mb…®k kat l…®mbala kwind…®.  
\v 31 Kwind…® maa nd…®na m…®ndama v…®ga maawut yelav…®pmb…®k. Nd…® Jisas waa yelav…®pmb…®k maa mb…®k kat kwagalalaa kwo s…®lawota yind…®. Ana v…®mb…®k.  
\v 32 Yind…® maa awat sowat ngambuga t…®mb…®t. Tak yamb…®mba an kat tamba la n…®mba p…®l…®wutnja nyaang…®t mbut…®nd…® maa ana maawut viyal…®nd…®. Apma nyaang…®tna waa yelav…®taa waa walaa  
\v 33 laataa Jerusalemat lungwamataa yimb…®t. Yimb…®t, Jisasna mbaapmamba la tamba v…®li kiyeli kita n…®mba yisolaa l…®ndi, v…®mb…®t.  
\v 34 Jisas tamba laataa kwo l…®gand…®. Saimon nd…®no nd…® kat v…®nd…® waa ndi kat wamb…®t.  
\v 35 Jisas mb…®k kat yamb…®mba mbutnda nyaang…®t, bret-nao kwutaa l…®mbala mb…®k kat kwinda vat aywaa mbupmb…®k.   
\s1 JISASNA MBAAPMA N∆óMBA ND∆ó KAT V∆óNDI  
\p
\v 36 Mbut…®mb…®k mala Jisas s…®lawota yand…®. Yanda vat ana v…®ndi. Nd…®na n…®nd…®mba t…®nd…®, v…®ndi. Laataa ndi kat apma vat al…® ngwula wand…®.  
\v 37 Ndi Jisas kat v…®laa kan wundumbua waa vaaka l…®ndi.  
\v 38 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Manda kat vaaka l…®gangwuk.  
\v 39 Wun wundumbu ana wun. Wuna man taamba av…®. Wuna mbang…® agwuk. Mbang…® ava tuwa vat wundumbu wupma ana l…®gandi waa walaa  
\v 40 (nd…®na man taambana lumwin ndi kat s…®mogwind…®.)  
\v 41 Ndi n…®mamba solat s…®ga mand…®p mand…®p velav…®ka l…®ndi. Jisas ndi kat wand…®. K…®g…®nda ngil…®ga waa wand…® maa  
\v 42 nd…® kat kami k…®ta kwindi.  
\v 43 Klalaa k…®nd…®, v…®ndi.   
\p
\v 44 Jisas ndi kat wand…®. Tamba la n…®mba, Moses, profet, Sam wal…®na nyaang…®t p…®l…®wutnja n…®mba tamba wun kat nyaang…®t p…®l…®wutndi. Tak ngwutnogwinala t…®wan p…®l…®wutnja nyaang…®tmba yet…®giyowun waa wowun. Mbambala tamba wan nyaang…®pmba ngiyambak yet…®wun waa walaa  
\v 45 tamba p…®o…®wutnja n…®mbana angwa nyaang…®t ndi kat v…®s…®mogwind…®. V…®s…®mogwiga wand…®.  
\v 46 Kraist kiyalaa nandinya kuvut t…®ga laakiyand…® waa tamba p…®l…®wutndi. P…®l…®wutnja vla yiwun.  
\v 47 Yiwun maa ngwuk kava kava yilaa nyaang…®t mbukiyangwuk. Kavle maawut kwagalangweyan God ngwutna kavle vat s…®l…®mbwigiyand…® waa mbukiyangwuk. Tak Jerusalemba l…®ga n…®mba kat mbukiyangwuk.  
\v 48 Kiyalaa laakwa vat ngwut m…®nimba tamba v…®ngwuk.  
\v 49 Samat t…®ga wowun maa wuna nyaek ngwuk kat nd…®na waagan kwigiyand…®. Ngwuk Jerusalemba t…®ga kwo kawiga al…® ngwula. Nyinangwupmba l…®ga yaiga kwondu ngwuk kat yaigand…®.   
\s1 GOD WAND∆ó MAA JISAS NYINANGWUTNAT WOKEND∆ó  
\p
\v 50 Jerusalem kwagalalaa Betani wal…®nja ngepmat yindi. Yindi maa Jisas taamba katsond…®. Katsolaa apma vat al…® ngwula wand…®.  
\v 51 Wal…®ga ndi kat kwagalalaa nyinangwutnat wokend…®.  
\v 52 Ndi solat s…®ga nd…®na s…® kwutaa katsolaa Jerusalemat lungwamataa yindi.  
\v 53 Nandinya nandinya Godna ngay wuleilaa solat s…®ga Godna s…® kwutaa katsol…®ndi. Ngiyambak.   